var book = {
	"name": "Jeremiah",
	"numChapters": 52,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18948A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18948A\"></sup>Jeremiah the son of Hilkiah, of the priests who were in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18948B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18948B\"></sup>Anathoth in the land of Benjamin,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>to whom the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18949C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18949C\"></sup>Josiah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18949D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18949D\"></sup>Amon, king of Judah, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18949E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18949E\"></sup>thirteenth year of his reign.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It came also in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18950F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18950F\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, until the end of the eleventh year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18950G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18950G\"></sup>Zedekiah the son of Josiah, king of Judah, until the exile of Jerusalem in the fifth month.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Before I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18952H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18952H\"></sup>formed you in the womb I knew you,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18952I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18952I\"></sup>before you were born I consecrated you;I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18952J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18952J\"></sup>appointed you a prophet to the nations.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18953K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18953K\"></sup>I said, “Alas, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>!Behold, I do not know how to speak,Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18953L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18953L\"></sup>I am a youth.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,“Do not say, ‘I am a youth,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18954M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18954M\"></sup>Because everywhere I send you, you shall go,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18954N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18954N\"></sup>all that I command you, you shall speak.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18955O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18955O\"></sup>Do not be afraid of them,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18955P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18955P\"></sup>I am with you to deliver you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> stretched out His hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18956Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18956Q\"></sup>touched my mouth, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,“Behold, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18956R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18956R\"></sup>put My words in your mouth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18957S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18957S\"></sup>I have appointed you this day over the nations and over the kingdoms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18957T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18957T\"></sup>To pluck up and to break down,To destroy and to overthrow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18957U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18957U\"></sup>To build and to plant.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying, “What do you see, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18958V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18958V\"></sup>Jeremiah?” And I said, “I see a rod of an almond tree.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “You have seen well, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18959W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18959W\"></sup>I am watching over My word to perform it.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me a second time saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18960X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18960X\"></sup>What do you see?” And I said, “I see a boiling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18960Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18960Y\"></sup>pot, facing away from the north.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18961Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18961Z\"></sup>Out of the north the evil will break forth on all the inhabitants of the land.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For, behold, I am calling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18962AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18962AA\"></sup>all the families of the kingdoms of the north,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; “and they will come and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18962AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18962AB\"></sup>set each one his throne at the entrance of the gates of Jerusalem, and against all its walls round about and against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18962AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18962AC\"></sup>cities of Judah.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will pronounce My judgments on them concerning all their wickedness, whereby they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18963AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18963AD\"></sup>forsaken Me and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18963AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18963AE\"></sup>offered sacrifices to other gods, and worshiped the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18963AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18963AF\"></sup>works of their own hands.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18964AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18964AG\"></sup>gird up your loins and arise, and speak to them all which I command you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18964AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18964AH\"></sup>Do not be dismayed before them, or I will dismay you before them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now behold, I have made you today as a fortified city and as a pillar of iron and as walls of bronze against the whole land, to the kings of Judah, to its princes, to its priests and to the people of the land.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will fight against you, but they will not overcome you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18966AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18966AI\"></sup>I am with you to deliver you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Now the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18968A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18968A\"></sup>proclaim in the ears of Jerusalem, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I remember concerning you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18968B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18968B\"></sup>devotion of your youth,The love of your betrothals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18968C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18968C\"></sup>Your following after Me in the wilderness,Through a land not sown.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Israel was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18969D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18969D\"></sup>holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18969E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18969E\"></sup>first of His harvest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18969F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18969F\"></sup>All who ate of it became guilty;Evil came upon them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O house of Jacob, and all the families of the house of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18971G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18971G\"></sup>What injustice did your fathers find in Me,That they went far from MeAnd walked after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18971H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18971H\"></sup>emptiness and became empty?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“They did not say, ‘Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18972I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18972I\"></sup>brought us up out of the land of Egypt,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18972J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18972J\"></sup>led us through the wilderness,Through a land of deserts and of pits,Through a land of drought and of deep darkness,Through a land that no one crossedAnd where no man dwelt?’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I brought you into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18973K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18973K\"></sup>fruitful landTo eat its fruit and its good things.But you came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18973L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18973L\"></sup>defiled My land,And My inheritance you made an abomination.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18974M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18974M\"></sup>priests did not say, ‘Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’And those who handle the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18974N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18974N\"></sup>did not know Me;The rulers also transgressed against Me,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18974O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18974O\"></sup>prophets prophesied by BaalAnd walked after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18974P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18974P\"></sup>things that did not profit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Therefore I will yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18975Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18975Q\"></sup>contend with you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And with your sons’ sons I will contend.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18976R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18976R\"></sup>cross to the coastlands of Kittim and see,And send to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18976S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18976S\"></sup>Kedar and observe closelyAnd see if there has been such <i>a thing</i> as this!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Has a nation changed godsWhen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18977T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18977T\"></sup>they were not gods?But My people have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18977U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18977U\"></sup>changed their gloryFor that which does not profit.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Be appalled, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18978V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18978V\"></sup>O heavens, at this,And shudder, be very desolate,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“For My people have committed two evils:They have forsaken Me,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18979W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18979W\"></sup>fountain of living waters,To hew for themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18979X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18979X\"></sup>cisterns,Broken cisternsThat can hold no water.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Is Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18980Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18980Y\"></sup>a slave? Or is he a homeborn servant?Why has he become a prey?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The young <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18981Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18981Z\"></sup>lions have roared at him,They have roared loudly.And they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18981AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18981AA\"></sup>made his land a waste;His cities have been destroyed, without inhabitant.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Also the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18982AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18982AB\"></sup>Memphis and TahpanhesHave shaved the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18982AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18982AC\"></sup>crown of your head.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Have you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18983AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18983AD\"></sup>done this to yourselfBy your forsaking the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your GodWhen He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18983AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18983AE\"></sup>led you in the way?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But now what are you doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18984AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18984AF\"></sup>on the road to Egypt,To drink the waters of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18984AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18984AG\"></sup>Nile?Or what are you doing on the road to Assyria,To drink the waters of the Euphrates?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18985AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18985AH\"></sup>Your own wickedness will correct you,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18985AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18985AI\"></sup>apostasies will reprove you;Know therefore and see that it is evil and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18985AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18985AJ\"></sup>bitterFor you to forsake the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18985AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18985AK\"></sup>the dread of Me is not in you,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“For long ago <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18986AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18986AL\"></sup>I broke your yoke<i>And</i> tore off your bonds;But you said, ‘I will not serve!’For on every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18986AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18986AM\"></sup>high hillAnd under every green treeYou have lain down as a harlot.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Yet I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18987AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18987AN\"></sup>planted you a choice vine,A completely faithful seed.How then have you turned yourself before MeInto the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18987AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18987AO\"></sup>degenerate shoots of a foreign vine?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Although you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18988AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18988AP\"></sup>wash yourself with lyeAnd use much soap,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18988AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18988AQ\"></sup>stain of your iniquity is before Me,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18989AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18989AR\"></sup>How can you say, ‘I am not defiled,I have not gone after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18989AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18989AS\"></sup>Baals’?Look at your way in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18989AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18989AT\"></sup>valley!Know what you have done!You are a swift young camel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18989AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18989AU\"></sup>entangling her ways,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18990AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18990AV\"></sup>wild donkey accustomed to the wilderness,That sniffs the wind in her passion.In <i>the time of</i> her heat who can turn her away?All who seek her will not become weary;In her month they will find her.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Keep your feet from being unshodAnd your throat from thirst;But you said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18991AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18991AW\"></sup>It is hopeless!No! For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18991AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18991AX\"></sup>loved strangers,And after them I will walk.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“As the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18992AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18992AY\"></sup>thief is shamed when he is discovered,So the house of Israel is shamed;They, their kings, their princesAnd their priests and their prophets,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Who say to a tree, ‘You are my father,’And to a stone, ‘You gave me birth.’For they have turned <i>their</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18993AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18993AZ\"></sup>back to Me,And not <i>their</i> face;But in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18993BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18993BA\"></sup>time of their trouble they will say,‘Arise and save us.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But where are your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18994BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18994BB\"></sup>godsWhich you made for yourself?Let them arise, if they can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18994BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18994BC\"></sup>save youIn the time of your trouble;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18994BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18994BD\"></sup><i>according to</i> the number of your citiesAre your gods, O Judah.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Why do you contend with Me?You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18995BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18995BE\"></sup>all transgressed against Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18996BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18996BF\"></sup>In vain I have struck your sons;They accepted no chastening.Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18996BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18996BG\"></sup>sword has devoured your prophetsLike a destroying lion.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“O generation, heed the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Have I been a wilderness to Israel,Or a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18997BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18997BH\"></sup>land of thick darkness?Why do My people say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18997BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18997BI\"></sup>We <i>are free to</i> roam;We will no longer come to You’?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Can a virgin forget her ornaments,Or a bride her attire?Yet My people have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18998BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18998BJ\"></sup>forgotten MeDays without number.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“How well you prepare your wayTo seek love!Therefore even the wicked womenYou have taught your ways.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Also on your skirts is foundThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19000BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19000BK\"></sup>lifeblood of the innocent poor;You did not find them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19000BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19000BL\"></sup>breaking in.But in spite of all these things,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Yet you said, ‘I am innocent;Surely His anger is turned away from me.’Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19001BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19001BM\"></sup>enter into judgment with youBecause you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19001BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19001BN\"></sup>say, ‘I have not sinned.’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19002BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19002BO\"></sup>go around so muchChanging your way?Also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19002BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19002BP\"></sup>you will be put to shame by EgyptAs you were put to shame by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19002BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19002BQ\"></sup>Assyria.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“From this <i>place</i> also you will go outWith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19003BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19003BR\"></sup>your hands on your head;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19003BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19003BS\"></sup>those in whom you trust,And you will not prosper with them.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><i>God</i> says, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19004A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19004A\"></sup>If a husband divorces his wifeAnd she goes from himAnd belongs to another man,Will he still return to her?Will not that land be completely polluted?But you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19004B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19004B\"></sup>are a harlot <i>with</i> many lovers;Yet you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19004C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19004C\"></sup>turn to Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Lift up your eyes to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19005D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19005D\"></sup>bare heights and see;Where have you not been violated?By the roads you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19005E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19005E\"></sup>sat for themLike an Arab in the desert,And you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19005F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19005F\"></sup>polluted a landWith your harlotry and with your wickedness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19006G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19006G\"></sup>showers have been withheld,And there has been no spring rain.Yet you had a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19006H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19006H\"></sup>harlot’s forehead;You refused to be ashamed.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Have you not just now called to Me,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19007I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19007I\"></sup>My Father, You are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19007J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19007J\"></sup>friend of my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19007K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19007K\"></sup>youth?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19008L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19008L\"></sup>Will He be angry forever?Will He be indignant to the end?’Behold, you have spokenAnd have done evil things,And you have had your way.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me in the days of Josiah the king, “Have you seen what faithless Israel did? She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19009M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19009M\"></sup>went up on every high hill and under every green tree, and she was a harlot there.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19010N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19010N\"></sup>I thought, ‘After she has done all these things she will return to Me’; but she did not return, and her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19010O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19010O\"></sup>treacherous sister Judah saw it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I saw that for all the adulteries of faithless Israel, I had sent her away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19011P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19011P\"></sup>given her a writ of divorce, yet her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19011Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19011Q\"></sup>treacherous sister Judah did not fear; but she went and was a harlot also.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Because of the lightness of her harlotry, she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19012R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19012R\"></sup>polluted the land and committed adultery with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19012S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19012S\"></sup>stones and trees.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet in spite of all this her treacherous sister Judah did not return to Me with all her heart, but rather in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19013T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19013T\"></sup>deception,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19014U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19014U\"></sup>Faithless Israel has proved herself more righteous than treacherous Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Go and proclaim these words toward the north and say,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19015V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19015V\"></sup>Return, faithless Israel,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19015W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19015W\"></sup>I will not look upon you in anger.For I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19015X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19015X\"></sup>gracious,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;‘I will not be angry forever.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘Only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19016Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19016Y\"></sup>acknowledge your iniquity,That you have transgressed against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your GodAnd have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19016Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19016Z\"></sup>scattered your favors to the strangers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19016AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19016AA\"></sup>under every green tree,And you have not obeyed My voice,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Return, O faithless sons,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;‘For I am a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19017AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19017AB\"></sup>master to you,And I will take you one from a city and two from a family,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19017AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19017AC\"></sup>I will bring you to Zion.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Then I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19018AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19018AD\"></sup>shepherds after My own heart, who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19018AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19018AE\"></sup>feed you on knowledge and understanding.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It shall be in those days when you are multiplied and increased in the land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19019AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19019AF\"></sup>no longer say, ‘The ark of the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’ And it will not come to mind, nor will they remember it, nor will they miss <i>it</i>, nor will it be made again.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>At that time they will call Jerusalem ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19020AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19020AG\"></sup>Throne of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19020AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19020AH\"></sup>all the nations will be gathered to it, to Jerusalem, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19020AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19020AI\"></sup>name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; nor will they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19020AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19020AJ\"></sup>walk anymore after the stubbornness of their evil heart.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19021AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19021AK\"></sup>In those days the house of Judah will walk with the house of Israel, and they will come together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19021AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19021AL\"></sup>from the land of the north to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19021AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19021AM\"></sup>land that I gave your fathers as an inheritance.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Then I said,‘How I would set you among My sonsAnd give you a pleasant land,The most <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19022AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19022AN\"></sup>beautiful inheritance of the nations!’And I said, ‘You shall call Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19022AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19022AO\"></sup>My Father,And not turn away from following Me.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Surely, as a woman treacherously departs from her lover,So you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19023AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19023AP\"></sup>dealt treacherously with Me,O house of Israel,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A voice is heard on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19024AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19024AQ\"></sup>bare heights,The weeping <i>and</i> the supplications of the sons of Israel;Because they have perverted their way,They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19024AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19024AR\"></sup>forgotten the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Return, O faithless sons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19025AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19025AS\"></sup>I will heal your faithlessness.”“Behold, we come to You;For You are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Surely, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19026AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19026AT\"></sup>the hills are a deception,A tumult <i>on</i> the mountains.Surely in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19026AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19026AU\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our GodIs the salvation of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19027AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19027AV\"></sup>the shameful thing has consumed the labor of our fathers since our youth, their flocks and their herds, their sons and their daughters.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let us lie down in our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19028AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19028AW\"></sup>shame, and let our humiliation cover us; for we have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, we and our fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19028AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19028AX\"></sup>from our youth even to this day. And we have not obeyed the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“If you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19029A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19029A\"></sup>return, O Israel,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<i>Then</i> you should return to Me.And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19029B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19029B\"></sup>if you will put away your detested things from My presence,And will not waver,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19030C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19030C\"></sup>swear, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19030D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19030D\"></sup>In truth, in justice and in righteousness;Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19030E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19030E\"></sup>nations will bless themselves in Him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19030F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19030F\"></sup>in Him they will glory.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to the men of Judah and to Jerusalem,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19031G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19031G\"></sup>Break up your fallow ground,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19031H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19031H\"></sup>do not sow among thorns.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19032I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19032I\"></sup>Circumcise yourselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And remove the foreskins of your heart,Men of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem,Or else My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19032J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19032J\"></sup>wrath will go forth like fireAnd burn with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19032K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19032K\"></sup>none to quench it,Because of the evil of your deeds.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Declare in Judah and proclaim in Jerusalem, and say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19033L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19033L\"></sup>Blow the trumpet in the land;Cry aloud and say,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19033M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19033M\"></sup>Assemble yourselves, and let us goInto the fortified cities.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Lift up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19034N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19034N\"></sup>standard toward Zion!Seek refuge, do not stand <i>still</i>,For I am bringing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19034O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19034O\"></sup>evil from the north,And great destruction.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19035P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19035P\"></sup>lion has gone up from his thicket,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19035Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19035Q\"></sup>destroyer of nations has set out;He has gone out from his placeTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19035R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19035R\"></sup>make your land a waste.Your cities will be ruinsWithout inhabitant.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19036S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19036S\"></sup>put on sackcloth,Lament and wail;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19036T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19036T\"></sup>fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Has not turned back from us.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“It shall come about in that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19037U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19037U\"></sup>heart of the king and the heart of the princes will fail; and the priests will be appalled and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19037V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19037V\"></sup>prophets will be astounded.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I said, “Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Surely You have utterly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19038W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19038W\"></sup>deceived this people and Jerusalem, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19038X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19038X\"></sup>You will have peace’; whereas a sword touches the throat.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In that time it will be said to this people and to Jerusalem, “A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19039Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19039Y\"></sup>scorching wind from the bare heights in the wilderness in the direction of the daughter of My people—not to winnow and not to cleanse,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>a wind too strong for this—will come at My command; now I will also pronounce judgments against them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Behold, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19041Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19041Z\"></sup>goes up like clouds,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19041AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19041AA\"></sup>chariots like the whirlwind;His horses are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19041AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19041AB\"></sup>swifter than eagles.Woe to us, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19041AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19041AC\"></sup>we are ruined!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Wash your heart from evil, O Jerusalem,That you may be saved.How long will your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19042AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19042AD\"></sup>wicked thoughtsLodge within you?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For a voice declares from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19043AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19043AE\"></sup>Dan,And proclaims wickedness from Mount Ephraim.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Report <i>it</i> to the nations, now!Proclaim over Jerusalem,‘Besiegers come from a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19044AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19044AF\"></sup>far country,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19044AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19044AG\"></sup>lift their voices against the cities of Judah.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Like watchmen of a field they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19045AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19045AH\"></sup>against her round about,Because she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19045AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19045AI\"></sup>rebelled against Me,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19046AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19046AJ\"></sup>ways and your deedsHave brought these things to you.This is your evil. How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19046AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19046AK\"></sup>bitter!How it has touched your heart!”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19047AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19047AL\"></sup>My soul, my soul! I am in anguish! Oh, my heart!My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19047AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19047AM\"></sup>heart is pounding in me;I cannot be silent,Because you have heard, O my soul,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19047AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19047AN\"></sup>sound of the trumpet,The alarm of war.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19048AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19048AO\"></sup>Disaster on disaster is proclaimed,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19048AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19048AP\"></sup>whole land is devastated;Suddenly my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19048AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19048AQ\"></sup>tents are devastated,My curtains in an instant.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>How long must I see the standardAnd hear the sound of the trumpet?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19050AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19050AR\"></sup>For My people are foolish,They know Me not;They are stupid childrenAnd have no understanding.They are shrewd to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19050AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19050AS\"></sup>do evil,But to do good they do not know.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I looked on the earth, and behold, <i>it was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19051AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19051AT\"></sup> formless and void;And to the heavens, and they had no light.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I looked on the mountains, and behold, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19052AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19052AU\"></sup>quaking,And all the hills moved to and fro.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I looked, and behold, there was no man,And all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19053AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19053AV\"></sup>birds of the heavens had fled.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I looked, and behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19054AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19054AW\"></sup>fruitful land was a wilderness,And all its cities were pulled downBefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, before His fierce anger.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19055AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19055AX\"></sup>whole land shall be a desolation,Yet I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19055AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19055AY\"></sup>not execute a complete destruction.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“For this the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19056AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19056AZ\"></sup>earth shall mournAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19056BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19056BA\"></sup>heavens above be dark,Because I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19056BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19056BB\"></sup>spoken, I have purposed,And I will not change My mind, nor will I turn from it.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At the sound of the horseman and bowman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19057BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19057BC\"></sup>every city flees;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19057BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19057BD\"></sup>go into the thickets and climb among the rocks;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19057BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19057BE\"></sup>Every city is forsaken,And no man dwells in them.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And you, O desolate one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19058BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19058BF\"></sup>what will you do?Although you dress in scarlet,Although you decorate <i>yourself with</i> ornaments of gold,Although you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19058BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19058BG\"></sup>enlarge your eyes with paint,In vain you make yourself beautiful.<i>Your</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19058BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19058BH\"></sup>lovers despise you;They seek your life.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For I heard a cry as of a woman in labor,The anguish as of one giving birth to her first child,The cry of the daughter of Zion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19059BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19059BI\"></sup>gasping for breath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19059BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19059BJ\"></sup>Stretching out her hands, <i>saying</i>,“Ah, woe is me, for I faint before murderers.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19060A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19060A\"></sup>Roam to and fro through the streets of Jerusalem,And look now and take note.And seek in her open squares,If you can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19060B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19060B\"></sup>find a man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19060C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19060C\"></sup>If there is one who does justice, who seeks truth,Then I will pardon her.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19061D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19061D\"></sup>although they say, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’Surely they swear falsely.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19062E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19062E\"></sup>Your eyes <i>look</i> for truth?You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19062F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19062F\"></sup>smitten them,<i>But</i> they did not weaken;You have consumed them,But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19062G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19062G\"></sup>refused to take correction.They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19062H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19062H\"></sup>made their faces harder than rock;They have refused to repent.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I said, “They are only the poor,They are foolish;For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19063I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19063I\"></sup>do not know the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><i>Or</i> the ordinance of their God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I will go to the greatAnd will speak to them,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19064J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19064J\"></sup>they know the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><i>And</i> the ordinance of their God.”But they too, with one accord, have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19064K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19064K\"></sup>broken the yoke<i>And</i> burst the bonds.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19065L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19065L\"></sup>a lion from the forest will slay them,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19065M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19065M\"></sup>wolf of the deserts will destroy them,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19065N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19065N\"></sup>leopard is watching their cities.Everyone who goes out of them will be torn in pieces,Because their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19065O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19065O\"></sup>transgressions are many,Their apostasies are numerous.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Why should I pardon you?Your sons have forsaken MeAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19066P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19066P\"></sup>sworn by those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19066Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19066Q\"></sup>not gods.When I had fed them to the full,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19066R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19066R\"></sup>committed adulteryAnd trooped to the harlot’s house.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“They were well-fed lusty horses,Each one neighing after his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19067S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19067S\"></sup>neighbor’s wife.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Shall I not punish these <i>people</i>,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And on a nation such as this<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19068T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19068T\"></sup>Shall I not avenge Myself?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Go up through her vine rows and destroy,But do not execute a complete destruction;Strip away her branches,For they are not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19070U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19070U\"></sup>house of Israel and the house of JudahHave dealt very treacherously with Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19071V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19071V\"></sup>lied about the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19071W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19071W\"></sup>Not He;Misfortune will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19071X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19071X\"></sup>not come on us,And we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19071Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19071Y\"></sup>will not see sword or famine.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19072Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19072Z\"></sup>prophets are <i>as</i> wind,And the word is not in them.Thus it will be done to them!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts,“Because you have spoken this word,Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19073AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19073AA\"></sup>making My words in your mouth fireAnd this people wood, and it will consume them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19074AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19074AB\"></sup>bringing a nation against you from afar, O house of Israel,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“It is an enduring nation,It is an ancient nation,A nation whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19074AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19074AC\"></sup>language you do not know,Nor can you understand what they say.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19075AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19075AD\"></sup>quiver is like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19075AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19075AE\"></sup>open grave,All of them are mighty men.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19076AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19076AF\"></sup>devour your harvest and your food;They will devour your sons and your daughters;They will devour your flocks and your herds;They will devour your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19076AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19076AG\"></sup>vines and your fig trees;They will demolish with the sword your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19076AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19076AH\"></sup>fortified cities in which you trust.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Yet even in those days,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I will not make you a complete destruction.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It shall come about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19078AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19078AI\"></sup>when they say, ‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God done all these things to us?’ then you shall say to them, ‘As you have forsaken Me and served foreign gods in your land, so you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19078AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19078AJ\"></sup>serve strangers in a land that is not yours.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Declare this in the house of JacobAnd proclaim it in Judah, saying,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>‘Now hear this, O foolish and senseless people,Who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19080AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19080AK\"></sup>eyes but do not see;Who have ears but do not hear.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>‘Do you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19081AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19081AL\"></sup>fear Me?’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.‘Do you not tremble in My presence?For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19081AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19081AM\"></sup>placed the sand as a boundary for the sea,An eternal decree, so it cannot cross over it.Though the waves toss, yet they cannot prevail;Though they roar, yet they cannot cross over it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>‘But this people has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19082AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19082AN\"></sup>stubborn and rebellious heart;They have turned aside and departed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>‘They do not say in their heart,“Let us now fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19083AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19083AO\"></sup>gives rain in its season,Both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19083AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19083AP\"></sup>the autumn rain and the spring rain,Who keeps for usThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19083AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19083AQ\"></sup>appointed weeks of the harvest.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>‘Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19084AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19084AR\"></sup>iniquities have turned these away,And your sins have withheld good from you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>‘For wicked men are found among My people,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19085AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19085AS\"></sup>watch like fowlers lying in wait;They set a trap,They catch men.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>‘Like a cage full of birds,So their houses are full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19086AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19086AT\"></sup>deceit;Therefore they have become great and rich.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>‘They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19087AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19087AU\"></sup>fat, they are sleek,They also excel in deeds of wickedness;They do not plead the cause,The cause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19087AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19087AV\"></sup>orphan, that they may prosper;And they do not defend the rights of the poor.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19088AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19088AW\"></sup>Shall I not punish these <i>people</i>?’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘On a nation such as thisShall I not avenge Myself?’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“An appalling and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19089AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19089AX\"></sup>horrible thingHas happened in the land:",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19090AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19090AY\"></sup>prophets prophesy falsely,And the priests rule on their <i>own</i> authority;And My people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19090AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19090AZ\"></sup>love it so!But what will you do at the end of it?"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“Flee for safety, O sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19091A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19091A\"></sup>Benjamin,From the midst of Jerusalem!Now blow a trumpet in TekoaAnd raise a signal over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19091B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19091B\"></sup>Beth-haccerem;For evil looks down from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19091C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19091C\"></sup>north,And a great destruction.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“The comely and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19092D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19092D\"></sup>dainty one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19092E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19092E\"></sup>the daughter of Zion, I will cut off.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19093F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19093F\"></sup>Shepherds and their flocks will come to her,They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19093G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19093G\"></sup>pitch <i>their</i> tents around her,They will pasture each in his place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19094H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19094H\"></sup>Prepare war against her;Arise, and let us attack at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19094I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19094I\"></sup>noon.Woe to us, for the day declines,For the shadows of the evening lengthen!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Arise, and let us attack by nightAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19095J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19095J\"></sup>destroy her palaces!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19096K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19096K\"></sup>Cut down her treesAnd cast up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19096L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19096L\"></sup>siege against Jerusalem.This is the city to be punished,In whose midst there is only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19096M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19096M\"></sup>oppression.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19097N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19097N\"></sup>As a well keeps its waters fresh,So she keeps fresh her wickedness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19097O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19097O\"></sup>Violence and destruction are heard in her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19097P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19097P\"></sup>Sickness and wounds are ever before Me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19098Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19098Q\"></sup>Be warned, O Jerusalem,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19098R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19098R\"></sup>I shall be alienated from you,And make you a desolation,A land not inhabited.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19099S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19099S\"></sup>thoroughly glean as the vine the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19099T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19099T\"></sup>remnant of Israel;Pass your hand again like a grape gathererOver the branches.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>To whom shall I speak and give warningThat they may hear?Behold, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19100U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19100U\"></sup>ears are closedAnd they cannot listen.Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19100V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19100V\"></sup>the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has become a reproach to them;They have no delight in it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19101W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19101W\"></sup>full of the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19101X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19101X\"></sup>weary with holding <i>it</i> in.“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19101Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19101Y\"></sup>Pour <i>it</i> out on the children in the streetAnd on the gathering of young men together;For both husband and wife shall be taken,The aged and the very old.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19102Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19102Z\"></sup>houses shall be turned over to others,Their fields and their wives together;For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19102AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19102AA\"></sup>stretch out My handAgainst the inhabitants of the land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19103AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19103AB\"></sup>from the least of them even to the greatest of them,Everyone is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19103AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19103AC\"></sup>greedy for gain,And from the prophet even to the priestEveryone deals falsely.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19104AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19104AD\"></sup>healed the brokenness of My people superficially,Saying, ‘Peace, peace,’But there is no peace.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Were they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19105AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19105AE\"></sup>ashamed because of the abomination they have done?They were not even ashamed at all;They did not even know how to blush.Therefore they shall fall among those who fall;At the time that I punish them,They shall be cast down,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Stand by the ways and see and ask for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19106AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19106AF\"></sup>ancient paths,Where the good way is, and walk in it;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19106AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19106AG\"></sup>you will find rest for your souls.But they said, ‘We will not walk <i>in it</i>.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“And I set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19107AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19107AH\"></sup>watchmen over you, <i>saying</i>,‘Listen to the sound of the trumpet!’But they said, ‘We will not listen.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Therefore hear, O nations,And know, O congregation, what is among them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19109AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19109AI\"></sup>Hear, O earth: behold, I am bringing disaster on this people,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19109AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19109AJ\"></sup>fruit of their plans,Because they have not listened to My words,And as for My law, they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19109AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19109AK\"></sup>rejected it also.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19110AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19110AL\"></sup>For what purpose does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19110AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19110AM\"></sup>frankincense come to Me from ShebaAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19110AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19110AN\"></sup>sweet cane from a distant land?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19110AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19110AO\"></sup>Your burnt offerings are not acceptableAnd your sacrifices are not pleasing to Me.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19111AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19111AP\"></sup>I am laying stumbling blocks before this people.And they will stumble against them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19111AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19111AQ\"></sup>Fathers and sons together;Neighbor and friend will perish.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19112AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19112AR\"></sup>a people is coming from the north land,And a great nation will be aroused from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19112AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19112AS\"></sup>remote parts of the earth.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“They seize <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19113AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19113AT\"></sup>bow and spear;They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19113AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19113AU\"></sup>cruel and have no mercy;Their voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19113AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19113AV\"></sup>roars like the sea,And they ride on horses,Arrayed as a man for the battleAgainst you, O daughter of Zion!”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19114AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19114AW\"></sup>heard the report of it;Our hands are limp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19114AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19114AX\"></sup>Anguish has seized us,Pain as of a woman in childbirth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19115AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19115AY\"></sup>Do not go out into the fieldAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19115AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19115AZ\"></sup>do not walk on the road,For the enemy has a sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19115BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19115BA\"></sup>Terror is on every side.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>O daughter of my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19116BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19116BB\"></sup>put on sackclothAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19116BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19116BC\"></sup>roll in ashes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19116BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19116BD\"></sup>Mourn as for an only son,A lamentation most bitter.For suddenly the destroyerWill come upon us.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19117BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19117BE\"></sup>made you an assayer <i>and</i> a tester among My people,That you may know and assay their way.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>All of them are stubbornly rebellious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19118BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19118BF\"></sup>Going about as a talebearer.<i>They are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19118BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19118BG\"></sup>bronze and iron;They, all of them, are corrupt.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The bellows blow fiercely,The lead is consumed by the fire;In vain the refining goes on,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19119BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19119BH\"></sup>wicked are not separated.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19120BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19120BI\"></sup>They call them rejected silver,Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19120BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19120BJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected them."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19122A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19122A\"></sup>Stand in the gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house and proclaim there this word and say, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you of Judah, who enter by these gates to worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!’”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19123B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19123B\"></sup>Amend your ways and your deeds, and I will let you dwell in this place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19124C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19124C\"></sup>Do not trust in deceptive words, saying, ‘This is the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19125D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19125D\"></sup>if you truly amend your ways and your deeds, if you truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19125E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19125E\"></sup>practice justice between a man and his neighbor,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><i>if</i> you do not oppress the alien, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19126F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19126F\"></sup>orphan, or the widow, and do not shed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19126G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19126G\"></sup>innocent blood in this place, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19126H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19126H\"></sup>walk after other gods to your own ruin,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>then I will let you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19127I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19127I\"></sup>dwell in this place, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19127J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19127J\"></sup>land that I gave to your fathers forever and ever.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Behold, you are trusting in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19128K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19128K\"></sup>deceptive words to no avail.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Will you steal, murder, and commit adultery and swear falsely, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19129L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19129L\"></sup>offer sacrifices to Baal and walk after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19129M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19129M\"></sup>other gods that you have not known,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19130N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19130N\"></sup>come and stand before Me in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19130O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19130O\"></sup>this house, which is called by My name, and say, ‘We are delivered!’—that you may do all these abominations?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19131P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19131P\"></sup>this house, which is called by My name, become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19131Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19131Q\"></sup>den of robbers in your sight? Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19131R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19131R\"></sup>I, even I, have seen <i>it</i>,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But go now to My place which was in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19132S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19132S\"></sup>Shiloh, where I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19132T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19132T\"></sup>made My name dwell at the first, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19132U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19132U\"></sup>see what I did to it because of the wickedness of My people Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And now, because you have done all these things,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and I spoke to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19133V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19133V\"></sup>rising up early and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19133W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19133W\"></sup>speaking, but you did not hear, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19133X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19133X\"></sup>called you but you did not answer,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>therefore, I will do to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19134Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19134Y\"></sup>house which is called by My name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19134Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19134Z\"></sup>in which you trust, and to the place which I gave you and your fathers, as I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19134AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19134AA\"></sup>did to Shiloh.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19135AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19135AB\"></sup>cast you out of My sight, as I have cast out all your brothers, all the offspring of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19135AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19135AC\"></sup>Ephraim.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“As for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19136AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19136AD\"></sup>do not pray for this people, and do not lift up cry or prayer for them, and do not intercede with Me; for I do not hear you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do you not see what they are doing in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The children gather wood, and the fathers kindle the fire, and the women knead dough to make cakes for the queen of heaven; and <i>they</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19138AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19138AE\"></sup>pour out drink offerings to other gods in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19138AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19138AF\"></sup>spite Me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19139AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19139AG\"></sup>Do they spite Me?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “Is it not themselves <i>they spite</i>, to their own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19139AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19139AH\"></sup>shame?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19140AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19140AI\"></sup>anger and My wrath will be poured out on this place, on man and on beast and on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19140AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19140AJ\"></sup>trees of the field and on the fruit of the ground; and it will burn and not be quenched.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Add your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19141AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19141AK\"></sup>burnt offerings to your sacrifices and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19141AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19141AL\"></sup>eat flesh.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For I did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19142AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19142AM\"></sup>speak to your fathers, or command them in the day that I brought them out of the land of Egypt, concerning burnt offerings and sacrifices.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But this is what I commanded them, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19143AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19143AN\"></sup>Obey My voice, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19143AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19143AO\"></sup>I will be your God, and you will be My people; and you will walk in all the way which I command you, that it may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19143AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19143AP\"></sup>be well with you.’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Yet they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19144AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19144AQ\"></sup>did not obey or incline their ear, but walked in <i>their own</i> counsels <i>and</i> in the stubbornness of their evil heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19144AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19144AR\"></sup>went backward and not forward.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Since the day that your fathers came out of the land of Egypt until this day, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19145AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19145AS\"></sup>sent you all My servants the prophets, daily rising early and sending <i>them</i>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Yet they did not listen to Me or incline their ear, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19146AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19146AT\"></sup>stiffened their neck; they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19146AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19146AU\"></sup>did more evil than their fathers.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“You shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19147AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19147AV\"></sup>speak all these words to them, but they will not listen to you; and you shall call to them, but they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19147AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19147AW\"></sup>not answer you.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You shall say to them, ‘This is the nation that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19148AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19148AX\"></sup>did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God or accept correction; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19148AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19148AY\"></sup>truth has perished and has been cut off from their mouth.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19149AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19149AZ\"></sup>Cut off your hair and cast <i>it</i> away,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19149BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19149BA\"></sup>take up a lamentation on the bare heights;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19149BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19149BB\"></sup>rejected and forsakenThe generation of His wrath.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For the sons of Judah have done that which is evil in My sight,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19150BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19150BC\"></sup>set their detestable things in the house which is called by My name, to defile it.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19151BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19151BD\"></sup>built the high places of Topheth, which is in the valley of the son of Hinnom, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19151BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19151BE\"></sup>burn their sons and their daughters in the fire, which I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19151BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19151BF\"></sup>did not command, and it did not come into My mind.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19152BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19152BG\"></sup>Therefore, behold, days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when it will no longer be called Topheth, or the valley of the son of Hinnom, but the valley of the Slaughter; for they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19152BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19152BH\"></sup>bury in Topheth because there is no <i>other</i> place.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19153BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19153BI\"></sup>dead bodies of this people will be food for the birds of the sky and for the beasts of the earth; and no one will frighten <i>them away</i>.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Then I will make to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19154BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19154BJ\"></sup>cease from the cities of Judah and from the streets of Jerusalem the voice of joy and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride; for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19154BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19154BK\"></sup>land will become a ruin."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>“At that time,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19155A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19155A\"></sup>bring out the bones of the kings of Judah and the bones of its princes, and the bones of the priests and the bones of the prophets, and the bones of the inhabitants of Jerusalem from their graves.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They will spread them out to the sun, the moon and to all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19156B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19156B\"></sup>host of heaven, which they have loved and which they have served, and which they have gone after and which they have sought, and which they have worshiped. They will not be gathered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19156C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19156C\"></sup>or buried; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19156D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19156D\"></sup>they will be as dung on the face of the ground.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19157E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19157E\"></sup>death will be chosen rather than life by all the remnant that remains of this evil family, that remains in all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19157F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19157F\"></sup>places to which I have driven them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“You shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Do <i>men</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19158G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19158G\"></sup>fall and not get up again?Does one turn away and not repent?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Why then has this people, Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19159H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19159H\"></sup>Turned away in continual apostasy?They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19159I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19159I\"></sup>hold fast to deceit,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19159J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19159J\"></sup>refuse to return.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19160K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19160K\"></sup>have listened and heard,They have spoken what is not right;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19160L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19160L\"></sup>No man repented of his wickedness,Saying, ‘What have I done?’Everyone turned to his course,Like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19160M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19160M\"></sup>horse charging into the battle.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Even the stork in the sky<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19161N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19161N\"></sup>Knows her seasons;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19161O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19161O\"></sup>turtledove and the swift and the thrushObserve the time of their migration;But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19161P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19161P\"></sup>My people do not knowThe ordinance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19162Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19162Q\"></sup>How can you say, ‘We are wise,And the law of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with us’?But behold, the lying pen of the scribesHas made <i>it</i> into a lie.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The wise men are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19163R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19163R\"></sup>put to shame,They are dismayed and caught;Behold, they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19163S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19163S\"></sup>rejected the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And what kind of wisdom do they have?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Therefore I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19164T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19164T\"></sup>give their wives to others,Their fields to new owners;Because from the least even to the greatestEveryone is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19164U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19164U\"></sup>greedy for gain;From the prophet even to the priestEveryone practices deceit.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19165V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19165V\"></sup>heal the brokenness of the daughter of My people superficially,Saying, ‘Peace, peace,’But there is no peace.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Were they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19166W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19166W\"></sup>ashamed because of the abomination they had done?They certainly were not ashamed,And they did not know how to blush;Therefore they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19166X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19166X\"></sup>fall among those who fall;At the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19166Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19166Y\"></sup>time of their punishment they shall be brought down,”Says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19167Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19167Z\"></sup>surely snatch them away,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;“There will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19167AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19167AA\"></sup>no grapes on the vineAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19167AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19167AB\"></sup>no figs on the fig tree,And the leaf will wither;And what I have given them will pass away.”’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Why are we sitting still?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19168AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19168AC\"></sup>Assemble yourselves, and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19168AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19168AD\"></sup>go into the fortified citiesAnd let us perish there,Because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has doomed usAnd given us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19168AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19168AE\"></sup>poisoned water to drink,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19168AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19168AF\"></sup>we have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><i>We</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19169AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19169AG\"></sup>waited for peace, but no good <i>came</i>;For a time of healing, but behold, terror!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19170AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19170AH\"></sup>Dan is heard the snorting of his horses;At the sound of the neighing of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19170AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19170AI\"></sup>stallionsThe whole land quakes;For they come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19170AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19170AJ\"></sup>devour the land and its fullness,The city and its inhabitants.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19171AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19171AK\"></sup>sending serpents against you,Adders, for which there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19171AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19171AL\"></sup>no charm,And they will bite you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19172AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19172AM\"></sup>sorrow is beyond healing,My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19172AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19172AN\"></sup>heart is faint <i>within me</i>!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Behold, listen! The cry of the daughter of my people from a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19173AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19173AO\"></sup>distant land:“Is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> not in Zion? Is her King not within her?”“Why have they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19173AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19173AP\"></sup>provoked Me with their graven images, with foreign <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19173AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19173AQ\"></sup>idols?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Harvest is past, summer is ended,And we are not saved.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19175AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19175AR\"></sup>brokenness of the daughter of my people I am broken;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19175AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19175AS\"></sup>mourn, dismay has taken hold of me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Is there no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19176AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19176AT\"></sup>balm in Gilead?Is there no physician there?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19176AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19176AU\"></sup>Why then has not the health of the daughter of my people been restored?"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19177A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19177A\"></sup>Oh that my head were watersAnd my eyes a fountain of tears,That I might weep day and nightFor the slain of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19177B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19177B\"></sup>daughter of my people!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19178C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19178C\"></sup>Oh that I had in the desertA wayfarers’ lodging place;That I might leave my peopleAnd go from them!For all of them are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19178D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19178D\"></sup>adulterers,An assembly of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19178E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19178E\"></sup>treacherous men.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19179F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19179F\"></sup>bend their tongue <i>like</i> their bow;Lies and not truth prevail in the land;For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19179G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19179G\"></sup>proceed from evil to evil,And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19179H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19179H\"></sup>do not know Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Let everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19180I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19180I\"></sup>be on guard against his neighbor,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19180J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19180J\"></sup>do not trust any brother;Because every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19180K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19180K\"></sup>brother deals craftily,And every neighbor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19180L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19180L\"></sup>goes about as a slanderer.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19181M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19181M\"></sup>deceives his neighborAnd does not speak the truth,They have taught their tongue to speak lies;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19181N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19181N\"></sup>weary themselves committing iniquity.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19182O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19182O\"></sup>dwelling is in the midst of deceit;Through deceit they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19182P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19182P\"></sup>refuse to know Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“Behold, I will refine them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19183Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19183Q\"></sup>assay them;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19183R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19183R\"></sup>what <i>else</i> can I do, because of the daughter of My people?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19184S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19184S\"></sup>tongue is a deadly arrow;It speaks deceit;With his mouth one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19184T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19184T\"></sup>speaks peace to his neighbor,But inwardly he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19184U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19184U\"></sup>sets an ambush for him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19185V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19185V\"></sup>Shall I not punish them for these things?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“On a nation such as thisShall I not avenge Myself?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19186W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19186W\"></sup>mountains I will take up a weeping and wailing,And for the pastures of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19186X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19186X\"></sup>wilderness a dirge,Because they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19186Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19186Y\"></sup>laid waste so that no one passes through,And the lowing of the cattle is not heard;Both the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19186Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19186Z\"></sup>birds of the sky and the beasts have fled; they are gone.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will make Jerusalem a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19187AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19187AA\"></sup>heap of ruins,A haunt of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19187AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19187AB\"></sup>jackals;And I will make the cities of Judah a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19187AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19187AC\"></sup>desolation, without inhabitant.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Who is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19188AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19188AD\"></sup>wise man that may understand this? And <i>who is</i> he to whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19188AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19188AE\"></sup>the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken, that he may declare it? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19188AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19188AF\"></sup>Why is the land ruined, laid waste like a desert, so that no one passes through?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19189AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19189AG\"></sup>forsaken My law which I set before them, and have not obeyed My voice nor walked according to it,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19190AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19190AH\"></sup>walked after the stubbornness of their heart and after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19190AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19190AI\"></sup>Baals, as their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19190AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19190AJ\"></sup>fathers taught them,”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19191AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19191AK\"></sup>I will feed them, this people, with wormwood and give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19191AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19191AL\"></sup>poisoned water to drink.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19192AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19192AM\"></sup>scatter them among the nations, whom neither they nor their fathers have known; and I will send the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19192AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19192AN\"></sup>sword after them until I have annihilated them.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“Consider and call for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19193AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19193AO\"></sup>mourning women, that they may come;And send for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19193AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19193AP\"></sup>wailing women, that they may come!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Let them make haste and take up a wailing for us,That our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19194AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19194AQ\"></sup>eyes may shed tearsAnd our eyelids flow with water.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“For a voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19195AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19195AR\"></sup>wailing is heard from Zion,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19195AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19195AS\"></sup>How are we ruined!We are put to great shame,For we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19195AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19195AT\"></sup>left the land,Because they have cast down our dwellings.’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19196AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19196AU\"></sup>women,And let your ear receive the word of His mouth;Teach your daughters wailing,And everyone her neighbor a dirge.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19197AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19197AV\"></sup>death has come up through our windows;It has entered our palacesTo cut off the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19197AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19197AW\"></sup>children from the streets,The young men from the town squares.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Speak, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘The corpses of men will fall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19198AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19198AX\"></sup>like dung on the open field,And like the sheaf after the reaper,But no one will gather <i>them</i>.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19199AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19199AY\"></sup>Let not a wise man boast of his wisdom, and let not the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19199AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19199AZ\"></sup>mighty man boast of his might, let not a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19199BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19199BA\"></sup>rich man boast of his riches;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but let him who boasts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19200BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19200BB\"></sup>boast of this, that he understands and knows Me, that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19200BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19200BC\"></sup>exercises lovingkindness, justice and righteousness on earth; for I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19200BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19200BD\"></sup>delight in these things,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Behold, the days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “that I will punish all who are circumcised and yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19201BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19201BE\"></sup>uncircumcised—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Egypt and Judah, and Edom and the sons of Ammon, and Moab and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19202BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19202BF\"></sup>all those inhabiting the desert who clip the hair on their temples; for all the nations are uncircumcised, and all the house of Israel are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19202BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19202BG\"></sup>uncircumcised of heart.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Hear the word which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> speaks to you, O house of Israel.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19204A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19204A\"></sup>Do not learn the way of the nations,And do not be terrified by the signs of the heavensAlthough the nations are terrified by them;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the customs of the peoples are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19205B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19205B\"></sup>delusion;Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19205C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19205C\"></sup>it is wood cut from the forest,The work of the hands of a craftsman with a cutting tool.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19206D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19206D\"></sup>decorate <i>it</i> with silver and with gold;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19206E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19206E\"></sup>fasten it with nails and with hammersSo that it will not totter.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Like a scarecrow in a cucumber field are they,And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19207F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19207F\"></sup>cannot speak;They must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19207G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19207G\"></sup>carried,Because they cannot walk!Do not fear them,For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19207H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19207H\"></sup>can do no harm,Nor can they do any good.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19208I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19208I\"></sup>There is none like You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19208J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19208J\"></sup>great, and great is Your name in might.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19209K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19209K\"></sup>Who would not fear You, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19209L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19209L\"></sup>King of the nations?Indeed it is Your due!For among all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19209M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19209M\"></sup>wise men of the nationsAnd in all their kingdoms,There is none like You.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But they are altogether <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19210N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19210N\"></sup>stupid and foolish<i>In their</i> discipline of delusion—their idol is wood!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Beaten <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19211O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19211O\"></sup>silver is brought from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19211P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19211P\"></sup>Tarshish,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19211Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19211Q\"></sup>gold from Uphaz,The work of a craftsman and of the hands of a goldsmith;Violet and purple are their clothing;They are all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19211R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19211R\"></sup>work of skilled men.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19212S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19212S\"></sup>true God;He is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19212T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19212T\"></sup>living God and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19212U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19212U\"></sup>everlasting King.At His wrath the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19212V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19212V\"></sup>earth quakes,And the nations cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19212W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19212W\"></sup>endure His indignation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus you shall say to them, “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19213X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19213X\"></sup>gods that did not make the heavens and the earth will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19213Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19213Y\"></sup>perish from the earth and from under the heavens.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><i>It is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19214Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19214Z\"></sup>He who made the earth by His power,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19214AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19214AA\"></sup>established the world by His wisdom;And by His understanding He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19214AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19214AB\"></sup>stretched out the heavens.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When He utters His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19215AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19215AC\"></sup>voice, <i>there is</i> a tumult of waters in the heavens,And He causes the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19215AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19215AD\"></sup>clouds to ascend from the end of the earth;He makes lightning for the rain,And brings out the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19215AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19215AE\"></sup>wind from His storehouses.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Every man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19216AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19216AF\"></sup>stupid, devoid of knowledge;Every goldsmith is put to shame by his idols;For his molten images are deceitful,And there is no breath in them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19217AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19217AG\"></sup>worthless, a work of mockery;In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19217AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19217AH\"></sup>time of their punishment they will perish.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19218AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19218AI\"></sup>portion of Jacob is not like these;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19218AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19218AJ\"></sup>Maker of all is He,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19218AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19218AK\"></sup>Israel is the tribe of His inheritance;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19218AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19218AL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19219AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19219AM\"></sup>Pick up your bundle from the ground,You who dwell under siege!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19220AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19220AN\"></sup>slinging out the inhabitants of the landAt this time,And will cause them distress,That they may be found.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19221AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19221AO\"></sup>Woe is me, because of my injury!My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19221AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19221AP\"></sup>wound is incurable.But I said, “Truly this is a sickness,And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19221AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19221AQ\"></sup>must bear it.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19222AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19222AR\"></sup>tent is destroyed,And all my ropes are broken;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19222AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19222AS\"></sup>sons have gone from me and are no more.There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19222AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19222AT\"></sup>no one to stretch out my tent againOr to set up my curtains.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the shepherds have become stupidAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19223AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19223AU\"></sup>have not sought the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;Therefore they have not prospered,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19223AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19223AV\"></sup>all their flock is scattered.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The sound of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19224AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19224AW\"></sup>report! Behold, it comes—A great commotion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19224AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19224AX\"></sup>out of the land of the north—To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19224AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19224AY\"></sup>make the cities of JudahA desolation, a haunt of jackals.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I know, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19225AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19225AZ\"></sup>a man’s way is not in himself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19225BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19225BA\"></sup>Nor is it in a man who walks to direct his steps.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19226BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19226BB\"></sup>Correct me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, but with justice;Not with Your anger, or You will bring me to nothing.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19227BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19227BC\"></sup>Pour out Your wrath on the nations that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19227BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19227BD\"></sup>do not know YouAnd on the families that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19227BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19227BE\"></sup>do not call Your name;For they have devoured Jacob;They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19227BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19227BF\"></sup>devoured him and consumed himAnd have laid waste his habitation."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19229A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19229A\"></sup>Hear the words of this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19229B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19229B\"></sup>covenant, and speak to the men of Judah and to the inhabitants of Jerusalem;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19230C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19230C\"></sup>Cursed is the man who does not heed the words of this covenant",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>which I commanded your forefathers in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19231D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19231D\"></sup>day that I brought them out of the land of Egypt, from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19231E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19231E\"></sup>iron furnace, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19231F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19231F\"></sup>Listen to My voice, and do according to all which I command you; so you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19231G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19231G\"></sup>My people, and I will be your God,’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>in order to confirm the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19232H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19232H\"></sup>oath which I swore to your forefathers, to give them a land flowing with milk and honey, as <i>it is</i> this day.”’” Then I said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19232I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19232I\"></sup>Amen, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19233J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19233J\"></sup>Proclaim all these words in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19233K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19233K\"></sup>Hear the words of this covenant and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19233L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19233L\"></sup>do them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For I solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19234M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19234M\"></sup>warned your fathers in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19234N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19234N\"></sup>day that I brought them up from the land of Egypt, even to this day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19234O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19234O\"></sup>warning persistently, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19234P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19234P\"></sup>Listen to My voice.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Yet they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19235Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19235Q\"></sup>did not obey or incline their ear, but walked, each one, in the stubbornness of his evil heart; therefore I brought on them all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19235R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19235R\"></sup>words of this covenant, which I commanded <i>them</i> to do, but they did not.’”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19236S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19236S\"></sup>conspiracy has been found among the men of Judah and among the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19237T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19237T\"></sup>turned back to the iniquities of their ancestors who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19237U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19237U\"></sup>refused to hear My words, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19237V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19237V\"></sup>have gone after other gods to serve them; the house of Israel and the house of Judah have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19237W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19237W\"></sup>broken My covenant which I made with their fathers.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19238X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19238X\"></sup>bringing disaster on them which they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19238Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19238Y\"></sup>not be able to escape; though they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19238Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19238Z\"></sup>cry to Me, yet I will not listen to them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the cities of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19239AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19239AA\"></sup>go and cry to the gods to whom they burn incense, but they surely will not save them in the time of their disaster.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For your gods are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19240AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19240AB\"></sup>as many as your cities, O Judah; and as many as the streets of Jerusalem are the altars you have set up to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19240AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19240AC\"></sup>shameful thing, altars to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19240AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19240AD\"></sup>burn incense to Baal.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19241AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19241AE\"></sup>do not pray for this people, nor lift up a cry or prayer for them; for I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19241AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19241AF\"></sup>not listen when they call to Me because of their disaster.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“What right has My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19242AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19242AG\"></sup>beloved in My houseWhen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19242AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19242AH\"></sup>she has done many vile deeds?Can the sacrificial flesh take away from you your disaster,So <i>that</i> you can rejoice?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> called your name,“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19243AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19243AI\"></sup>green olive tree, beautiful in fruit and form”;With the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19243AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19243AJ\"></sup>noise of a great tumultHe has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19243AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19243AK\"></sup>kindled fire on it,And its branches are worthless.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19244AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19244AL\"></sup>planted you, has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19244AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19244AM\"></sup>pronounced evil against you because of the evil of the house of Israel and of the house of Judah, which they have done to provoke Me by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19244AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19244AN\"></sup>offering up sacrifices to Baal.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Moreover, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19245AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19245AO\"></sup>made it known to me and I knew it;Then You showed me their deeds.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But I was like a gentle <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19246AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19246AP\"></sup>lamb led to the slaughter;And I did not know that they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19246AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19246AQ\"></sup>devised plots against me, <i>saying</i>,“Let us destroy the tree with its fruit,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19246AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19246AR\"></sup>let us cut him off from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19246AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19246AS\"></sup>land of the living,That his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19246AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19246AT\"></sup>name be remembered no more.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19247AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19247AU\"></sup>judges righteously,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19247AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19247AV\"></sup>tries the feelings and the heart,Let me see Your vengeance on them,For to You have I committed my cause.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19248AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19248AW\"></sup>Anathoth, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19248AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19248AX\"></sup>seek your life, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19248AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19248AY\"></sup>Do not prophesy in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, so that you will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19248AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19248AZ\"></sup>die at our hand”;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “Behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19249BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19249BA\"></sup>punish them! The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19249BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19249BB\"></sup>young men will die by the sword, their sons and daughters will die by famine;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and a remnant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19250BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19250BC\"></sup>will not be left to them, for I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19250BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19250BD\"></sup>bring disaster on the men of Anathoth—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19250BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19250BE\"></sup>the year of their punishment.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19251A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19251A\"></sup>Righteous are You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that I would plead <i>my</i> case with You;Indeed I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19251B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19251B\"></sup>discuss matters of justice with You:Why has the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19251C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19251C\"></sup>way of the wicked prospered?<i>Why</i> are all those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19251D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19251D\"></sup>deal in treachery at ease?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19252E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19252E\"></sup>planted them, they have also taken root;They grow, they have even produced fruit.You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19252F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19252F\"></sup>near to their lipsBut far from their mind.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19253G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19253G\"></sup>know me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;You see me;And You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19253H\"></sup>examine my heart’s <i>attitude</i> toward You.Drag them off like sheep for the slaughterAnd set them apart for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19253I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19253I\"></sup>day of carnage!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>How long is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19254J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19254J\"></sup>land to mournAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19254K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19254K\"></sup>vegetation of the countryside to wither?For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19254L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19254L\"></sup>wickedness of those who dwell in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19254M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19254M\"></sup>Animals and birds have been snatched away,Because <i>men</i> have said, “He will not see our latter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19254N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19254N\"></sup>ending.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If you have run with footmen and they have tired you out,Then how can you compete with horses?If you fall down in a land of peace,How will you do in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19255O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19255O\"></sup>thicket of the Jordan?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For even your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19256P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19256P\"></sup>brothers and the household of your father,Even they have dealt treacherously with you,Even they have cried aloud after you.Do not believe them, although they may say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19256Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19256Q\"></sup>nice things to you.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19257R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19257R\"></sup>forsaken My house,I have abandoned My inheritance;I have given the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19257S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19257S\"></sup>beloved of My soulInto the hand of her enemies.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“My inheritance has become to MeLike a lion in the forest;She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19258T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19258T\"></sup>roared against Me;Therefore I have come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19258U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19258U\"></sup>hate her.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Is My inheritance like a speckled bird of prey to Me?Are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19259V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19259V\"></sup>birds of prey against her on every side?Go, gather all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19259W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19259W\"></sup>beasts of the field,Bring them to devour!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19260X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19260X\"></sup>shepherds have ruined My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19260Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19260Y\"></sup>vineyard,They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19260Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19260Z\"></sup>trampled down My field;They have made My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19260AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19260AA\"></sup>pleasant fieldA desolate wilderness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“It has been made a desolation,Desolate, it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19261AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19261AB\"></sup>mourns before Me;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19261AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19261AC\"></sup>whole land has been made desolate,Because no man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19261AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19261AD\"></sup>lays it to heart.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“On all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19262AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19262AE\"></sup>bare heights in the wildernessDestroyers have come,For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19262AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19262AF\"></sup>sword of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is devouringFrom one end of the land even to the other;There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19262AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19262AG\"></sup>no peace for anyone.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19263AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19263AH\"></sup>sown wheat and have reaped thorns,They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19263AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19263AI\"></sup>strained themselves to no profit.But be ashamed of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19263AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19263AJ\"></sup>harvestBecause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19263AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19263AK\"></sup>fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning all My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19264AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19264AL\"></sup>wicked neighbors who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19264AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19264AM\"></sup>strike at the inheritance with which I have endowed My people Israel, “Behold I am about to uproot them from their land and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19264AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19264AN\"></sup>uproot the house of Judah from among them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And it will come about that after I have uprooted them, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19265AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19265AO\"></sup>again have compassion on them; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19265AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19265AP\"></sup>bring them back, each one to his inheritance and each one to his land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then if they will really <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19266AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19266AQ\"></sup>learn the ways of My people, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19266AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19266AR\"></sup>swear by My name, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’ even as they taught My people to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19266AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19266AS\"></sup>swear by Baal, they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19266AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19266AT\"></sup>built up in the midst of My people.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if they will not listen, then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19267AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19267AU\"></sup>uproot that nation, uproot and destroy it,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19268A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19268A\"></sup>buy yourself a linen waistband and put it around your waist, but do not put it in water.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I bought the waistband in accordance with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19269B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19269B\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and put it around my waist.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me a second time, saying,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Take the waistband that you have bought, which is around your waist, and arise, go to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19271C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19271C\"></sup>Euphrates and hide it there in a crevice of the rock.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So I went and hid it by the Euphrates, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19272D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19272D\"></sup>as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>After many days the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Arise, go to the Euphrates and take from there the waistband which I commanded you to hide there.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then I went to the Euphrates and dug, and I took the waistband from the place where I had hidden it; and lo, the waistband was ruined, it was totally worthless.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Just so will I destroy the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19276E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19276E\"></sup>pride of Judah and the great pride of Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This wicked people, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19277F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19277F\"></sup>refuse to listen to My words, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19277G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19277G\"></sup>walk in the stubbornness of their hearts and have gone after other gods to serve them and to bow down to them, let them be just like this waistband which is totally worthless.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For as the waistband clings to the waist of a man, so I made the whole household of Israel and the whole household of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19278H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19278H\"></sup>cling to Me,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘that they might be for Me a people, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19278I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19278I\"></sup>renown, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19278J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19278J\"></sup>praise and for glory; but they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19278K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19278K\"></sup>did not listen.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore you are to speak this word to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, “Every jug is to be filled with wine.”’ And when they say to you, ‘Do we not very well know that every jug is to be filled with wine?’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>then say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold I am about to fill all the inhabitants of this land—the kings that sit for David on his throne, the priests, the prophets and all the inhabitants of Jerusalem—with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19280L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19280L\"></sup>drunkenness!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19281M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19281M\"></sup>dash them against each other, both the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19281N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19281N\"></sup>fathers and the sons together,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19281O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19281O\"></sup>not show pity nor be sorry nor have compassion so as not to destroy them.”’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Listen and give heed, do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19282P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19282P\"></sup>haughty,For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19283Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19283Q\"></sup>Give glory to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,Before He brings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19283R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19283R\"></sup>darknessAnd before your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19283S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19283S\"></sup>feet stumbleOn the dusky mountains,And while you are hoping for lightHe makes it into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19283T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19283T\"></sup>deep darkness,<i>And</i> turns <i>it</i> into gloom.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19284U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19284U\"></sup>if you will not listen to it,My soul will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19284V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19284V\"></sup>sob in secret for <i>such</i> pride;And my eyes will bitterly weepAnd flow down with tears,Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19284W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19284W\"></sup>flock of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has been taken captive.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19285X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19285X\"></sup>king and the queen mother,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19285Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19285Y\"></sup>Take a lowly seat,For your beautiful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19285Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19285Z\"></sup>crownHas come down from your head.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19286AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19286AA\"></sup>cities of the Negev have been locked up,And there is no one to open <i>them</i>;All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19286AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19286AB\"></sup>Judah has been carried into exile,Wholly carried into exile.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Lift up your eyes and seeThose coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19287AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19287AC\"></sup>from the north.Where is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19287AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19287AD\"></sup>flock that was given you,Your beautiful sheep?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“What will you say when He appoints over you—And you yourself had taught them—Former <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19288AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19288AE\"></sup>companions to be head over you?Will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19288AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19288AF\"></sup>pangs take hold of youLike a woman in childbirth?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19289AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19289AG\"></sup>say in your heart,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19289AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19289AH\"></sup>Why have these things happened to me?’Because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19289AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19289AI\"></sup>magnitude of your iniquity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19289AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19289AJ\"></sup>Your skirts have been removedAnd your heels have been exposed.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19290AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19290AK\"></sup>Can the Ethiopian change his skinOr the leopard his spots?<i>Then</i> you also can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19290AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19290AL\"></sup>do goodWho are accustomed to doing evil.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Therefore I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19291AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19291AM\"></sup>scatter them like drifting strawTo the desert <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19291AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19291AN\"></sup>wind.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“This is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19292AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19292AO\"></sup>lot, the portion measured to youFrom Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19292AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19292AP\"></sup>forgotten MeAnd trusted in falsehood.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“So I Myself have also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19293AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19293AQ\"></sup>stripped your skirts off over your face,That your shame may be seen.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“As for your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19294AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19294AR\"></sup>adulteries and your <i>lustful</i> neighings,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19294AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19294AS\"></sup>lewdness of your prostitutionOn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19294AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19294AT\"></sup>hills in the field,I have seen your abominations.Woe to you, O Jerusalem!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19294AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19294AU\"></sup>How long will you remain unclean?”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>That which came as the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Jeremiah in regard to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19295A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19295A\"></sup>drought:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Judah mournsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19296B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19296B\"></sup>her gates languish;They sit on the ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19296C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19296C\"></sup>in mourning,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19296D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19296D\"></sup>cry of Jerusalem has ascended.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Their nobles have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19297E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19297E\"></sup>sent their servants for water;They have come to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19297F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19297F\"></sup>cisterns and found no water.They have returned with their vessels empty;They have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19297G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19297G\"></sup>put to shame and humiliated,And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19297H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19297H\"></sup>cover their heads.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19298I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19298I\"></sup>ground is cracked,For there has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19298J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19298J\"></sup>no rain on the land;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19298K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19298K\"></sup>farmers have been put to shame,They have covered their heads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For even the doe in the field has given birth only to abandon <i>her young</i>,Because there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19299L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19299L\"></sup>no grass.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19300M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19300M\"></sup>wild donkeys stand on the bare heights;They pant for air like jackals,Their eyes failFor there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19300N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19300N\"></sup>no vegetation.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Although our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19301O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19301O\"></sup>iniquities testify against us,O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, act <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19301P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19301P\"></sup>for Your name’s sake!Truly our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19301Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19301Q\"></sup>apostasies have been many,We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19301R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19301R\"></sup>sinned against You.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19302S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19302S\"></sup>Hope of Israel,Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19302T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19302T\"></sup>Savior in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19302U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19302U\"></sup>time of distress,Why are You like a stranger in the landOr like a traveler who has pitched his <i>tent</i> for the night?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Why are You like a man dismayed,Like a mighty man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19303V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19303V\"></sup>cannot save?Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19303W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19303W\"></sup>You are in our midst, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19303X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19303X\"></sup>called by Your name;Do not forsake us!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to this people, “Even so they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19304Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19304Y\"></sup>loved to wander; they have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19304Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19304Z\"></sup>kept their feet in check. Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19304AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19304AA\"></sup>not accept them; now He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19304AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19304AB\"></sup>remember their iniquity and call their sins to account.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19305AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19305AC\"></sup>Do not pray for the welfare of this people.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When they fast, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19306AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19306AD\"></sup>not going to listen to their cry; and when they offer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19306AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19306AE\"></sup>burnt offering and grain offering, I am not going to accept them. Rather I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19306AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19306AF\"></sup>make an end of them by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19306AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19306AG\"></sup>sword, famine and pestilence.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But, “Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>!” I said, “Look, the prophets are telling them, ‘You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19307AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19307AH\"></sup>will not see the sword nor will you have famine, but I will give you lasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19307AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19307AI\"></sup>peace in this place.’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19308AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19308AJ\"></sup>prophets are prophesying falsehood in My name. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19308AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19308AK\"></sup>I have neither sent them nor commanded them nor spoken to them; they are prophesying to you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19308AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19308AL\"></sup>false vision, divination, futility and the deception of their own minds.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the prophets who are prophesying in My name, although it was not I who sent them—yet they keep saying, ‘There will be no sword or famine in this land’—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19309AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19309AM\"></sup>by sword and famine those prophets shall meet their end!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The people also to whom they are prophesying will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19310AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19310AN\"></sup>thrown out into the streets of Jerusalem because of the famine and the sword; and there will be no one to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19310AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19310AO\"></sup>bury them—<i>neither</i> them, <i>nor</i> their wives, nor their sons, nor their daughters—for I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19310AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19310AP\"></sup>pour out their <i>own</i> wickedness on them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“You will say this word to them,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19311AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19311AQ\"></sup>Let my eyes flow down with tears night and day,And let them not cease;For the virgin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19311AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19311AR\"></sup>daughter of my people has been crushed with a mighty blow,With a sorely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19311AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19311AS\"></sup>infected wound.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>‘If I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19312AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19312AT\"></sup>go out to the country,Behold, those slain with the sword!Or if I enter the city,Behold, diseases of famine!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19312AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19312AU\"></sup>both prophet and priestHave gone roving about in the land that they do not know.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Have You completely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19313AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19313AV\"></sup>rejected Judah?Or have You loathed Zion?Why have You stricken us so that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19313AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19313AW\"></sup>are beyond healing?<i>We</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19313AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19313AX\"></sup>waited for peace, but nothing good <i>came</i>;And for a time of healing, but behold, terror!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19314AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19314AY\"></sup>know our wickedness, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,The iniquity of our fathers, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19314AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19314AZ\"></sup>we have sinned against You.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not despise <i>us</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19315BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19315BA\"></sup>for Your own name’s sake;Do not disgrace the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19315BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19315BB\"></sup>throne of Your glory;Remember <i>and</i> do not annul Your covenant with us.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Are there any among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19316BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19316BC\"></sup>idols of the nations who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19316BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19316BD\"></sup>give rain?Or can the heavens grant showers?Is it not You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God?Therefore we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19316BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19316BE\"></sup>hope in You,For You are the one who has done all these things."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19317A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19317A\"></sup>though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19317B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19317B\"></sup>Moses and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19317C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19317C\"></sup>Samuel were to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19317D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19317D\"></sup>stand before Me, My heart would not be with this people; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19317E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19317E\"></sup>send them away from My presence and let them go!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And it shall be that when they say to you, ‘Where should we go?’ then you are to tell them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Those <i>destined</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19318F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19318F\"></sup>for death, to death;And those <i>destined</i> for the sword, to the sword;And those <i>destined</i> for famine, to famine;And those <i>destined</i> for captivity, to captivity.”’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19319G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19319G\"></sup>appoint over them four kinds <i>of doom</i>,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: “the sword to slay, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19319H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19319H\"></sup>dogs to drag off, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19319I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19319I\"></sup>birds of the sky and the beasts of the earth to devour and destroy.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19320J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19320J\"></sup>make them an object of horror among all the kingdoms of the earth because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19320K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19320K\"></sup>Manasseh, the son of Hezekiah, the king of Judah, for what he did in Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Indeed, who will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19321L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19321L\"></sup>pity on you, O Jerusalem,Or who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19321M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19321M\"></sup>mourn for you,Or who will turn aside to ask about your welfare?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“You who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19322N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19322N\"></sup>forsaken Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“You keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19322O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19322O\"></sup>going backward.So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19322P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19322P\"></sup>stretch out My hand against you and destroy you;I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19322Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19322Q\"></sup>tired of relenting!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19323R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19323R\"></sup>winnow them with a winnowing forkAt the gates of the land;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19323S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19323S\"></sup>bereave <i>them</i> of children, I will destroy My people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19323T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19323T\"></sup>They did not repent of their ways.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19324U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19324U\"></sup>widows will be more numerous before MeThan the sand of the seas;I will bring against them, against the mother of a young man,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19324V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19324V\"></sup>destroyer at noonday;I will suddenly bring down on herAnguish and dismay.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“She who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19325W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19325W\"></sup>bore seven <i>sons</i> pines away;Her breathing is labored.Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19325X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19325X\"></sup>sun has set while it was yet day;She has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19325Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19325Y\"></sup>shamed and humiliated.So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19325Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19325Z\"></sup>give over their survivors to the swordBefore their enemies,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19326AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19326AA\"></sup>Woe to me, my mother, that you have borne me<i>As</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19326AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19326AB\"></sup>man of strife and a man of contention to all the land!I have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19326AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19326AC\"></sup>lent, nor have men lent money to me,<i>Yet</i> everyone curses me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Surely I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19327AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19327AD\"></sup>set you free for <i>purposes of</i> good;Surely I will cause the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19327AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19327AE\"></sup>enemy to make supplication to youIn a time of disaster and a time of distress.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Can anyone smash iron,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19328AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19328AF\"></sup>Iron from the north, or bronze?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19329AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19329AG\"></sup>wealth and your treasuresI will give for booty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19329AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19329AH\"></sup>without cost,Even for all your sinsAnd within all your borders.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Then I will cause your enemies to bring <i>it</i>Into a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19330AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19330AI\"></sup>land you do not know;For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19330AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19330AJ\"></sup>fire has been kindled in My anger,It will burn upon you.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19331AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19331AK\"></sup>You who know, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Remember me, take notice of me,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19331AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19331AL\"></sup>take vengeance for me on my persecutors.Do not, in view of Your patience, take me away;Know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19331AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19331AM\"></sup>for Your sake I endure reproach.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Your words were found and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19332AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19332AN\"></sup>ate them,And Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19332AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19332AO\"></sup>words became for me a joy and the delight of my heart;For I have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19332AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19332AP\"></sup>called by Your name,O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of hosts.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19333AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19333AQ\"></sup>did not sit in the circle of merrymakers,Nor did I exult.Because of Your hand <i>upon me</i> I sat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19333AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19333AR\"></sup>alone,For You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19333AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19333AS\"></sup>filled me with indignation.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Why has my pain been perpetualAnd my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19334AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19334AT\"></sup>wound incurable, refusing to be healed?Will You indeed be to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19334AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19334AU\"></sup>like a deceptive <i>stream</i>With water that is unreliable?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19335AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19335AV\"></sup>If you return, then I will restore you—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19335AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19335AW\"></sup>Before Me you will stand;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19335AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19335AX\"></sup>if you extract the precious from the worthless,You will become My spokesman.They for their part may turn to you,But as for you, you must not turn to them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19336AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19336AY\"></sup>make you to this peopleA fortified wall of bronze;And though they fight against you,They will not prevail over you;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19336AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19336AZ\"></sup>I am with you to save youAnd deliver you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19337BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19337BA\"></sup>deliver you from the hand of the wicked,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19337BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19337BB\"></sup>redeem you from the grasp of the violent.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> also came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“You shall not take a wife for yourself nor have sons or daughters in this place.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the sons and daughters born in this place, and concerning their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19340A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19340A\"></sup>mothers who bear them, and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19340B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19340B\"></sup>fathers who beget them in this land:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19341C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19341C\"></sup>die of deadly diseases, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19341D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19341D\"></sup>will not be lamented or buried; they will be as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19341E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19341E\"></sup>dung on the surface of the ground and come to an end by sword and famine, and their carcasses will become food for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19341F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19341F\"></sup>birds of the sky and for the beasts of the earth.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Do not enter a house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19342G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19342G\"></sup>mourning, or go to lament or to console them; for I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19342H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19342H\"></sup>withdrawn My peace from this people,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<i>My</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19342I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19342I\"></sup>lovingkindness and compassion.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19343J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19343J\"></sup>great men and small will die in this land; they will not be buried, they will not be lamented, nor will anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19343K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19343K\"></sup>gash himself or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19343L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19343L\"></sup>shave his head for them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Men will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19344M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19344M\"></sup>break <i>bread</i> in mourning for them, to comfort anyone for the dead, nor give them a cup of consolation to drink for anyone’s father or mother.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Moreover you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19345N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19345N\"></sup>not go into a house of feasting to sit with them to eat and drink.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: “Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19346O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19346O\"></sup>eliminate from this place, before your eyes and in your time, the voice of rejoicing and the voice of gladness, the voice of the groom and the voice of the bride.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Now when you tell this people all these words, they will say to you, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19347P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19347P\"></sup>For what reason has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declared all this great calamity against us? And what is our iniquity, or what is our sin which we have committed against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God?’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then you are to say to them, ‘<i>It is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19348Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19348Q\"></sup>because your forefathers have forsaken Me,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and have followed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19348R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19348R\"></sup>other gods and served them and bowed down to them; but Me they have forsaken and have not kept My law.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You too have done evil, <i>even</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19349S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19349S\"></sup>more than your forefathers; for behold, you are each one walking according to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19349T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19349T\"></sup>stubbornness of his own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19349U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19349U\"></sup>evil heart, without listening to Me.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19350V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19350V\"></sup>hurl you out of this land into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19350W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19350W\"></sup>land which you have not known, neither you nor your fathers; and there you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19350X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19350X\"></sup>serve other gods day and night, for I will grant you no favor.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19351Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19351Y\"></sup>Therefore behold, days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when it will no longer be said, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19351Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19351Z\"></sup>brought up the sons of Israel out of the land of Egypt,’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who brought up the sons of Israel from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19352AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19352AA\"></sup>land of the north and from all the countries where He had banished them.’ For I will restore them to their own land which I gave to their fathers.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Behold, I am going to send for many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19353AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19353AB\"></sup>fishermen,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and they will fish for them; and afterwards I will send for many hunters, and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19353AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19353AC\"></sup>hunt them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19353AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19353AD\"></sup>from every mountain and every hill and from the clefts of the rocks.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19354AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19354AE\"></sup>For My eyes are on all their ways; they are not hidden from My face, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19354AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19354AF\"></sup>nor is their iniquity concealed from My eyes.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19355AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19355AG\"></sup>doubly repay their iniquity and their sin, because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19355AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19355AH\"></sup>polluted My land; they have filled My inheritance with the carcasses of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19355AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19355AI\"></sup>detestable idols and with their abominations.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19356AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19356AJ\"></sup>strength and my stronghold,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19356AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19356AK\"></sup>refuge in the day of distress,To You the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19356AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19356AL\"></sup>nations will comeFrom the ends of the earth and say,“Our fathers have inherited nothing but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19356AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19356AM\"></sup>falsehood,Futility and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19356AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19356AN\"></sup>things of no profit.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Can man make gods for himself?Yet they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19357AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19357AO\"></sup>not gods!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Therefore behold, I am going to make them know—This time I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19358AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19358AP\"></sup>make them knowMy power and My might;And they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19358AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19358AQ\"></sup>know that My name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19359A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19359A\"></sup>sin of Judah is written down with an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19359B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19359B\"></sup>iron stylus;With a diamond point it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19359C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19359C\"></sup>engraved upon the tablet of their heartAnd on the horns of their altars,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As they remember their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19360D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19360D\"></sup>children,So they <i>remember</i> their altars and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19360E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19360E\"></sup>AsherimBy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19360F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19360F\"></sup>green trees on the high hills.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19361G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19361G\"></sup>mountain of Mine in the countryside,I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19361H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19361H\"></sup>give over your wealth and all your treasures for booty,Your high places for sin throughout your borders.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And you will, even of yourself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19362I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19362I\"></sup>let go of your inheritanceThat I gave you;And I will make you serve your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19362J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19362J\"></sup>enemiesIn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19362K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19362K\"></sup>land which you do not know;For you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19362L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19362L\"></sup>kindled a fire in My angerWhich will burn forever.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19363M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19363M\"></sup>Cursed is the man who trusts in mankindAnd makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19363N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19363N\"></sup>flesh his strength,And whose heart turns away from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For he will be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19364O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19364O\"></sup>bush in the desertAnd will not see when prosperity comes,But will live in stony wastes in the wilderness,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19364P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19364P\"></sup>land of salt without inhabitant.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19365Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19365Q\"></sup>Blessed is the man who trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19365R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19365R\"></sup>trust is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For he will be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19366S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19366S\"></sup>tree planted by the water,That extends its roots by a streamAnd will not fear when the heat comes;But its leaves will be green,And it will not be anxious in a year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19366T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19366T\"></sup>droughtNor cease to yield fruit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19367U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19367U\"></sup>heart is more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19367V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19367V\"></sup>deceitful than all elseAnd is desperately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19367W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19367W\"></sup>sick;Who can understand it?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19368X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19368X\"></sup>search the heart,I test the mind,Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19368Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19368Y\"></sup>to give to each man according to his ways,According to the results of his deeds.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“As a partridge that hatches eggs which it has not laid,<i>So</i> is he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19369Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19369Z\"></sup>makes a fortune, but unjustly;In the midst of his days it will forsake him,And in the end he will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19369AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19369AA\"></sup>fool.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19370AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19370AB\"></sup>A glorious throne on high from the beginningIs the place of our sanctuary.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19371AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19371AC\"></sup>hope of Israel,All who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19371AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19371AD\"></sup>forsake You will be put to shame.Those who turn away on earth will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19371AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19371AE\"></sup>written down,Because they have forsaken the fountain of living water, even the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19372AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19372AF\"></sup>Heal me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I will be healed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19372AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19372AG\"></sup>Save me and I will be saved,For You are my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19372AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19372AH\"></sup>praise.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Look, they keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19373AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19373AI\"></sup>saying to me,“Where is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?Let it come now!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But as for me, I have not hurried away from <i>being</i> a shepherd after You,Nor have I longed for the woeful day;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19374AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19374AJ\"></sup>You Yourself know that the utterance of my lipsWas in Your presence.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19375AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19375AK\"></sup>terror to me;You are my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19375AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19375AL\"></sup>refuge in the day of disaster.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let those who persecute me be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19376AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19376AM\"></sup>put to shame, but as for me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19376AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19376AN\"></sup>let me not be put to shame;Let them be dismayed, but let me not be dismayed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19376AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19376AO\"></sup>Bring on them a day of disaster,And crush them with twofold destruction!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Go and stand in the public gate, through which the kings of Judah come in and go out, as well as in all the gates of Jerusalem;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and say to them, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19378AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19378AP\"></sup>Listen to the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19378AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19378AQ\"></sup>kings of Judah, and all Judah and all inhabitants of Jerusalem who come in through these gates:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19379AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19379AR\"></sup>Take heed for yourselves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19379AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19379AS\"></sup>do not carry any load on the sabbath day or bring anything in through the gates of Jerusalem.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You shall not bring a load out of your houses on the sabbath day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19380AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19380AT\"></sup>nor do any work, but keep the sabbath day holy, as I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19380AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19380AU\"></sup>commanded your forefathers.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Yet they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19381AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19381AV\"></sup>did not listen or incline their ears, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19381AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19381AW\"></sup>stiffened their necks in order not to listen or take correction.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But it will come about, if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19382AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19382AX\"></sup>listen attentively to Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19382AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19382AY\"></sup>bring no load in through the gates of this city on the sabbath day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19382AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19382AZ\"></sup>but to keep the sabbath day holy by doing no work on it,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19383BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19383BA\"></sup>then there will come in through the gates of this city kings and princes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19383BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19383BB\"></sup>sitting on the throne of David, riding in chariots and on horses, they and their princes, the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem, and this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19383BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19383BC\"></sup>city will be inhabited forever.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will come in from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19384BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19384BD\"></sup>cities of Judah and from the environs of Jerusalem, from the land of Benjamin, from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19384BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19384BE\"></sup>lowland, from the hill country and from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19384BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19384BF\"></sup>Negev, bringing burnt offerings, sacrifices, grain offerings and incense, and bringing sacrifices of thanksgiving to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19385BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19385BG\"></sup>if you do not listen to Me to keep the sabbath day holy by not carrying a load and coming in through the gates of Jerusalem on the sabbath day, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19385BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19385BH\"></sup>I will kindle a fire in its gates and it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19385BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19385BI\"></sup>devour the palaces of Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19385BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19385BJ\"></sup>not be quenched.”’”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Arise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19387A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19387A\"></sup>go down to the potter’s house, and there I will announce My words to you.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I went down to the potter’s house, and there he was, making something on the wheel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But the vessel that he was making of clay was spoiled in the hand of the potter; so he remade it into another vessel, as it pleased the potter to make.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Can I not, O house of Israel, deal with you as this potter <i>does</i>?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “Behold, like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19391B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19391B\"></sup>clay in the potter’s hand, so are you in My hand, O house of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>At one moment I might speak concerning a nation or concerning a kingdom to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19392C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19392C\"></sup>uproot, to pull down, or to destroy <i>it</i>;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19393D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19393D\"></sup>if that nation against which I have spoken turns from its evil, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19393E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19393E\"></sup>relent concerning the calamity I planned to bring on it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Or at another moment I might speak concerning a nation or concerning a kingdom to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19394F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19394F\"></sup>build up or to plant <i>it</i>;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>if it does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19395G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19395G\"></sup>evil in My sight by not obeying My voice, then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19395H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19395H\"></sup>think better of the good with which I had promised to bless it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So now then, speak to the men of Judah and against the inhabitants of Jerusalem saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19396I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19396I\"></sup>fashioning calamity against you and devising a plan against you. Oh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19396J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19396J\"></sup>turn back, each of you from his evil way, and reform your ways and your deeds.”’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19397K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19397K\"></sup>they will say, ‘It’s hopeless! For we are going to follow our own plans, and each of us will act according to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19397L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19397L\"></sup>stubbornness of his evil heart.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19398M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19398M\"></sup>Ask now among the nations,Who ever heard the like of this?The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19398N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19398N\"></sup>virgin of IsraelHas done a most <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19398O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19398O\"></sup>appalling thing.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Does the snow of Lebanon forsake the rock of the open country?Or is the cold flowing water <i>from</i> a foreign <i>land</i> ever snatched away?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19400P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19400P\"></sup>My people have forgotten Me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19400Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19400Q\"></sup>They burn incense to worthless godsAnd they have stumbled from their ways,From the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19400R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19400R\"></sup>ancient paths,To walk in bypaths,Not on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19400S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19400S\"></sup>highway,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>To make their land a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19401T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19401T\"></sup>desolation,<i>An object of</i> perpetual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19401U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19401U\"></sup>hissing;Everyone who passes by it will be astonishedAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19401V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19401V\"></sup>shake his head.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19402W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19402W\"></sup>east wind I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19402X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19402X\"></sup>scatter themBefore the enemy;I will show them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19402Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19402Y\"></sup>My back and not <i>My</i> face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19402Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19402Z\"></sup>In the day of their calamity.’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then they said, “Come and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19403AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19403AA\"></sup>devise plans against Jeremiah. Surely the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19403AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19403AB\"></sup>law is not going to be lost to the priest, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19403AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19403AC\"></sup>counsel to the sage, nor the <i>divine</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19403AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19403AD\"></sup>word to the prophet! Come on and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19403AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19403AE\"></sup>strike at him with <i>our</i> tongue, and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19403AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19403AF\"></sup>give no heed to any of his words.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do give heed to me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And listen to what my opponents are saying!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19405AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19405AG\"></sup>Should good be repaid with evil?For they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19405AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19405AH\"></sup>dug a pit for me.Remember how I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19405AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19405AI\"></sup>stood before YouTo speak good on their behalf,So as to turn away Your wrath from them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19406AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19406AJ\"></sup>give their children over to famineAnd deliver them up to the power of the sword;And let their wives become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19406AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19406AK\"></sup>childless and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19406AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19406AL\"></sup>widowed.Let their men also be smitten to death,Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19406AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19406AM\"></sup>young men struck down by the sword in battle.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>May an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19407AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19407AN\"></sup>outcry be heard from their houses,When You suddenly bring raiders upon them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19407AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19407AO\"></sup>For they have dug a pit to capture meAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19407AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19407AP\"></sup>hidden snares for my feet.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Yet You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, knowAll their deadly designs against me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19408AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19408AQ\"></sup>Do not forgive their iniquityOr blot out their sin from Your sight.But may they be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19408AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19408AR\"></sup>overthrown before You;Deal with them in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19408AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19408AS\"></sup>time of Your anger!"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Go and buy a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19409A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19409A\"></sup>potter’s earthenware <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19409B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19409B\"></sup>jar, and <i>take</i> some of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19409C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19409C\"></sup>elders of the people and some of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19409D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19409D\"></sup>senior priests.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then go out to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19410E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19410E\"></sup>valley of Ben-hinnom, which is by the entrance of the potsherd gate, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19410F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19410F\"></sup>proclaim there the words that I tell you,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19411G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19411G\"></sup>kings of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem: thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Behold I am about to bring a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19411H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19411H\"></sup>calamity upon this place, at which the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19411I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19411I\"></sup>ears of everyone that hears of it will tingle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19412J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19412J\"></sup>forsaken Me and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19412K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19412K\"></sup>made this an alien place and have burned sacrifices in it to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19412L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19412L\"></sup>other gods, that neither they nor their forefathers nor the kings of Judah had <i>ever</i> known, and <i>because</i> they have filled this place with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19412M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19412M\"></sup>blood of the innocent",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and have built the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19413N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19413N\"></sup>high places of Baal to burn their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19413O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19413O\"></sup>sons in the fire as burnt offerings to Baal, a thing which I never commanded or spoke of, nor did it <i>ever</i> enter My mind;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>therefore, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19414P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19414P\"></sup>days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when this place will no longer be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19414Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19414Q\"></sup>Topheth or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19414R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19414R\"></sup>the valley of Ben-hinnom, but rather the valley of Slaughter.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19415S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19415S\"></sup>make void the counsel of Judah and Jerusalem in this place, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19415T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19415T\"></sup>I will cause them to fall by the sword before their enemies and by the hand of those who seek their life; and I will give over their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19415U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19415U\"></sup>carcasses as food for the birds of the sky and the beasts of the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will also make this city a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19416V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19416V\"></sup>desolation and an <i>object of</i> hissing; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19416W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19416W\"></sup>everyone who passes by it will be astonished and hiss because of all its disasters.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19417X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19417X\"></sup>eat the flesh of their sons and the flesh of their daughters, and they will eat one another’s flesh in the siege and in the distress with which their enemies and those who seek their life will distress them.”’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Then you are to break the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19418Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19418Y\"></sup>jar in the sight of the men who accompany you",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “Just so will I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19419Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19419Z\"></sup>break this people and this city, even as one breaks a potter’s vessel, which cannot again be repaired; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19419AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19419AA\"></sup>bury in Topheth because there is no <i>other</i> place for burial.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is how I will treat this place and its inhabitants,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “so as to make this city like Topheth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19421AB\"></sup>houses of Jerusalem and the houses of the kings of Judah will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19421AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19421AC\"></sup>defiled like the place Topheth, because of all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19421AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19421AD\"></sup>houses on whose rooftops they burned sacrifices to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19421AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19421AE\"></sup>all the heavenly host and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19421AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19421AF\"></sup>poured out drink offerings to other gods.”’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then Jeremiah came from Topheth, where the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had sent him to prophesy; and he stood in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19422AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19422AG\"></sup>court of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house and said to all the people:",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Behold, I am about to bring on this city and all its towns the entire calamity that I have declared against it, because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19423AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19423AH\"></sup>stiffened their necks so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19423AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19423AI\"></sup>as not to heed My words.’”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>When Pashhur the priest, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19424A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19424A\"></sup>Immer, who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19424B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19424B\"></sup>chief officer in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, heard Jeremiah prophesying these things,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Pashhur had Jeremiah the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19425C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19425C\"></sup>beaten and put him in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19425D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19425D\"></sup>stocks that were at the upper <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19425E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19425E\"></sup>Benjamin Gate, which was by the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>On the next day, when Pashhur released Jeremiah from the stocks, Jeremiah said to him, “Pashhur is not the name the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19426F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19426F\"></sup>called you, but rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19426G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19426G\"></sup>Magor-missabib.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Behold, I am going to make you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19427H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19427H\"></sup>terror to yourself and to all your friends; and while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19427I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19427I\"></sup>your eyes look on, they will fall by the sword of their enemies. So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19427J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19427J\"></sup>give over all Judah to the hand of the king of Babylon, and he will carry them away as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19427K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19427K\"></sup>exiles to Babylon and will slay them with the sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will also give over all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19428L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19428L\"></sup>wealth of this city, all its produce and all its costly things; even all the treasures of the kings of Judah I will give over to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19428M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19428M\"></sup>hand of their enemies, and they will plunder them, take them away and bring them to Babylon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19429N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19429N\"></sup>Pashhur, and all who live in your house will go into captivity; and you will enter Babylon, and there you will die and there you will be buried, you and all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19429O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19429O\"></sup>friends to whom you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19429P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19429P\"></sup>falsely prophesied.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, You have deceived me and I was deceived;You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19430Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19430Q\"></sup>overcome me and prevailed.I have become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19430R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19430R\"></sup>laughingstock all day long;Everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19430S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19430S\"></sup>mocks me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For each time I speak, I cry aloud;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19431T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19431T\"></sup>proclaim violence and destruction,Because for me the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19431U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19431U\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has resultedIn reproach and derision all day long.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But if I say, “I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19432V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19432V\"></sup>remember HimOr speak anymore in His name,”Then in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19432W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19432W\"></sup>my heart it becomes like a burning fireShut up in my bones;And I am weary of holding <i>it</i> in,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19432X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19432X\"></sup>I cannot endure <i>it</i>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19433Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19433Y\"></sup>I have heard the whispering of many,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19433Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19433Z\"></sup>Terror on every side!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19433AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19433AA\"></sup>Denounce <i>him</i>; yes, let us denounce him!”All my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19433AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19433AB\"></sup>trusted friends,Watching for my fall, say:“Perhaps he will be deceived, so that we may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19433AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19433AC\"></sup>prevail against himAnd take our revenge on him.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19434AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19434AD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with me like a dread champion;Therefore my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19434AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19434AE\"></sup>persecutors will stumble and not prevail.They will be utterly ashamed, because they have failed,With an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19434AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19434AF\"></sup>everlasting disgrace that will not be forgotten.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Yet, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, You who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19435AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19435AG\"></sup>test the righteous,Who see the mind and the heart;Let me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19435AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19435AH\"></sup>see Your vengeance on them;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19435AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19435AI\"></sup>to You I have set forth my cause.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19436AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19436AJ\"></sup>Sing to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!For He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19436AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19436AK\"></sup>delivered the soul of the needy oneFrom the hand of evildoers.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Cursed be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19437AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19437AL\"></sup>day when I was born;Let the day not be blessed when my mother bore me!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Cursed be the man who brought the newsTo my father, saying,“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19438AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19438AM\"></sup>baby boy has been born to you!”<i>And</i> made him very happy.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But let that man be like the citiesWhich the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19439AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19439AN\"></sup>overthrew without relenting,And let him hear an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19439AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19439AO\"></sup>outcry in the morningAnd a shout of alarm at noon;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because he did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19440AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19440AP\"></sup>kill me before birth,So that my mother would have been my grave,And her womb ever pregnant.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Why did I ever come forth from the wombTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19441AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19441AQ\"></sup>look on trouble and sorrow,So that my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19441AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19441AR\"></sup>days have been spent in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19441AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19441AS\"></sup>shame?"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19442A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19442A\"></sup>King Zedekiah sent to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19442B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19442B\"></sup>Pashhur the son of Malchijah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19442C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19442C\"></sup>Zephaniah the priest, the son of Maaseiah, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Please <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19443D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19443D\"></sup>inquire of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on our behalf, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19443E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19443E\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19443F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19443F\"></sup>Babylon is warring against us; perhaps the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deal with us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19443G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19443G\"></sup>according to all His wonderful acts, so that <i>the enemy</i> will withdraw from us.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to them, “You shall say to Zedekiah as follows:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel, “Behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19445H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19445H\"></sup>turn back the weapons of war which are in your hands, with which you are warring against the king of Babylon and the Chaldeans who are besieging you outside the wall; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19445I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19445I\"></sup>gather them into the center of this city.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19446J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19446J\"></sup>Myself will war against you with an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19446K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19446K\"></sup>outstretched hand and a mighty arm, even in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19446L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19446L\"></sup>anger and wrath and great indignation.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will also strike down the inhabitants of this city, both man and beast; they will die of a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19447M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19447M\"></sup>pestilence.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then afterwards,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19448N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19448N\"></sup>I will give over Zedekiah king of Judah and his servants and the people, even those who survive in this city from the pestilence, the sword and the famine, into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and into the hand of their foes and into the hand of those who seek their lives; and he will strike them down with the edge of the sword. He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19448O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19448O\"></sup>will not spare them nor have pity nor compassion.”’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“You shall also say to this people, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19449P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19449P\"></sup>set before you the way of life and the way of death.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19450Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19450Q\"></sup>dwells in this city will die by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19450R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19450R\"></sup>sword and by famine and by pestilence; but he who goes out and falls away to the Chaldeans who are besieging you will live, and he will have his own life as booty.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19451S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19451S\"></sup>set My face against this city for harm and not for good,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “It will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19451T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19451T\"></sup>given into the hand of the king of Babylon and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19451U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19451U\"></sup>burn it with fire.”’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Then <i>say</i> to the household of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19452V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19452V\"></sup>king of Judah, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19453W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19453W\"></sup>house of David, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19453X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19453X\"></sup>Administer justice every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19453Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19453Y\"></sup>morning;And deliver the <i>person</i> who has been robbed from the power of <i>his</i> oppressor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19453Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19453Z\"></sup>That My wrath may not go forth like fireAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19453AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19453AA\"></sup>burn with none to extinguish <i>it</i>,Because of the evil of their deeds.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19454AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19454AB\"></sup>I am against you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19454AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19454AC\"></sup>valley dweller,O rocky plain,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“You men who say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19454AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19454AD\"></sup>Who will come down against us?Or who will enter into our habitations?’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“But I will punish you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19455AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19455AE\"></sup>according to the results of your deeds,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19455AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19455AF\"></sup>kindle a fire in its forestThat it may devour all its environs.”’”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Go down to the house of the king of Judah, and there speak this word",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and say, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O king of Judah, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19457A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19457A\"></sup>sits on David’s throne, you and your servants and your people who enter these gates.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19458B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19458B\"></sup>Do justice and righteousness, and deliver the one who has been robbed from the power of <i>his</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19458C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19458C\"></sup>oppressor. Also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19458D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19458D\"></sup>do not mistreat <i>or</i> do violence to the stranger, the orphan, or the widow; and do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19458E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19458E\"></sup>shed innocent blood in this place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For if you men will indeed perform this thing, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19459F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19459F\"></sup>kings will enter the gates of this house, sitting in David’s place on his throne, riding in chariots and on horses, <i>even the king</i> himself and his servants and his people.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19460G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19460G\"></sup>But if you will not obey these words, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19460H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19460H\"></sup>swear by Myself,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “that this house will become a desolation.”’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the house of the king of Judah:“You are <i>like</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19461I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19461I\"></sup>Gilead to Me,<i>Like</i> the summit of Lebanon;Yet most assuredly I will make you like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19461J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19461J\"></sup>wilderness,<i>Like</i> cities which are not inhabited.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For I will set apart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19462K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19462K\"></sup>destroyers against you,Each with his weapons;And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19462L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19462L\"></sup>cut down your choicest cedarsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19462M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19462M\"></sup>throw <i>them</i> on the fire.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Many nations will pass by this city; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19463N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19463N\"></sup>say to one another, ‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> done thus to this great city?’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then they will answer, ‘Because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19464O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19464O\"></sup>forsook the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and bowed down to other gods and served them.’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19465P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19465P\"></sup>Do not weep for the dead or mourn for him,<i>But</i> weep continually for the one who goes away;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19465Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19465Q\"></sup>he will never returnOr see his native land.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in regard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19466R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19466R\"></sup>Shallum the son of Josiah, king of Judah, who became king in the place of Josiah his father, who went forth from this place, “He will never return there;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>but in the place where they led him captive, there he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19467S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19467S\"></sup>die and not see this land again.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Woe to him who builds his house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19468T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19468T\"></sup>without righteousnessAnd his upper rooms without justice,Who uses his neighbor’s services without payAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19468U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19468U\"></sup>does not give him his wages,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Who says, ‘I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19469V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19469V\"></sup>build myself a roomy houseWith spacious upper rooms,And cut out its windows,Paneling <i>it</i> with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19469W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19469W\"></sup>cedar and painting <i>it</i> bright red.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Do you become a king because you are competing in cedar?Did not your father eat and drinkAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19470X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19470X\"></sup>do justice and righteousness?Then it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19470Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19470Y\"></sup>well with him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“He pled the cause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19471Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19471Z\"></sup>afflicted and needy;Then it was well.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19471AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19471AA\"></sup>Is not that what it means to know Me?”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But your eyes and your heartAre <i>intent</i> only upon your own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19472AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19472AB\"></sup>dishonest gain,And on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19472AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19472AC\"></sup>shedding innocent bloodAnd on practicing oppression and extortion.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in regard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19473AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19473AD\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah,“They will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19473AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19473AE\"></sup>lament for him:‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19473AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19473AF\"></sup>Alas, my brother!’ or, ‘Alas, sister!’They will not lament for him:‘Alas for the master!’ or, ‘Alas for his splendor!’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19474AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19474AG\"></sup>buried with a donkey’s burial,Dragged off and thrown out beyond the gates of Jerusalem.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Go up to Lebanon and cry out,And lift up your voice in Bashan;Cry out also from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19475AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19475AH\"></sup>Abarim,For all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19475AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19475AI\"></sup>lovers have been crushed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“I spoke to you in your prosperity;But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19476AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19476AJ\"></sup>you said, ‘I will not listen!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19476AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19476AK\"></sup>This has been your practice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19476AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19476AL\"></sup>from your youth,That you have not obeyed My voice.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“The wind will sweep away all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19477AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19477AM\"></sup>shepherds,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19477AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19477AN\"></sup>lovers will go into captivity;Then you will surely be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19477AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19477AO\"></sup>ashamed and humiliatedBecause of all your wickedness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“You who dwell in Lebanon,Nested in the cedars,How you will groan when pangs come upon you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19478AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19478AP\"></sup>Pain like a woman in childbirth!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“As I live,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “even though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19479AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19479AQ\"></sup>Coniah the son of Jehoiakim king of Judah were a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19479AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19479AR\"></sup>signet <i>ring</i> on My right hand, yet I would pull you off;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19480AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19480AS\"></sup>give you over into the hand of those who are seeking your life, yes, into the hand of those whom you dread, even into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and into the hand of the Chaldeans.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19481AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19481AT\"></sup>hurl you and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19481AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19481AU\"></sup>mother who bore you into another country where you were not born, and there you will die.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But as for the land to which they desire to return, they will not return to it.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Is this man Coniah a despised, shattered jar?Or is he an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19483AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19483AV\"></sup>undesirable vessel?Why have he and his descendants been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19483AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19483AW\"></sup>hurled outAnd cast into a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19483AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19483AX\"></sup>land that they had not known?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19484AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19484AY\"></sup>O land, land, land,Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘Write this man down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19485AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19485AZ\"></sup>childless,A man who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19485BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19485BA\"></sup>not prosper in his days;For no man of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19485BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19485BB\"></sup>descendants will prosperSitting on the throne of DavidOr ruling again in Judah.’”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19486A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19486A\"></sup>Woe to the shepherds who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19486B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19486B\"></sup>destroying and scattering the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19486C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19486C\"></sup>sheep of My pasture!” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel concerning the shepherds who are tending My people: “You have scattered My flock and driven them away, and have not attended to them; behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19487D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19487D\"></sup>attend to you for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19487E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19487E\"></sup>evil of your deeds,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Then I Myself will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19488F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19488F\"></sup>gather the remnant of My flock out of all the countries where I have driven them and bring them back to their pasture, and they will be fruitful and multiply.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will also raise up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19489G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19489G\"></sup>shepherds over them and they will tend them; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19489H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19489H\"></sup>not be afraid any longer, nor be terrified, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19489I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19489I\"></sup>nor will any be missing,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Behold, <i>the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19490J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19490J\"></sup>days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“When I will raise up for David a righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19490K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19490K\"></sup>Branch;And He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19490L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19490L\"></sup>reign as king and act wiselyAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19490M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19490M\"></sup>do justice and righteousness in the land.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“In His days Judah will be saved,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19491N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19491N\"></sup>Israel will dwell securely;And this is His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19491O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19491O\"></sup>name by which He will be called,‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19491P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19491P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our righteousness.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19492Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19492Q\"></sup>Therefore behold, <i>the</i> days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when they will no longer say, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who brought up the sons of Israel from the land of Egypt,’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19493R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19493R\"></sup>but, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19493S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19493S\"></sup>brought up and led back the descendants of the household of Israel from <i>the</i> north land and from all the countries where I had driven them.’ Then they will live on their own soil.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As for the prophets:My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19494T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19494T\"></sup>heart is broken within me,All my bones tremble;I have become like a drunken man,Even like a man overcome with wine,Because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And because of His holy words.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the land is full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19495U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19495U\"></sup>adulterers;For the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19495V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19495V\"></sup>mourns because of the curse.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19495W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19495W\"></sup>pastures of the wilderness have dried up.Their course also is evilAnd their might is not right.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19496X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19496X\"></sup>both prophet and priest are polluted;Even in My house I have found their wickedness,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore their way will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19497Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19497Y\"></sup>slippery paths to them,They will be driven away into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19497Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19497Z\"></sup>gloom and fall down in it;For I will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19497AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19497AA\"></sup>calamity upon them,The year of their punishment,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Moreover, among the prophets of Samaria I saw an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19498AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19498AB\"></sup>offensive thing:They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19498AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19498AC\"></sup>prophesied by Baal and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19498AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19498AD\"></sup>led My people Israel astray.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Also among the prophets of Jerusalem I have seen a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19499AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19499AE\"></sup>horrible thing:The committing of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19499AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19499AF\"></sup>adultery and walking in falsehood;And they strengthen the hands of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19499AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19499AG\"></sup>evildoers,So that no one has turned back from his wickedness.All of them have become to Me like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19499AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19499AH\"></sup>Sodom,And her inhabitants like Gomorrah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts concerning the prophets,‘Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19500AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19500AI\"></sup>feed them wormwoodAnd make them drink poisonous water,For from the prophets of JerusalemPollution has gone forth into all the land.’”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19501AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19501AJ\"></sup>Do not listen to the words of the prophets who are prophesying to you.They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19501AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19501AK\"></sup>leading you into futility;They speak a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19501AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19501AL\"></sup>vision of their own imagination,Not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19501AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19501AM\"></sup>from the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“They keep saying to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19502AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19502AN\"></sup>despise Me,‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19502AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19502AO\"></sup>You will have peace”’;And as for everyone who walks in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19502AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19502AP\"></sup>stubbornness of his own heart,They say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19502AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19502AQ\"></sup>Calamity will not come upon you.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19503AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19503AR\"></sup>who has stood in the council of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,That he should see and hear His word?Who has given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19503AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19503AS\"></sup>heed to His word and listened?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19504AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19504AT\"></sup>storm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has gone forth in wrath,Even a whirling tempest;It will swirl down on the head of the wicked.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19505AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19505AU\"></sup>anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not turn backUntil He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19505AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19505AV\"></sup>performed and carried out the purposes of His heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19505AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19505AW\"></sup>In the last days you will clearly understand it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19506AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19506AX\"></sup>I did not send <i>these</i> prophets,But they ran.I did not speak to them,But they prophesied.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“But if they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19507AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19507AY\"></sup>stood in My council,Then they would have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19507AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19507AZ\"></sup>announced My words to My people,And would have turned them back from their evil wayAnd from the evil of their deeds.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Am I a God who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19508BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19508BA\"></sup>near,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And not a God far off?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Can a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19509BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19509BB\"></sup>hide himself in hiding placesSo I do not see him?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19509BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19509BC\"></sup>Do I not fill the heavens and the earth?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19510BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19510BD\"></sup>heard what the prophets have said who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19510BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19510BE\"></sup>prophesy falsely in My name, saying, ‘I had a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19510BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19510BF\"></sup>dream, I had a dream!’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>How long? Is there <i>anything</i> in the hearts of the prophets who prophesy falsehood, even <i>these</i> prophets of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19511BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19511BG\"></sup>deception of their own heart,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>who intend to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19512BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19512BH\"></sup>make My people forget My name by their dreams which they relate to one another, just as their fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19512BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19512BI\"></sup>forgot My name because of Baal?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The prophet who has a dream may relate <i>his</i> dream, but let him who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19513BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19513BJ\"></sup>My word speak My word in truth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19513BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19513BK\"></sup>What does straw have <i>in common</i> with grain?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Is not My word like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19514BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19514BL\"></sup>fire?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19514BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19514BM\"></sup>hammer which shatters a rock?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19515BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19515BN\"></sup>I am against the prophets,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “who steal My words from each other.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Behold, I am against the prophets,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “who use their tongues and declare, ‘<i>The Lord</i> declares.’",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Behold, I am against those who have prophesied <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19517BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19517BO\"></sup>false dreams,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and related them and led My people astray by their falsehoods and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19517BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19517BP\"></sup>reckless boasting; yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19517BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19517BQ\"></sup>I did not send them or command them, nor do they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19517BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19517BR\"></sup>furnish this people the slightest benefit,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Now when this people or the prophet or a priest asks you saying, ‘What is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19518BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19518BS\"></sup>oracle of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’ then you shall say to them, ‘What oracle?’ The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares, ‘I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19518BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19518BT\"></sup>abandon you.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Then as for the prophet or the priest or the people who say, ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19519BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19519BU\"></sup>oracle of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ I will bring punishment upon that man and his household.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Thus will each of you say to his neighbor and to his brother, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19520BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19520BV\"></sup>What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered?’ or, ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken?’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For you will no longer remember the oracle of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, because every man’s own word will become the oracle, and you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19521BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19521BW\"></sup>perverted the words of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19521BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19521BX\"></sup>living God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, our God.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Thus you will say to <i>that</i> prophet, ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered you?’ and, ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken?’",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>For if you say, ‘The oracle of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!’ surely thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Because you said this word, “The oracle of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!” I have also sent to you, saying, “You shall not say, ‘The oracle of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!’”’",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Therefore behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19524BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19524BY\"></sup>I will surely forget you and cast you away from My presence, along with the city which I gave you and your fathers.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>I will put an everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19525BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19525BZ\"></sup>reproach on you and an everlasting humiliation which will not be forgotten.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19526A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19526A\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon had carried away captive Jeconiah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, and the officials of Judah with the craftsmen and smiths from Jerusalem and had brought them to Babylon, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me: behold, two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19526B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19526B\"></sup>baskets of figs set before the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>One basket had very good figs, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19527C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19527C\"></sup>first-ripe figs, and the other basket had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19527D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19527D\"></sup>very bad figs which could not be eaten due to rottenness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19528E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19528E\"></sup>What do you see, Jeremiah?” And I said, “Figs, the good figs, very good; and the bad <i>figs</i>, very bad, which cannot be eaten due to rottenness.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel, ‘Like these good figs, so I will regard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19530F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19530F\"></sup>as good the captives of Judah, whom I have sent out of this place <i>into</i> the land of the Chaldeans.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For I will set My eyes on them for good, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19531G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19531G\"></sup>bring them again to this land; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19531H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19531H\"></sup>build them up and not overthrow them, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19531I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19531I\"></sup>plant them and not pluck them up.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will give them a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19532J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19532J\"></sup>heart to know Me, for I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; and they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19532K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19532K\"></sup>My people, and I will be their God, for they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19532L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19532L\"></sup>return to Me with their whole heart.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘But like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19533M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19533M\"></sup>bad figs which cannot be eaten due to rottenness—indeed, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—so I will abandon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19533N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19533N\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah and his officials, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19533O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19533O\"></sup>remnant of Jerusalem who remain in this land and the ones who dwell in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19533P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19533P\"></sup>Egypt.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19534Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19534Q\"></sup>make them a terror <i>and an</i> evil for all the kingdoms of the earth, as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19534R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19534R\"></sup>reproach and a proverb, a taunt and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19534S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19534S\"></sup>curse in all places where I will scatter them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will send the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19535T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19535T\"></sup>sword, the famine and the pestilence upon them until they are destroyed from the land which I gave to them and their forefathers.’”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah concerning all the people of Judah, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19536A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19536A\"></sup>fourth year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19536B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19536B\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah (that was the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19536C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19536C\"></sup>first year of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon),",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>which Jeremiah the prophet spoke to all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19537D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19537D\"></sup>people of Judah and to all the inhabitants of Jerusalem, saying,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“From the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19538E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19538E\"></sup>thirteenth year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19538F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19538F\"></sup>Josiah the son of Amon, king of Judah, even to this day, these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19538G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19538G\"></sup>twenty-three years the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has come to me, and I have spoken to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19538H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19538H\"></sup>again and again, but you have not listened.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent to you all His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19539I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19539I\"></sup>servants the prophets again and again, but you have not listened nor inclined your ear to hear,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19540J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19540J\"></sup>Turn now everyone from his evil way and from the evil of your deeds, and dwell on the land which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given to you and your forefathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19540K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19540K\"></sup>forever and ever;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19541L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19541L\"></sup>do not go after other gods to serve them and to worship them, and do not provoke Me to anger with the work of your hands, and I will do you no harm.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet you have not listened to Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “in order that you might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19542M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19542M\"></sup>provoke Me to anger with the work of your hands to your own harm.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘Because you have not obeyed My words,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19544N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19544N\"></sup>send and take all the families of the north,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and <i>I will send</i> to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19544O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19544O\"></sup>My servant, and will bring them against this land and against its inhabitants and against all these nations round about; and I will utterly destroy them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19544P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19544P\"></sup>make them a horror and a hissing, and an everlasting desolation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Moreover, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19545Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19545Q\"></sup>take from them the voice of joy and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19545R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19545R\"></sup>sound of the millstones and the light of the lamp.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19546S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19546S\"></sup>This whole land will be a desolation and a horror, and these nations will serve the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19546T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19546T\"></sup>seventy years.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘Then it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19547U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19547U\"></sup>when seventy years are completed I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19547V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19547V\"></sup>punish the king of Babylon and that nation,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘for their iniquity, and the land of the Chaldeans; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19547W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19547W\"></sup>I will make it an everlasting desolation.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will bring upon that land all My words which I have pronounced against it, all that is written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19548X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19548X\"></sup>this book which Jeremiah has prophesied against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19548Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19548Y\"></sup>all the nations.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>(For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19549Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19549Z\"></sup>many nations and great kings will make slaves of them, even them; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19549AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19549AA\"></sup>recompense them according to their deeds and according to the work of their hands.)’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says to me, “Take this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19550AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19550AB\"></sup>cup of the wine of wrath from My hand and cause all the nations to whom I send you to drink it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19551AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19551AC\"></sup>drink and stagger and go mad because of the sword that I will send among them.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then I took the cup from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19552AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19552AD\"></sup>made all the nations to whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent me drink it:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19553AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19553AE\"></sup>Jerusalem and the cities of Judah and its kings <i>and</i> its princes, to make them a ruin, a horror, a hissing and a curse, as it is this day;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19554AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19554AF\"></sup>Pharaoh king of Egypt, his servants, his princes and all his people;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19555AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19555AG\"></sup>foreign people, all the kings of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19555AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19555AH\"></sup>land of Uz, all the kings of the land of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19555AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19555AI\"></sup>Philistines (even Ashkelon, Gaza, Ekron and the remnant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19555AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19555AJ\"></sup>Ashdod);",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19556AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19556AK\"></sup>Edom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19556AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19556AL\"></sup>Moab and the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19556AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19556AM\"></sup>Ammon;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19557AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19557AN\"></sup>Tyre, all the kings of Sidon and the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19557AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19557AO\"></sup>the coastlands which are beyond the sea;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19558AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19558AP\"></sup>Dedan, Tema, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19558AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19558AQ\"></sup>Buz and all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19558AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19558AR\"></sup>cut the corners <i>of their hair</i>;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19559AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19559AS\"></sup>Arabia and all the kings of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19559AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19559AT\"></sup>foreign people who dwell in the desert;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and all the kings of Zimri, all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19560AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19560AU\"></sup>Elam and all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19560AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19560AV\"></sup>Media;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and all the kings of the north, near and far, one with another; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19561AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19561AW\"></sup>all the kingdoms of the earth which are upon the face of the ground, and the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19561AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19561AX\"></sup>Sheshach shall drink after them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“You shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19562AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19562AY\"></sup>Drink, be drunk, vomit, fall and rise no more because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19562AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19562AZ\"></sup>sword which I will send among you.”’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And it will be, if they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19563BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19563BA\"></sup>refuse to take the cup from your hand to drink, then you will say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19563BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19563BB\"></sup>You shall surely drink!",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19564BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19564BC\"></sup>beginning to work calamity in <i>this</i> city which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19564BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19564BD\"></sup>called by My name, and shall you be completely free from punishment? You will not be free from punishment; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19564BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19564BE\"></sup>I am summoning a sword against all the inhabitants of the earth,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Therefore you shall prophesy against them all these words, and you shall say to them,‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19565BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19565BF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19565BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19565BG\"></sup>roar from on highAnd utter His voice from His holy habitation;He will roar mightily against His fold.He will shout like those who tread <i>the grapes</i>,Against all the inhabitants of the earth.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>‘A clamor has come to the end of the earth,Because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19566BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19566BH\"></sup>a controversy with the nations.He is entering into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19566BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19566BI\"></sup>judgment with all flesh;As for the wicked, He has given them to the sword,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“Behold, evil is going forthFrom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19567BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19567BJ\"></sup>nation to nation,And a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19567BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19567BK\"></sup>storm is being stirred upFrom the remotest parts of the earth.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19568BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19568BL\"></sup>slain by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on that day will be from one end of the earth to the other. They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19568BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19568BM\"></sup>not be lamented, gathered or buried; they will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19568BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19568BN\"></sup>dung on the face of the ground.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Wail, you shepherds, and cry;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19569BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19569BO\"></sup>wallow <i>in ashes</i>, you masters of the flock;For the days of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19569BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19569BP\"></sup>slaughter and your dispersions have come,And you will fall like a choice vessel.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19570BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19570BQ\"></sup>Flight will perish from the shepherds,And escape from the masters of the flock.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“<i>Hear</i> the sound of the cry of the shepherds,And the wailing of the masters of the flock!For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is destroying their pasture,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“And the peaceful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19572BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19572BR\"></sup>folds are made silentBecause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19572BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19572BS\"></sup>fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“He has left His hiding place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19573BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19573BT\"></sup>like the lion;For their land has become a horrorBecause of the fierceness of the oppressing <i>sword</i>And because of His fierce anger.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>In the beginning of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19574A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19574A\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, this word came from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19575B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19575B\"></sup>Stand in the court of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house, and speak to all the cities of Judah who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19575C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19575C\"></sup>come to worship <i>in</i> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19575D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19575D\"></sup>all the words that I have commanded you to speak to them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19575E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19575E\"></sup>Do not omit a word!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19576F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19576F\"></sup>Perhaps they will listen and everyone will turn from his evil way, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19576G\"></sup>I may repent of the calamity which I am planning to do to them because of the evil of their deeds.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And you will say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19577H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19577H\"></sup>If you will not listen to Me, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19577I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19577I\"></sup>walk in My law which I have set before you,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to listen to the words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19578J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19578J\"></sup>My servants the prophets, whom I have been sending to you again and again, but you have not listened;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>then I will make this house like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19579K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19579K\"></sup>Shiloh, and this city I will make a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19579L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19579L\"></sup>curse to all the nations of the earth.”’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19580M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19580M\"></sup>priests and the prophets and all the people heard Jeremiah speaking these words in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When Jeremiah finished speaking all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded <i>him</i> to speak to all the people, the priests and the prophets and all the people seized him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19581N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19581N\"></sup>You must die!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Why have you prophesied in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saying, ‘This house will be like Shiloh and this city will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19582O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19582O\"></sup>desolate, without inhabitant’?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19582P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19582P\"></sup>all the people gathered about Jeremiah in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19583Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19583Q\"></sup>officials of Judah heard these things, they came up from the king’s house to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and sat in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19583R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19583R\"></sup>entrance of the New Gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> <i>house</i>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the priests and the prophets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19584S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19584S\"></sup>spoke to the officials and to all the people, saying, “A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19584T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19584T\"></sup>death sentence for this man! For he has prophesied <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19584U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19584U\"></sup>against this city as you have heard in your hearing.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Jeremiah spoke to all the officials and to all the people, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19585V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19585V\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent me to prophesy against this house and against this city all the words that you have heard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19586W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19586W\"></sup>amend your ways and your deeds and obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God; and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will change His mind about the misfortune which He has pronounced against you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But as for me, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19587X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19587X\"></sup>I am in your hands; do with me as is good and right in your sight.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Only know for certain that if you put me to death, you will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19588Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19588Y\"></sup>innocent blood on yourselves, and on this city and on its inhabitants; for truly the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent me to you to speak all these words in your hearing.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then the officials and all the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19589Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19589Z\"></sup>said to the priests and to the prophets, “No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19589AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19589AA\"></sup>death sentence for this man! For he has spoken to us in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19590AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19590AB\"></sup>some of the elders of the land rose up and spoke to all the assembly of the people, saying,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19591AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19591AC\"></sup>Micah of Moresheth prophesied in the days of Hezekiah king of Judah; and he spoke to all the people of Judah, saying, ‘Thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19591AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19591AD\"></sup>Zion will be plowed <i>as</i> a field,And Jerusalem will become ruins,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19591AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19591AE\"></sup>mountain of the house as the high places of a forest.”’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Did Hezekiah king of Judah and all Judah put him to death? Did he not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19592AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19592AF\"></sup>fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19592AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19592AG\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> changed His mind about the misfortune which He had pronounced against them? But we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19592AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19592AH\"></sup>committing a great evil against ourselves.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Indeed, there was also a man who prophesied in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Uriah the son of Shemaiah from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19593AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19593AI\"></sup>Kiriath-jearim; and he prophesied against this city and against this land words similar to all those of Jeremiah.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When King Jehoiakim and all his mighty men and all the officials heard his words, then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19594AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19594AJ\"></sup>king sought to put him to death; but Uriah heard <i>it</i>, and he was afraid and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19594AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19594AK\"></sup>fled and went to Egypt.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then King Jehoiakim sent men to Egypt: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19595AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19595AL\"></sup>Elnathan the son of Achbor and <i>certain</i> men with him <i>went</i> into Egypt.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And they brought Uriah from Egypt and led him to King Jehoiakim, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19596AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19596AM\"></sup>slew him with a sword and cast his dead body into the burial place of the common people.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19597AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19597AN\"></sup>Ahikam the son of Shaphan was with Jeremiah, so that he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19597AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19597AO\"></sup>not given into the hands of the people to put him to death."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>In the beginning of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19598A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19598A\"></sup>Zedekiah the son of Josiah, king of Judah, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to me—“Make for yourself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19599B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19599B\"></sup>bonds and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19599C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19599C\"></sup>yokes and put them on your neck,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and send word to the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19600D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19600D\"></sup>Edom, to the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19600E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19600E\"></sup>Moab, to the king of the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19600F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19600F\"></sup>Ammon, to the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19600G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19600G\"></sup>Tyre and to the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19600H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19600H\"></sup>Sidon by the messengers who come to Jerusalem to Zedekiah king of Judah.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Command them <i>to go</i> to their masters, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, thus you shall say to your masters,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19602I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19602I\"></sup>I have made the earth, the men and the beasts which are on the face of the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19602J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19602J\"></sup>by My great power and by My outstretched arm, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19602K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19602K\"></sup>give it to the one who is pleasing in My sight.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19603L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19603L\"></sup>have given all these lands into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19603M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19603M\"></sup>My servant, and I have given him also the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19603N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19603N\"></sup>wild animals of the field to serve him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19604O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19604O\"></sup>All the nations shall serve him and his son and his grandson <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19604P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19604P\"></sup>until the time of his own land comes; then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19604Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19604Q\"></sup>many nations and great kings will make him their servant.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“It will be, <i>that</i> the nation or the kingdom which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19605R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19605R\"></sup>will not serve him, Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and which will not put its neck under the yoke of the king of Babylon, I will punish that nation with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19605S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19605S\"></sup>sword, with famine and with pestilence,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “until I have destroyed it by his hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But as for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19606T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19606T\"></sup>do not listen to your prophets, your diviners, your dreamers, your soothsayers or your sorcerers who speak to you, saying, ‘You will not serve the king of Babylon.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For they prophesy a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19607U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19607U\"></sup>lie to you in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19607V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19607V\"></sup>remove you far from your land; and I will drive you out and you will perish.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the nation which will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19608W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19608W\"></sup>bring its neck under the yoke of the king of Babylon and serve him, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19608X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19608X\"></sup>let remain on its land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and they will till it and dwell in it.”’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I spoke words like all these to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19609Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19609Y\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah, saying, “Bring your necks under the yoke of the king of Babylon and serve him and his people, and live!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Why will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19610Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19610Z\"></sup>die, you and your people, by the sword, famine and pestilence, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken to that nation which will not serve the king of Babylon?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19611AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19611AA\"></sup>do not listen to the words of the prophets who speak to you, saying, ‘You will not serve the king of Babylon,’ for they prophesy a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19611AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19611AB\"></sup>lie to you;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19612AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19612AC\"></sup>I have not sent them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “but they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19612AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19612AD\"></sup>prophesy falsely in My name, in order that I may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19612AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19612AE\"></sup>drive you out and that you may perish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19612AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19612AF\"></sup>you and the prophets who prophesy to you.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><i>Then</i> I spoke to the priests and to all this people, saying, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Do not listen to the words of your prophets who prophesy to you, saying, ‘Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19613AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19613AG\"></sup>vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house will now shortly be brought again from Babylon’; for they are prophesying a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19613AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19613AH\"></sup>lie to you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not listen to them; serve the king of Babylon, and live! Why should this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19614AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19614AI\"></sup>become a ruin?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19615AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19615AJ\"></sup>if they are prophets, and if the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with them, let them now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19615AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19615AK\"></sup>entreat the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts that the vessels which are left in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, in the house of the king of Judah and in Jerusalem may not go to Babylon.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19616AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19616AL\"></sup>pillars, concerning the sea, concerning the stands and concerning the rest of the vessels that are left in this city,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon did not take when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19617AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19617AM\"></sup>carried into exile Jeconiah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, from Jerusalem to Babylon, and all the nobles of Judah and Jerusalem.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Yes, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, concerning the vessels that are left in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and in the house of the king of Judah and in Jerusalem,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>‘They will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19619AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19619AN\"></sup>carried to Babylon and they will be there until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19619AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19619AO\"></sup>day I visit them,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. ‘Then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19619AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19619AP\"></sup>bring them back and restore them to this place.’”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>Now in the same year, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19620A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19620A\"></sup>in the beginning of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19620B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19620B\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah, in the fourth year, in the fifth month, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19620C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19620C\"></sup>Hananiah the son of Azzur, the prophet, who was from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19620D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19620D\"></sup>Gibeon, spoke to me in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the presence of the priests and all the people, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19621E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19621E\"></sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘I have broken the yoke of the king of Babylon.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Within two years I am going to bring back to this place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19622F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19622F\"></sup>all the vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house, which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon took away from this place and carried to Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19623G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19623G\"></sup>also going to bring back to this place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19623H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19623H\"></sup>Jeconiah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19623I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19623I\"></sup>exiles of Judah who went to Babylon,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘for I will break the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19623J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19623J\"></sup>yoke of the king of Babylon.’”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the prophet Jeremiah spoke to the prophet Hananiah in the presence of the priests and in the presence of all the people who were standing in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19624K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19624K\"></sup>house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and the prophet Jeremiah said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19625L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19625L\"></sup>Amen! May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> do so; may the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> confirm your words which you have prophesied to bring back the vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house and all the exiles, from Babylon to this place.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19626M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19626M\"></sup>hear now this word which I am about to speak in your hearing and in the hearing of all the people!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The prophets who were before me and before you from ancient times <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19627N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19627N\"></sup>prophesied against many lands and against great kingdoms, of war and of calamity and of pestilence.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The prophet who prophesies of peace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19628O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19628O\"></sup>when the word of the prophet comes to pass, then that prophet will be known <i>as</i> one whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has truly sent.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Hananiah the prophet took the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19629P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19629P\"></sup>yoke from the neck of Jeremiah the prophet and broke it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Hananiah spoke in the presence of all the people, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19630Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19630Q\"></sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Even so will I break within two full years the yoke of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon from the neck of all the nations.’” Then the prophet Jeremiah went his way.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19631R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19631R\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah after Hananiah the prophet had broken the yoke from off the neck of the prophet Jeremiah, saying,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Go and speak to Hananiah, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “You have broken the yokes of wood, but you have made instead of them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19632S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19632S\"></sup>yokes of iron.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “I have put a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19633T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19633T\"></sup>yoke of iron on the neck of all these nations, that they may serve Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19633U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19633U\"></sup>serve him. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19633V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19633V\"></sup>I have also given him the beasts of the field.”’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then Jeremiah the prophet said to Hananiah the prophet, “Listen now, Hananiah, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not sent you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19634W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19634W\"></sup>you have made this people trust in a lie.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19635X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19635X\"></sup>Behold, I am about to remove you from the face of the earth. This year you are going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19635Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19635Y\"></sup>die, because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19635Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19635Z\"></sup>counseled rebellion against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So Hananiah the prophet died in the same year in the seventh month."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>Now these are the words of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19637A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19637A\"></sup>letter which Jeremiah the prophet sent from Jerusalem to the rest of the elders of the exile, the priests, the prophets and all the people whom Nebuchadnezzar had taken into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>(This was after King <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19638B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19638B\"></sup>Jeconiah and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19638C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19638C\"></sup>queen mother, the court officials, the princes of Judah and Jerusalem, the craftsmen and the smiths had departed from Jerusalem.)",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><i>The letter was sent</i> by the hand of Elasah the son of Shaphan, and Gemariah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19639D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19639D\"></sup>Hilkiah, whom Zedekiah king of Judah sent to Babylon to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, saying,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, to all the exiles whom I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19640E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19640E\"></sup>sent into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19641F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19641F\"></sup>Build houses and live <i>in them</i>; and plant gardens and eat their produce.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19642G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19642G\"></sup>wives and become the fathers of sons and daughters, and take wives for your sons and give your daughters to husbands, that they may bear sons and daughters; and multiply there and do not decrease.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19643H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19643H\"></sup>Seek the welfare of the city where I have sent you into exile, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19643I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19643I\"></sup>pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on its behalf; for in its welfare you will have welfare.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Do not let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19644J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19644J\"></sup>prophets who are in your midst and your diviners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19644K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19644K\"></sup>deceive you, and do not listen to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19644L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19644L\"></sup>the dreams which they dream.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19645M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19645M\"></sup>prophesy falsely to you in My name; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19645N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19645N\"></sup>I have not sent them,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19646O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19646O\"></sup>seventy years have been completed for Babylon, I will visit you and fulfill My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19646P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19646P\"></sup>good word to you, to bring you back to this place.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For I know the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19647Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19647Q\"></sup>plans that I have for you,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘plans for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19647R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19647R\"></sup>welfare and not for calamity to give you a future and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19647S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19647S\"></sup>hope.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19648T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19648T\"></sup>call upon Me and come and pray to Me, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19648U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19648U\"></sup>listen to you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19649V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19649V\"></sup>seek Me and find <i>Me</i> when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19649W\"></sup>search for Me with all your heart.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19650X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19650X\"></sup>found by you,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19650Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19650Y\"></sup>restore your fortunes and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19650Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19650Z\"></sup>gather you from all the nations and from all the places where I have driven you,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19650AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19650AA\"></sup>bring you back to the place from where I sent you into exile.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Because you have said, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has raised up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19651AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19651AB\"></sup>prophets for us in Babylon’—",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the king who sits on the throne of David, and concerning all the people who dwell in this city, your brothers who did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19652AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19652AC\"></sup>not go with you into exile—",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘Behold, I am sending upon them the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19653AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19653AD\"></sup>sword, famine and pestilence, and I will make them like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19653AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19653AE\"></sup>split-open figs that cannot be eaten due to rottenness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will pursue them with the sword, with famine and with pestilence; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19654AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19654AF\"></sup>make them a terror to all the kingdoms of the earth, to be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19654AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19654AG\"></sup>curse and a horror and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19654AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19654AH\"></sup>hissing, and a reproach among all the nations where I have driven them,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19655AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19655AI\"></sup>not listened to My words,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘which I sent to them again and again by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19655AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19655AJ\"></sup>My servants the prophets; but you did not listen,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You, therefore, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you exiles, whom I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19656AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19656AK\"></sup>sent away from Jerusalem to Babylon.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, concerning Ahab the son of Kolaiah and concerning Zedekiah the son of Maaseiah, who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19657AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19657AL\"></sup>prophesying to you falsely in My name, ‘Behold, I will deliver them into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and he will slay them before your eyes.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Because of them a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19658AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19658AM\"></sup>curse will be used by all the exiles from Judah who are in Babylon, saying, “May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> make you like Zedekiah and like Ahab, whom the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19658AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19658AN\"></sup>roasted in the fire,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19659AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19659AO\"></sup>acted foolishly in Israel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19659AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19659AP\"></sup>have committed adultery with their neighbors’ wives and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19659AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19659AQ\"></sup>spoken words in My name falsely, which I did not command them; and I am He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19659AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19659AR\"></sup>knows and am a witness,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19660AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19660AS\"></sup>Shemaiah the Nehelamite you shall speak, saying,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Because you have sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19661AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19661AT\"></sup>letters in your own name to all the people who are in Jerusalem, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19661AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19661AU\"></sup>Zephaniah the son of Maaseiah, the priest, and to all the priests, saying,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made you priest instead of Jehoiada the priest, to be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19662AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19662AV\"></sup>overseer in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> over every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19662AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19662AW\"></sup>madman who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19662AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19662AX\"></sup>prophesies, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19662AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19662AY\"></sup>put him in the stocks and in the iron collar,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>now then, why have you not rebuked Jeremiah of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19663AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19663AZ\"></sup>Anathoth who prophesies to you?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19664BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19664BA\"></sup>sent to us in Babylon, saying, ‘<i>The exile</i> will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19664BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19664BB\"></sup>long; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19664BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19664BC\"></sup>build houses and live <i>in them</i> and plant gardens and eat their produce.’”’”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19665BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19665BD\"></sup>Zephaniah the priest read this letter to Jeremiah the prophet.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then came the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Jeremiah, saying,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Send to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19667BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19667BE\"></sup>all the exiles, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19667BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19667BF\"></sup>Shemaiah the Nehelamite, “Because Shemaiah has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19667BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19667BG\"></sup>prophesied to you, although I did not send him, and he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19667BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19667BH\"></sup>made you trust in a lie,”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19668BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19668BI\"></sup>punish Shemaiah the Nehelamite and his descendants; he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19668BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19668BJ\"></sup>not have anyone living among this people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19668BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19668BK\"></sup>and he will not see the good that I am about to do to My people,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “because he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19668BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19668BL\"></sup>preached rebellion against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19670A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19670A\"></sup>Write all the words which I have spoken to you in a book.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19671B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19671B\"></sup>days are coming,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘when I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19671C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19671C\"></sup>restore the fortunes of My people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19671D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19671D\"></sup>Israel and Judah.’ The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says, ‘I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19671E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19671E\"></sup>bring them back to the land that I gave to their forefathers and they shall possess it.’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now these are the words which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke concerning Israel and concerning Judah:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘I have heard a sound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19673F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19673F\"></sup>terror,Of dread, and there is no peace.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘Ask now, and seeIf a male can give birth.Why do I see every man<i>With</i> his hands on his loins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19674G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19674G\"></sup>as a woman in childbirth?And <i>why</i> have all faces turned pale?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘Alas! for that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19675H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19675H\"></sup>day is great,There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19675I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19675I\"></sup>none like it;And it is the time of Jacob’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19675J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19675J\"></sup>distress,But he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19675K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19675K\"></sup>saved from it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘It shall come about on that day,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19676L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19676L\"></sup>break his yoke from off their neck and will tear off their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19676M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19676M\"></sup>bonds; and strangers will no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19676N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19676N\"></sup>make them their slaves.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But they shall serve the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19677O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19677O\"></sup>David their king, whom I will raise up for them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19678P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19678P\"></sup>Fear not, O Jacob My servant,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘And do not be dismayed, O Israel;For behold, I will save you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19678Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19678Q\"></sup>from afarAnd your offspring from the land of their captivity.And Jacob will return and will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19678R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19678R\"></sup>quiet and at ease,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19678S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19678S\"></sup>no one will make him afraid.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19679T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19679T\"></sup>I am with you,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘to save you;For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19679U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19679U\"></sup>destroy completely all the nations where I have scattered you,Only I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19679V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19679V\"></sup>not destroy you completely.But I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19679W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19679W\"></sup>chasten you justlyAnd will by no means leave you unpunished.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘Your wound is incurableAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19680X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19680X\"></sup>injury is serious.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘There is no one to plead your cause;<i>No</i> healing for <i>your</i> sore,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19681Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19681Y\"></sup>No recovery for you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘All your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19682Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19682Z\"></sup>lovers have forgotten you,They do not seek you;For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19682AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19682AA\"></sup>wounded you with the wound of an enemy,With the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19682AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19682AB\"></sup>punishment of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19682AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19682AC\"></sup>cruel one,Because your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19682AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19682AD\"></sup>iniquity is great<i>And</i> your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19682AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19682AE\"></sup>sins are numerous.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘Why do you cry out over your injury?Your pain is incurable.Because your iniquity is great<i>And</i> your sins are numerous,I have done these things to you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>‘Therefore all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19684AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19684AF\"></sup>devour you will be devoured;And all your adversaries, every one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19684AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19684AG\"></sup>will go into captivity;And those who plunder you will be for plunder,And all who prey upon you I will give for prey.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘For I will restore you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19685AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19685AH\"></sup>healthAnd I will heal you of your wounds,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘Because they have called you an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19685AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19685AI\"></sup>outcast, saying:“It is Zion; no one cares for her.”’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19686AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19686AJ\"></sup>restore the fortunes of the tents of JacobAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19686AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19686AK\"></sup>have compassion on his dwelling places;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19686AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19686AL\"></sup>city will be rebuilt on its ruin,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19686AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19686AM\"></sup>palace will stand on its rightful place.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘From them will proceed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19687AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19687AN\"></sup>thanksgivingAnd the voice of those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19687AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19687AO\"></sup>celebrate;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19687AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19687AP\"></sup>multiply them and they will not be diminished;I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19687AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19687AQ\"></sup>honor them and they will not be insignificant.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>‘Their children also will be as formerly,And their congregation shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19688AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19688AR\"></sup>established before Me;And I will punish all their oppressors.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>‘Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19689AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19689AS\"></sup>leader shall be one of them,And their ruler shall come forth from their midst;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19689AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19689AT\"></sup>bring him near and he shall approach Me;For who would dare to risk his life to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19689AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19689AU\"></sup>approach Me?’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>‘You shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19690AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19690AV\"></sup>My people,And I will be your God.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19691AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19691AW\"></sup>tempest of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!Wrath has gone forth,A sweeping tempest;It will burst on the head of the wicked.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19692AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19692AX\"></sup>fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not turn backUntil He has performed and until He has accomplishedThe intent of His heart;In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19692AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19692AY\"></sup>latter days you will understand this."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>“At that time,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I will be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19693A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19693A\"></sup>God of all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19693B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19693B\"></sup>families of Israel, and they shall be My people.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“The people who survived the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19694C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19694C\"></sup>Found grace in the wilderness—Israel, when it went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19694D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19694D\"></sup>find its rest.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> appeared to him from afar, <i>saying</i>,“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19695E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19695E\"></sup>loved you with an everlasting love;Therefore I have drawn you with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19695F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19695F\"></sup>lovingkindness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19696G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19696G\"></sup>Again I will build you and you will be rebuilt,O virgin of Israel!Again you will take up your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19696H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19696H\"></sup>tambourines,And go forth to the dances of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19696I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19696I\"></sup>merrymakers.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Again you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19697J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19697J\"></sup>plant vineyardsOn the hills of Samaria;The planters will plantAnd will enjoy <i>them</i>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For there will be a day when watchmenOn the hills of Ephraim call out,‘Arise, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19698K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19698K\"></sup>let us go up <i>to</i> Zion,To the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19699L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19699L\"></sup>Sing aloud with gladness for Jacob,And shout among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19699M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19699M\"></sup>chief of the nations;Proclaim, give praise and say,‘O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19699N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19699N\"></sup>save Your people,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19699O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19699O\"></sup>remnant of Israel.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19700P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19700P\"></sup>bringing them from the north country,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19700Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19700Q\"></sup>gather them from the remote parts of the earth,Among them the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19700R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19700R\"></sup>blind and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19700S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19700S\"></sup>lame,The woman with child and she who is in labor with child, together;A great company, they will return here.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19701T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19701T\"></sup>With weeping they will come,And by supplication I will lead them;I will make them walk by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19701U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19701U\"></sup>streams of waters,On a straight path in which they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19701V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19701V\"></sup>not stumble;For I am a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19701W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19701W\"></sup>father to Israel,And Ephraim is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19701X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19701X\"></sup>My firstborn.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O nations,And declare in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19702Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19702Y\"></sup>coastlands afar off,And say, “He who scattered Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19702Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19702Z\"></sup>gather himAnd keep him as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19702AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19702AA\"></sup>shepherd keeps his flock.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19703AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19703AB\"></sup>ransomed JacobAnd redeemed him from the hand of him who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19703AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19703AC\"></sup>stronger than he.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AD\"></sup>come and shout for joy on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AE\"></sup>height of Zion,And they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AF\"></sup>radiant over the bounty of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—Over the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AG\"></sup>grain and the new wine and the oil,And over the young of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AH\"></sup>flock and the herd;And their life will be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AI\"></sup>watered garden,And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19704AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19704AJ\"></sup>never languish again.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Then the virgin will rejoice in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19705AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19705AK\"></sup>dance,And the young men and the old, together,For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19705AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19705AL\"></sup>turn their mourning into joyAnd will comfort them and give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19705AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19705AM\"></sup>joy for their sorrow.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I will fill the soul of the priests with abundance,And My people will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19706AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19706AN\"></sup>satisfied with My goodness,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19707AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19707AO\"></sup>A voice is heard in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19707AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19707AP\"></sup>Ramah,Lamentation <i>and</i> bitter weeping.Rachel is weeping for her children;She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19707AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19707AQ\"></sup>refuses to be comforted for her children,Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19707AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19707AR\"></sup>they are no more.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19708AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19708AS\"></sup>Restrain your voice from weepingAnd your eyes from tears;For your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19708AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19708AT\"></sup>work will be rewarded,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19708AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19708AU\"></sup>return from the land of the enemy.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19709AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19709AV\"></sup>hope for your future,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And <i>your</i> children will return to their own territory.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I have surely heard Ephraim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19710AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19710AW\"></sup>grieving,‘You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19710AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19710AX\"></sup>chastised me, and I was chastised,Like an untrained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19710AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19710AY\"></sup>calf;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19710AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19710AZ\"></sup>Bring me back that I may be restored,For You are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘For after I turned back, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19711BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19711BA\"></sup>repented;And after I was instructed, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19711BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19711BB\"></sup>smote on <i>my</i> thigh;I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19711BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19711BC\"></sup>ashamed and also humiliatedBecause I bore the reproach of my youth.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19712BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19712BD\"></sup>Ephraim My dear son?Is he a delightful child?Indeed, as often as I have spoken against him,I certainly <i>still</i> remember him;Therefore My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19712BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19712BE\"></sup>heart yearns for him;I will surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19712BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19712BF\"></sup>have mercy on him,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Set up for yourself roadmarks,Place for yourself guideposts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19713BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19713BG\"></sup>Direct your mind to the highway,The way by which you went.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19713BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19713BH\"></sup>Return, O virgin of Israel,Return to these your cities.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“How long will you go here and there,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19714BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19714BI\"></sup>faithless daughter?For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has created a new thing in the earth—A woman will encompass a man.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Once again they will speak this word in the land of Judah and in its cities when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19715BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19715BJ\"></sup>restore their fortunes,‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> bless you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19715BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19715BK\"></sup>abode of righteousness,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19715BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19715BL\"></sup>holy hill!’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Judah and all its cities will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19716BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19716BM\"></sup>dwell together in it, the farmer and they who go about with flocks.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19717BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19717BN\"></sup>For I satisfy the weary ones and refresh everyone who languishes.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At this I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19718BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19718BO\"></sup>awoke and looked, and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19718BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19718BP\"></sup>sleep was pleasant to me.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Behold, days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19719BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19719BQ\"></sup>sow the house of Israel and the house of Judah with the seed of man and with the seed of beast.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>As I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19720BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19720BR\"></sup>watched over them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19720BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19720BS\"></sup>pluck up, to break down, to overthrow, to destroy and to bring disaster, so I will watch over them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19720BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19720BT\"></sup>build and to plant,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“In those days they will not say again,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19721BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19721BU\"></sup>The fathers have eaten sour grapes,And the children’s teeth are set on edge.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19722BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19722BV\"></sup>everyone will die for his own iniquity; each man who eats the sour grapes, his teeth will be set on edge.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19723BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19723BW\"></sup>Behold, days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when I will make a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19723BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19723BX\"></sup>new covenant with the house of Israel and with the house of Judah,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>not like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19724BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19724BY\"></sup>covenant which I made with their fathers in the day I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19724BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19724BZ\"></sup>took them by the hand to bring them out of the land of Egypt, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19724CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19724CA\"></sup>covenant which they broke, although I was a husband to them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19725CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19725CB\"></sup>this is the covenant which I will make with the house of Israel after those days,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19725CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19725CC\"></sup>I will put My law within them and on their heart I will write it; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19725CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19725CD\"></sup>I will be their God, and they shall be My people.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19726CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19726CE\"></sup>not teach again, each man his neighbor and each man his brother, saying, ‘Know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ for they will all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19726CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19726CF\"></sup>know Me, from the least of them to the greatest of them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “for I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19726CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19726CG\"></sup>forgive their iniquity, and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19726CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19726CH\"></sup>sin I will remember no more.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19727CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19727CI\"></sup>gives the sun for light by dayAnd the fixed order of the moon and the stars for light by night,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19727CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19727CJ\"></sup>stirs up the sea so that its waves roar;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19727CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19727CK\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name:",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19728CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19728CL\"></sup>If this fixed order departsFrom before Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Then the offspring of Israel also will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19728CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19728CM\"></sup>ceaseFrom being a nation before Me forever.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19729CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19729CN\"></sup>If the heavens above can be measuredAnd the foundations of the earth searched out below,Then I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19729CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19729CO\"></sup>cast off all the offspring of IsraelFor all that they have done,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“Behold, days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19730CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19730CP\"></sup>city will be rebuilt for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19730CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19730CQ\"></sup>Tower of Hananel to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19730CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19730CR\"></sup>Corner Gate.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19731CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19731CS\"></sup>measuring line will go out farther straight ahead to the hill Gareb; then it will turn to Goah.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19732CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19732CT\"></sup>the whole valley of the dead bodies and of the ashes, and all the fields as far as the brook <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19732CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19732CU\"></sup>Kidron, to the corner of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19732CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19732CV\"></sup>Horse Gate toward the east, shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19732CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19732CW\"></sup>holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; it will not be plucked up or overthrown anymore forever.”"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19733A\"></sup>tenth year of Zedekiah king of Judah, which was the eighteenth year of Nebuchadnezzar.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now at that time the army of the king of Babylon was besieging Jerusalem, and Jeremiah the prophet was shut up in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19734B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19734B\"></sup>court of the guard, which <i>was in</i> the house of the king of Judah,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>because Zedekiah king of Judah had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19735C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19735C\"></sup>shut him up, saying, “Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19735D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19735D\"></sup>prophesy, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19735E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19735E\"></sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19735F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19735F\"></sup>give this city into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he will take it;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and Zedekiah king of Judah will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19736G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19736G\"></sup>not escape out of the hand of the Chaldeans, but he will surely be given into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19736H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19736H\"></sup>speak with him face to face and see him eye to eye;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19737I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19737I\"></sup>take Zedekiah to Babylon, and he will be there until I visit him,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “If you fight against the Chaldeans, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19737J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19737J\"></sup>not succeed”’?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And Jeremiah said, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘Behold, Hanamel the son of Shallum your uncle is coming to you, saying, “Buy for yourself my field which is at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19739K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19739K\"></sup>Anathoth, for you have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19739L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19739L\"></sup>right of redemption to buy <i>it</i>.”’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Hanamel my uncle’s son came to me in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19740M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19740M\"></sup>court of the guard according to the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said to me, ‘Buy my field, please, that is at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19740N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19740N\"></sup>Anathoth, which is in the land of Benjamin; for you have the right of possession and the redemption is yours; buy <i>it</i> for yourself.’ Then I knew that this was the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19740O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19740O\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“I bought the field which was at Anathoth from Hanamel my uncle’s son, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19741P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19741P\"></sup>weighed out the silver for him, seventeen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19741Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19741Q\"></sup>shekels of silver.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19742R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19742R\"></sup>signed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19742S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19742S\"></sup>sealed the deed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19742T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19742T\"></sup>called in witnesses, and weighed out the silver on the scales.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I took the deeds of purchase, both the sealed <i>copy containing</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19743U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19743U\"></sup>terms and conditions and the open <i>copy</i>;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and I gave the deed of purchase to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19744V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19744V\"></sup>Baruch the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19744W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19744W\"></sup>Neriah, the son of Mahseiah, in the sight of Hanamel my uncle’s <i>son</i> and in the sight of the witnesses who signed the deed of purchase, before all the Jews who were sitting in the court of the guard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I commanded Baruch in their presence, saying,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Take these deeds, this sealed deed of purchase and this open deed, and put them in an earthenware jar, that they may last a long time.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19747X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19747X\"></sup>Houses and fields and vineyards will again be bought in this land.”’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“After I had given the deed of purchase to Baruch the son of Neriah, then I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19748Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19748Y\"></sup>prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19749Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19749Z\"></sup>Ah Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Behold, You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19749AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19749AA\"></sup>made the heavens and the earth by Your great power and by Your outstretched arm! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19749AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19749AB\"></sup>Nothing is too difficult for You,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19750AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19750AC\"></sup>shows lovingkindness to thousands, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19750AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19750AD\"></sup>repays the iniquity of fathers into the bosom of their children after them, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19750AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19750AE\"></sup>great and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19750AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19750AF\"></sup>mighty God. The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19750AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19750AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19751AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19751AH\"></sup>great in counsel and mighty in deed, whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19751AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19751AI\"></sup>eyes are open to all the ways of the sons of men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19751AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19751AJ\"></sup>giving to everyone according to his ways and according to the fruit of his deeds;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19752AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19752AK\"></sup>set signs and wonders in the land of Egypt, <i>and</i> even to this day both in Israel and among mankind; and You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19752AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19752AL\"></sup>made a name for Yourself, as at this day.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19753AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19753AM\"></sup>brought Your people Israel out of the land of Egypt with signs and with wonders, and with a strong hand and with an outstretched arm and with great terror;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and gave them this land, which You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19754AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19754AN\"></sup>swore to their forefathers to give them, a land flowing with milk and honey.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19755AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19755AO\"></sup>came in and took possession of it, but they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19755AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19755AP\"></sup>did not obey Your voice or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19755AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19755AQ\"></sup>walk in Your law; they have done nothing of all that You commanded them to do; therefore You have made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19755AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19755AR\"></sup>all this calamity come upon them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19756AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19756AS\"></sup>siege ramps have reached the city to take it; and the city is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19756AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19756AT\"></sup>given into the hand of the Chaldeans who fight against it, because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19756AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19756AU\"></sup>sword, the famine and the pestilence; and what You have spoken has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19756AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19756AV\"></sup>come to pass; and behold, You see <i>it</i>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>You have said to me, O Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Buy for yourself the field with money and call in witnesses”—although the city is given into the hand of the Chaldeans.’”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah, saying,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Behold, I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19759AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19759AW\"></sup>God of all flesh; is anything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19759AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19759AX\"></sup>too difficult for Me?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19760AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19760AY\"></sup>give this city into the hand of the Chaldeans and into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and he will take it.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The Chaldeans who are fighting against this city will enter and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19761AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19761AZ\"></sup>set this city on fire and burn it, with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19761BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19761BA\"></sup>houses where <i>people</i> have offered incense to Baal on their roofs and poured out drink offerings to other gods to provoke Me to anger.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Indeed the sons of Israel and the sons of Judah have been doing only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19762BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19762BB\"></sup>evil in My sight from their youth; for the sons of Israel have been only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19762BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19762BC\"></sup>provoking Me to anger by the work of their hands,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Indeed this city has been to Me <i>a</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19763BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19763BD\"></sup><i>provocation of</i> My anger and My wrath from the day that they built it, even to this day, so that it should be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19763BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19763BE\"></sup>removed from before My face,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>because of all the evil of the sons of Israel and the sons of Judah which they have done to provoke Me to anger—they, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19764BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19764BF\"></sup>kings, their leaders, their priests, their prophets, the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>They have turned <i>their</i> back to Me and not <i>their</i> face; though <i>I</i> taught them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19765BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19765BG\"></sup>teaching again and again, they would not listen and receive instruction.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19766BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19766BH\"></sup>put their detestable things in the house which is called by My name, to defile it.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They built the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19767BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19767BI\"></sup>high places of Baal that are in the valley of Ben-hinnom to cause their sons and their daughters to pass through <i>the fire</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19767BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19767BJ\"></sup>Molech, which I had not commanded them nor had it entered My mind that they should do this abomination, to cause Judah to sin.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Now therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel concerning this city of which you say, ‘It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19768BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19768BK\"></sup>given into the hand of the king of Babylon by sword, by famine and by pestilence.’",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19769BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19769BL\"></sup>gather them out of all the lands to which I have driven them in My anger, in My wrath and in great indignation; and I will bring them back to this place and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19769BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19769BM\"></sup>make them dwell in safety.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>They shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19770BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19770BN\"></sup>My people, and I will be their God;",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19771BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19771BO\"></sup>give them one heart and one way, that they may fear Me always, for their own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19771BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19771BP\"></sup>good and for <i>the good of</i> their children after them.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>I will make an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19772BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19772BQ\"></sup>everlasting covenant with them that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19772BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19772BR\"></sup>not turn away from them, to do them good; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19772BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19772BS\"></sup>put the fear of Me in their hearts so that they will not turn away from Me.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19773BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19773BT\"></sup>rejoice over them to do them good and will faithfully <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19773BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19773BU\"></sup>plant them in this land with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19773BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19773BV\"></sup>all My heart and with all My soul.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19774BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19774BW\"></sup>Just as I brought all this great disaster on this people, so I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19774BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19774BX\"></sup>bring on them all the good that I am promising them.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19775BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19775BY\"></sup>Fields will be bought in this land of which you say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19775BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19775BZ\"></sup>It is a desolation, without man or beast; it is given into the hand of the Chaldeans.”",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Men will buy fields for money, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19776CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19776CA\"></sup>sign and seal deeds, and call in witnesses in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19776CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19776CB\"></sup>land of Benjamin, in the environs of Jerusalem, in the cities of Judah, in the cities of the hill country, in the cities of the lowland and in the cities of the Negev; for I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19776CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19776CC\"></sup>restore their fortunes,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah the second time, while he was still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19777A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19777A\"></sup>confined in the court of the guard, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19778B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19778B\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who made <i>the earth</i>, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who formed it to establish it, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19778C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19778C\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is His name,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19779D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19779D\"></sup>Call to Me and I will answer you, and I will tell you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19779E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19779E\"></sup>great and mighty things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19779F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19779F\"></sup>which you do not know.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19780G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19780G\"></sup>houses of this city, and concerning the houses of the kings of Judah which are broken down <i>to make a defense</i> against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19780H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19780H\"></sup>siege ramps and against the sword,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>‘While <i>they</i> are coming to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19781I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19781I\"></sup>fight with the Chaldeans and to fill them with the corpses of men whom I have slain in My anger and in My wrath, and I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19781J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19781J\"></sup>hidden My face from this city because of all their wickedness:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Behold, I will bring to it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19782K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19782K\"></sup>health and healing, and I will heal them; and I will reveal to them an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19782L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19782L\"></sup>abundance of peace and truth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19783M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19783M\"></sup>restore the fortunes of Judah and the fortunes of Israel and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19783N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19783N\"></sup>rebuild them as they were at first.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19784O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19784O\"></sup>cleanse them from all their iniquity by which they have sinned against Me, and I will pardon all their iniquities by which they have sinned against Me and by which they have transgressed against Me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It will be to Me a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19785P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19785P\"></sup>name of joy, praise and glory before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19785Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19785Q\"></sup>all the nations of the earth which will hear of all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19785R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19785R\"></sup>good that I do for them, and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19785S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19785S\"></sup>fear and tremble because of all the good and all the peace that I make for it.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Yet again there will be heard in this place, of which you say, “It is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19786T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19786T\"></sup>waste, without man and without beast,” <i>that is</i>, in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem that are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19786U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19786U\"></sup>desolate, without man and without inhabitant and without beast,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>the voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19787V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19787V\"></sup>joy and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride, the voice of those who say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19787W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19787W\"></sup>Give thanks to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is good,For His lovingkindness is everlasting”;<i>and of those</i> who bring a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19787X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19787X\"></sup>thank offering into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. For I will restore the fortunes of the land as they were at first,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘There will again be in this place which is waste, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19788Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19788Y\"></sup>without man or beast, and in all its cities, a habitation of shepherds who rest their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19788Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19788Z\"></sup>flocks.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19789AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19789AA\"></sup>cities of the hill country, in the cities of the lowland, in the cities of the Negev, in the land of Benjamin, in the environs of Jerusalem and in the cities of Judah, the flocks will again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19789AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19789AB\"></sup>pass under the hands of the one who numbers them,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19790AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19790AC\"></sup>days are coming,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘when I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19790AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19790AD\"></sup>fulfill the good word which I have spoken concerning the house of Israel and the house of Judah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In those days and at that time I will cause a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19791AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19791AE\"></sup>righteous Branch of David to spring forth; and He shall execute <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19791AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19791AF\"></sup>justice and righteousness on the earth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19792AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19792AG\"></sup>Judah will be saved and Jerusalem will dwell in safety; and this is <i>the name</i> by which she will be called: the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19792AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19792AH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our righteousness.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘David shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19793AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19793AI\"></sup>never lack a man to sit on the throne of the house of Israel;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19794AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19794AJ\"></sup>Levitical priests shall never lack a man before Me to offer burnt offerings, to burn grain offerings and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19794AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19794AK\"></sup>prepare sacrifices continually.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah, saying,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘If you can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19796AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19796AL\"></sup>break My covenant for the day and My covenant for the night, so that day and night will not be at their appointed time,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19797AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19797AM\"></sup>My covenant may also be broken with David My servant so that he will not have a son to reign on his throne, and with the Levitical priests, My ministers.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>As the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19798AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19798AN\"></sup>host of heaven cannot be counted and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19798AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19798AO\"></sup>sand of the sea cannot be measured, so I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19798AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19798AP\"></sup>multiply the descendants of David My servant and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19798AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19798AQ\"></sup>Levites who minister to Me.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah, saying,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Have you not observed what this people have spoken, saying, ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19800AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19800AR\"></sup>two families which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> chose, He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19800AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19800AS\"></sup>rejected them’? Thus they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19800AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19800AT\"></sup>despise My people, no longer are they as a nation in their sight.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘If My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19801AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19801AU\"></sup>covenant <i>for</i> day and night <i>stand</i> not, <i>and</i> the fixed patterns of heaven and earth I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19801AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19801AV\"></sup>not established,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19802AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19802AW\"></sup>reject the descendants of Jacob and David My servant, not taking from his descendants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19802AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19802AX\"></sup>rulers over the descendants of Abraham, Isaac and Jacob. But I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19802AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19802AY\"></sup>restore their fortunes and will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19802AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19802AZ\"></sup>mercy on them.’”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19803A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19803A\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and all his army, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19803B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19803B\"></sup>all the kingdoms of the earth that were under his dominion and all the peoples, were fighting against Jerusalem and against all its cities, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19804C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19804C\"></sup>Go and speak to Zedekiah king of Judah and say to him: “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19804D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19804D\"></sup>I am giving this city into the hand of the king of Babylon, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19804E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19804E\"></sup>he will burn it with fire.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19805F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19805F\"></sup>You will not escape from his hand, for you will surely be captured and delivered into his hand; and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19805G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19805G\"></sup>see the king of Babylon eye to eye, and he will speak with you face to face, and you will go to Babylon.’”’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O Zedekiah king of Judah! Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning you, ‘You will not die by the sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You will die in peace; and as <i>spices</i> were burned for your fathers, the former kings who were before you, so they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19807H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19807H\"></sup>burn <i>spices</i> for you; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19807I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19807I\"></sup>they will lament for you, “Alas, lord!”’ For I have spoken the word,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Jeremiah the prophet spoke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19808J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19808J\"></sup>all these words to Zedekiah king of Judah in Jerusalem",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>when the army of the king of Babylon was fighting against Jerusalem and against all the remaining cities of Judah, <i>that is</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19809K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19809K\"></sup>Lachish and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19809L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19809L\"></sup>Azekah, for they <i>alone</i> remained as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19809M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19809M\"></sup>fortified cities among the cities of Judah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> after King Zedekiah had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19810N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19810N\"></sup>made a covenant with all the people who were in Jerusalem to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19810O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19810O\"></sup>proclaim release to them:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>that each man should set free his male servant and each man his female servant, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19811P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19811P\"></sup>Hebrew man or a Hebrew woman; so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19811Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19811Q\"></sup>no one should keep them, a Jew his brother, in bondage.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19812R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19812R\"></sup>officials and all the people obeyed who had entered into the covenant that each man should set free his male servant and each man his female servant, so that no one should keep them any longer in bondage; they obeyed, and set <i>them free</i>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But afterward they turned around and took back the male servants and the female servants whom they had set free, and brought them into subjection for male servants and for female servants.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel, ‘I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19815S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19815S\"></sup>made a covenant with your forefathers in the day that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19815T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19815T\"></sup>brought them out of the land of Egypt, from the house of bondage, saying,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19816U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19816U\"></sup>At the end of seven years each of you shall set free his Hebrew brother who has been sold to you and has served you six years, you shall send him out free from you; but your forefathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19816V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19816V\"></sup>did not obey Me or incline their ear to Me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Although recently you <i>had</i> turned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19817W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19817W\"></sup>done what is right in My sight, each man proclaiming release to his neighbor, and you had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19817X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19817X\"></sup>made a covenant before Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19817Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19817Y\"></sup>in the house which is called by My name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Yet you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19818Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19818Z\"></sup>turned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19818AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19818AA\"></sup>profaned My name, and each man took back his male servant and each man his female servant whom you had set free according to their desire, and you brought them into subjection to be your male servants and female servants.”’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘You have not obeyed Me in proclaiming release each man to his brother and each man to his neighbor. Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19819AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19819AB\"></sup>proclaiming a release to you,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19819AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19819AC\"></sup>sword, to the pestilence and to the famine; and I will make you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19819AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19819AD\"></sup>terror to all the kingdoms of the earth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will give the men who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19820AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19820AE\"></sup>transgressed My covenant, who have not fulfilled the words of the covenant which they made before Me, <i>when</i> they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19820AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19820AF\"></sup>cut the calf in two and passed between its parts—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19821AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19821AG\"></sup>officials of Judah and the officials of Jerusalem, the court officers and the priests and all the people of the land who passed between the parts of the calf—",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I will give them into the hand of their enemies and into the hand of those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19822AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19822AH\"></sup>seek their life. And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19822AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19822AI\"></sup>dead bodies will be food for the birds of the sky and the beasts of the earth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19823AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19823AJ\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah and his officials I will give into the hand of their enemies and into the hand of those who seek their life, and into the hand of the army of the king of Babylon which has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19823AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19823AK\"></sup>gone away from you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, I am going to command,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and I will bring them back to this city; and they will fight against it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19824AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19824AL\"></sup>take it and burn it with fire; and I will make the cities of Judah a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19824AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19824AM\"></sup>desolation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19824AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19824AN\"></sup>without inhabitant.’”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19825A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19825A\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go to the house of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19826B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19826B\"></sup>Rechabites and speak to them, and bring them into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, into one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19826C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19826C\"></sup>chambers, and give them wine to drink.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I took Jaazaniah the son of Jeremiah, son of Habazziniah, and his brothers and all his sons and the whole house of the Rechabites,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and I brought them into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, into the chamber of the sons of Hanan the son of Igdaliah, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19828D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19828D\"></sup>man of God, which was near the chamber of the officials, which was above the chamber of Maaseiah the son of Shallum, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19828E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19828E\"></sup>the doorkeeper.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I set before the men of the house of the Rechabites pitchers full of wine and cups; and I said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19829F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19829F\"></sup>Drink wine!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But they said, “We will not drink wine, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19830G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19830G\"></sup>Jonadab the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19830H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19830H\"></sup>Rechab, our father, commanded us, saying, ‘You shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19830I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19830I\"></sup>not drink wine, you or your sons, forever.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You shall not build a house, and you shall not sow seed and you shall not plant a vineyard or own one; but in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19831J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19831J\"></sup>tents you shall dwell all your days, that you may live <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19831K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19831K\"></sup>many days in the land where you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19831L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19831L\"></sup>sojourn.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19832M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19832M\"></sup>obeyed the voice of Jonadab the son of Rechab, our father, in all that he commanded us, not to drink wine all our days, we, our wives, our sons or our daughters,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>nor to build ourselves houses to dwell in; and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19833N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19833N\"></sup>do not have vineyard or field or seed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We have only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19834O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19834O\"></sup>dwelt in tents, and have obeyed and have done according to all that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19834P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19834P\"></sup>Jonadab our father commanded us.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19835Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19835Q\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon came up against the land, we said, ‘Come and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19835R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19835R\"></sup>go to Jerusalem before the army of the Chaldeans and before the army of the Arameans.’ So we have dwelt in Jerusalem.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah, saying,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Go and say to the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19837S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19837S\"></sup>Will you not receive instruction by listening to My words?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19838T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19838T\"></sup>words of Jonadab the son of Rechab, which he commanded his sons not to drink wine, are observed. So they do not drink <i>wine</i> to this day, for they have obeyed their father’s command. But I have spoken to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19838U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19838U\"></sup>again and again; yet you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19838V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19838V\"></sup>not listened to Me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Also I have sent to you all My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19839W\"></sup>servants the prophets, sending <i>them</i> again and again, saying: ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19839X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19839X\"></sup>Turn now every man from his evil way and amend your deeds, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19839Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19839Y\"></sup>do not go after other gods to worship them. Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19839Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19839Z\"></sup>dwell in the land which I have given to you and to your forefathers; but you have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19839AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19839AA\"></sup>inclined your ear or listened to Me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Indeed, the sons of Jonadab the son of Rechab have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19840AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19840AB\"></sup>observed the command of their father which he commanded them, but this people has not listened to Me.’”’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19841AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19841AC\"></sup>I am bringing on Judah and on all the inhabitants of Jerusalem all the disaster that I have pronounced against them; because I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19841AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19841AD\"></sup>spoke to them but they did not listen, and I have called them but they did not answer.’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to the house of the Rechabites, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19842AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19842AE\"></sup>obeyed the command of Jonadab your father, kept all his commands and done according to all that he commanded you;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Jonadab the son of Rechab <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19843AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19843AF\"></sup>shall not lack a man to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19843AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19843AG\"></sup>stand before Me always.”’”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19844A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19844A\"></sup>fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Take a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19845B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19845B\"></sup>scroll and write on it all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19845C\"></sup>words which I have spoken to you concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19845D\"></sup>Israel and concerning Judah, and concerning all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19845E\"></sup>nations, from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19845F\"></sup>day I <i>first</i> spoke to you, from the days of Josiah, even to this day.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19846G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19846G\"></sup>Perhaps the house of Judah will hear all the calamity which I plan to bring on them, in order that every man will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19846H\"></sup>turn from his evil way; then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19846I\"></sup>forgive their iniquity and their sin.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then Jeremiah called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19847J\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah, and Baruch wrote on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19847K\"></sup>scroll at the dictation of Jeremiah all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which He had spoken to him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Jeremiah commanded Baruch, saying, “I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19848L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19848L\"></sup>restricted; I cannot go into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So you go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19849M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19849M\"></sup>read from the scroll which you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19849N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19849N\"></sup>written at my dictation the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to the people in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19849O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19849O\"></sup>fast day. And also you shall read them to all <i>the people of</i> Judah who come from their cities.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19850P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19850P\"></sup>Perhaps their supplication will come before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and everyone will turn from his evil way, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19850Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19850Q\"></sup>great is the anger and the wrath that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has pronounced against this people.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Baruch the son of Neriah did according to all that Jeremiah the prophet commanded him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19851R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19851R\"></sup>reading from the book the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19852S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19852S\"></sup>fifth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19852T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19852T\"></sup>ninth month, all the people in Jerusalem and all the people who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19852U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19852U\"></sup>came from the cities of Judah to Jerusalem proclaimed a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19852V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19852V\"></sup>fast before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Baruch read from the book the words of Jeremiah in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19853W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19853W\"></sup>chamber of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19853X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19853X\"></sup>Gemariah the son of Shaphan the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19853Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19853Y\"></sup>scribe, in the upper court, at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19853Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19853Z\"></sup>entry of the New Gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house, to all the people.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19854AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19854AA\"></sup>Micaiah the son of Gemariah, the son of Shaphan, had heard all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the book,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>he went down to the king’s house, into the scribe’s chamber. And behold, all the officials were sitting there—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19855AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19855AB\"></sup>Elishama the scribe, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19855AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19855AC\"></sup>Delaiah the son of Shemaiah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19855AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19855AD\"></sup>Elnathan the son of Achbor, and Gemariah the son of Shaphan, and Zedekiah the son of Hananiah, and all the <i>other</i> officials.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Micaiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19856AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19856AE\"></sup>declared to them all the words that he had heard when Baruch read from the book to the people.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then all the officials sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19857AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19857AF\"></sup>Jehudi the son of Nethaniah, the son of Shelemiah, the son of Cushi, to Baruch, saying, “Take in your hand the scroll from which you have read to the people and come.” So Baruch the son of Neriah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19857AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19857AG\"></sup>took the scroll in his hand and went to them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They said to him, “Sit down, please, and read it to us.” So Baruch <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19858AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19858AH\"></sup>read it to them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When they had heard all the words, they turned in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19859AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19859AI\"></sup>fear one to another and said to Baruch, “We will surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19859AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19859AJ\"></sup>report all these words to the king.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they asked Baruch, saying, “Tell us, please, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19860AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19860AK\"></sup>how did you write all these words? <i>Was it</i> at his dictation?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then Baruch said to them, “He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19861AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19861AL\"></sup>dictated all these words to me, and I wrote them with ink on the book.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the officials said to Baruch, “Go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19862AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19862AM\"></sup>hide yourself, you and Jeremiah, and do not let anyone know where you are.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So they went to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19863AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19863AN\"></sup>king in the court, but they had deposited the scroll in the chamber of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19863AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19863AO\"></sup>Elishama the scribe, and they reported all the words to the king.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then the king sent Jehudi to get the scroll, and he took it out of the chamber of Elishama the scribe. And Jehudi <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19864AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19864AP\"></sup>read it to the king as well as to all the officials who stood beside the king.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now the king was sitting in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19865AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19865AQ\"></sup>winter house in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19865AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19865AR\"></sup>ninth month, with <i>a fire</i> burning in the brazier before him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When Jehudi had read three or four columns, <i>the king</i> cut it with a scribe’s knife and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19866AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19866AS\"></sup>threw <i>it</i> into the fire that was in the brazier, until all the scroll was consumed in the fire that was in the brazier.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Yet the king and all his servants who heard all these words were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19867AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19867AT\"></sup>not afraid, nor did they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19867AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19867AU\"></sup>rend their garments.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Even though Elnathan and Delaiah and Gemariah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19868AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19868AV\"></sup>pleaded with the king not to burn the scroll, he would not listen to them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And the king commanded Jerahmeel the king’s son, Seraiah the son of Azriel, and Shelemiah the son of Abdeel to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19869AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19869AW\"></sup>seize Baruch the scribe and Jeremiah the prophet, but the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19869AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19869AX\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hid them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah after the king had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19870AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19870AY\"></sup>burned the scroll and the words which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19870AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19870AZ\"></sup>Baruch had written at the dictation of Jeremiah, saying,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19871BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19871BA\"></sup>Take again another scroll and write on it all the former words that were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19871BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19871BB\"></sup>on the first scroll which Jehoiakim the king of Judah burned.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And concerning Jehoiakim king of Judah you shall say, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19872BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19872BC\"></sup>burned this scroll, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19872BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19872BD\"></sup>Why have you written on it that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19872BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19872BE\"></sup>king of Babylon will certainly come and destroy this land, and will make man and beast to cease from it?’”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Jehoiakim king of Judah, “He shall have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19873BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19873BF\"></sup>no one to sit on the throne of David, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19873BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19873BG\"></sup>dead body shall be cast out to the heat of the day and the frost of the night.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19874BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19874BH\"></sup>punish him and his descendants and his servants for their iniquity, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19874BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19874BI\"></sup>bring on them and the inhabitants of Jerusalem and the men of Judah all the calamity that I have declared to them—but they did not listen.”’”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then Jeremiah took another scroll and gave it to Baruch the son of Neriah, the scribe, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19875BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19875BJ\"></sup>wrote on it at the dictation of Jeremiah all the words of the book which Jehoiakim king of Judah had burned in the fire; and many similar words were added to them."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19876A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19876A\"></sup>Zedekiah the son of Josiah whom Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19876B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19876B\"></sup>made king in the land of Judah, reigned as king in place of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19876C\"></sup>Coniah the son of Jehoiakim.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19877D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19877D\"></sup>neither he nor his servants nor the people of the land listened to the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which He spoke through Jeremiah the prophet.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19878E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19878E\"></sup>King Zedekiah sent Jehucal the son of Shelemiah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19878F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19878F\"></sup>Zephaniah the son of Maaseiah, the priest, to Jeremiah the prophet, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19878G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19878G\"></sup>Please pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God on our behalf.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now Jeremiah was <i>still</i> coming in and going out among the people, for they had not <i>yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19879H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19879H\"></sup>put him in the prison.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Meanwhile, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19880I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19880I\"></sup>Pharaoh’s army had set out from Egypt; and when the Chaldeans who had been besieging Jerusalem heard the report about them, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19880J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19880J\"></sup>lifted the <i>siege</i> from Jerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah the prophet, saying,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19882K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19882K\"></sup>Thus you are to say to the king of Judah, who sent you to Me to inquire of Me: “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19882L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19882L\"></sup>Pharaoh’s army which has come out for your assistance is going to return to its own land of Egypt.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Chaldeans will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19883M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19883M\"></sup>return and fight against this city, and they will capture it and burn it with fire.”’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19884N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19884N\"></sup>deceive yourselves, saying, “The Chaldeans will surely go away from us,” for they will not go.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19885O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19885O\"></sup>even if you had defeated the entire army of Chaldeans who were fighting against you, and there were <i>only</i> wounded men left among them, each man in his tent, they would rise up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19885P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19885P\"></sup>burn this city with fire.’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now it happened when the army of the Chaldeans had lifted <i>the siege</i> from Jerusalem because of Pharaoh’s army,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>that Jeremiah went out from Jerusalem to go to the land of Benjamin in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19887Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19887Q\"></sup>take possession of <i>some</i> property there among the people.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>While he was at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19888R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19888R\"></sup>Gate of Benjamin, a captain of the guard whose name was Irijah, the son of Shelemiah the son of Hananiah was there; and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19888S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19888S\"></sup>arrested Jeremiah the prophet, saying, “You are going over to the Chaldeans!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Jeremiah said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19889T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19889T\"></sup>A lie! I am not going over to the Chaldeans”; yet he would not listen to him. So Irijah arrested Jeremiah and brought him to the officials.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the officials were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19890U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19890U\"></sup>angry at Jeremiah and beat him, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19890V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19890V\"></sup>put him in jail in the house of Jonathan the scribe, which they had made into the prison.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For Jeremiah had come into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19891W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19891W\"></sup>dungeon, that is, the vaulted cell; and Jeremiah stayed there many days.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now King Zedekiah sent and took him <i>out</i>; and in his palace the king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19892X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19892X\"></sup>secretly asked him and said, “Is there a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19892Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19892Y\"></sup>word from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?” And Jeremiah said, “There is!” Then he said, “You will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19892Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19892Z\"></sup>given into the hand of the king of Babylon!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Moreover Jeremiah said to King Zedekiah, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19893AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19893AA\"></sup><i>In</i> what <i>way</i> have I sinned against you, or against your servants, or against this people, that you have put me in prison?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19894AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19894AB\"></sup>Where then are your prophets who prophesied to you, saying, ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19894AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19894AC\"></sup>king of Babylon will not come against you or against this land’?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But now, please listen, O my lord the king; please let my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19895AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19895AD\"></sup>petition come before you and do not make me return to the house of Jonathan the scribe, that I may not die there.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then King Zedekiah gave commandment, and they committed Jeremiah to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19896AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19896AE\"></sup>court of the guardhouse and gave him a loaf of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19896AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19896AF\"></sup>bread daily from the bakers’ street, until all the bread in the city was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19896AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19896AG\"></sup>gone. So Jeremiah remained in the court of the guardhouse."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>Now Shephatiah the son of Mattan, and Gedaliah the son of Pashhur, and Jucal the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19897A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19897A\"></sup>son of Shelemiah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19897B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19897B\"></sup>Pashhur the son of Malchijah heard the words that Jeremiah was speaking to all the people, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19898C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19898C\"></sup>stays in this city will die by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19898D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19898D\"></sup>sword and by famine and by pestilence, but he who goes out to the Chaldeans will live and have his <i>own</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19898E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19898E\"></sup>life as booty and stay alive.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘This city will certainly be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19899F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19899F\"></sup>given into the hand of the army of the king of Babylon and he will capture it.’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19900G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19900G\"></sup>officials said to the king, “Now let this man be put to death, inasmuch as he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19900H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19900H\"></sup>discouraging the men of war who are left in this city and all the people, by speaking such words to them; for this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19900I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19900I\"></sup>is not seeking the well-being of this people but rather their harm.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So King Zedekiah said, “Behold, he is in your hands; for the king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19901J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19901J\"></sup>can <i>do</i> nothing against you.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then they took Jeremiah and cast him into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19902K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19902K\"></sup>cistern <i>of</i> Malchijah the king’s son, which was in the court of the guardhouse; and they let Jeremiah down with ropes. Now in the cistern there was no water but only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19902L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19902L\"></sup>mud, and Jeremiah sank into the mud.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19903M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19903M\"></sup>Ebed-melech the Ethiopian, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19903N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19903N\"></sup>eunuch, while he was in the king’s palace, heard that they had put Jeremiah into the cistern. Now the king was sitting in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19903O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19903O\"></sup>Gate of Benjamin;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and Ebed-melech went out from the king’s palace and spoke to the king, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“My lord the king, these men have acted wickedly in all that they have done to Jeremiah the prophet whom they have cast into the cistern; and he will die right where he is because of the famine, for there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19905P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19905P\"></sup>no more bread in the city.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the king commanded Ebed-melech the Ethiopian, saying, “Take thirty men from here under your authority and bring up Jeremiah the prophet from the cistern before he dies.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So Ebed-melech took the men under his authority and went into the king’s palace to <i>a place</i> beneath the storeroom and took from there worn-out clothes and worn-out rags and let them down by ropes into the cistern to Jeremiah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Ebed-melech the Ethiopian said to Jeremiah, “Now put these worn-out clothes and rags under your armpits under the ropes”; and Jeremiah did so.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So they pulled Jeremiah up with the ropes and lifted him out of the cistern, and Jeremiah stayed in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19909Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19909Q\"></sup>court of the guardhouse.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then King Zedekiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19910R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19910R\"></sup>sent and had Jeremiah the prophet brought to him at the third entrance that is in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; and the king said to Jeremiah, “I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19910S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19910S\"></sup>ask you something; do not hide anything from me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to Zedekiah, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19911T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19911T\"></sup>If I tell you, will you not certainly put me to death? Besides, if I give you advice, you will not listen to me.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But King Zedekiah swore to Jeremiah in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19912U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19912U\"></sup>secret saying, “As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who made this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19912V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19912V\"></sup>life for us, surely I will not put you to death nor will I give you over to the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19912W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19912W\"></sup>these men who are seeking your life.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to Zedekiah, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19913X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19913X\"></sup>God of hosts, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19913Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19913Y\"></sup>God of Israel, ‘If you will indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19913Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19913Z\"></sup>go out to the officers of the king of Babylon, then you will live, this city will not be burned with fire, and you and your household will survive.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19914AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19914AA\"></sup>not go out to the officers of the king of Babylon, then this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19914AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19914AB\"></sup>will be given over to the hand of the Chaldeans; and they will burn it with fire, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19914AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19914AC\"></sup>you yourself will not escape from their hand.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then King Zedekiah said to Jeremiah, “I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19915AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19915AD\"></sup>dread the Jews who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19915AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19915AE\"></sup>gone over to the Chaldeans, for they may give me over into their hand and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19915AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19915AF\"></sup>abuse me.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But Jeremiah said, “They will not give you over. Please <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19916AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19916AG\"></sup>obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in what I am saying to you, that it may go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19916AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19916AH\"></sup>well with you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19916AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19916AI\"></sup>you may live.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But if you keep refusing to go out, this is the word which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has shown me:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>‘Then behold, all of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19918AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19918AJ\"></sup>women who have been left in the palace of the king of Judah are going to be brought out to the officers of the king of Babylon; and those women will say,“Your close friendsHave misled and overpowered you;While your feet were sunk in the mire,They turned back.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They will also bring out all your wives and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19919AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19919AK\"></sup>sons to the Chaldeans, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19919AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19919AL\"></sup>you yourself will not escape from their hand, but will be seized by the hand of the king of Babylon, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19919AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19919AM\"></sup>this city will be burned with fire.’”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Zedekiah said to Jeremiah, “Let no man know about these words and you will not die.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But if the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19921AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19921AN\"></sup>officials hear that I have talked with you and come to you and say to you, ‘Tell us now what you said to the king and what the king said to you; do not hide <i>it</i> from us and we will not put you to death,’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then you are to say to them, ‘I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19922AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19922AO\"></sup>presenting my petition before the king, not to make me return to the house of Jonathan to die there.’”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then all the officials came to Jeremiah and questioned him. So he reported to them in accordance with all these words which the king had commanded; and they ceased speaking with him, since the conversation had not been overheard.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So Jeremiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19924AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19924AP\"></sup>stayed in the court of the guardhouse until the day that Jerusalem was captured."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>Now when Jerusalem was captured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19925A\"></sup>in the ninth year of Zedekiah king of Judah, in the tenth month, Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and all his army came to Jerusalem and laid siege to it;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>in the eleventh year of Zedekiah, in the fourth month, in the ninth <i>day</i> of the month, the city <i>wall</i> was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19926B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19926B\"></sup>breached.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19927C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19927C\"></sup>officials of the king of Babylon came in and sat down at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19927D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19927D\"></sup>Middle Gate: Nergal-sar-ezer, Samgar-nebu, Sar-sekim the Rab-saris, Nergal-sar-ezer <i>the</i> Rab-mag, and all the rest of the officials of the king of Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When Zedekiah the king of Judah and all the men of war saw them, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19928E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19928E\"></sup>fled and went out of the city at night by way of the king’s garden through the gate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19928F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19928F\"></sup>between the two walls; and he went out toward the Arabah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the army of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19929G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19929G\"></sup>Chaldeans pursued them and overtook Zedekiah in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19929H\"></sup>plains of Jericho; and they seized him and brought him up to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19929I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19929I\"></sup>Riblah in the land of Hamath, and he passed sentence on him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19930J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19930J\"></sup>king of Babylon slew the sons of Zedekiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19930K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19930K\"></sup>before his eyes at Riblah; the king of Babylon also slew all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19930L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19930L\"></sup>nobles of Judah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19931M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19931M\"></sup>blinded Zedekiah’s eyes and bound him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19931N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19931N\"></sup>fetters of bronze to bring him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19931O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19931O\"></sup>Babylon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Chaldeans also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19932P\"></sup>burned with fire the king’s palace and the houses of the people, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19932Q\"></sup>broke down the walls of Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As for the rest of the people who were left in the city, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19933R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19933R\"></sup>deserters who had gone over to him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19933S\"></sup>the rest of the people who remained, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19933T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19933T\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19933U\"></sup>captain of the bodyguard carried <i>them</i> into exile in Babylon.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But some of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19934V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19934V\"></sup>poorest people who had nothing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19934W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19934W\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard left behind in the land of Judah, and gave them vineyards and fields at that time.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon gave orders about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19935X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19935X\"></sup>Jeremiah through Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard, saying,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Take him and look after him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19936Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19936Y\"></sup>do nothing harmful to him, but rather deal with him just as he tells you.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard sent <i>word</i>, along with Nebushazban the Rab-saris, and Nergal-sar-ezer the Rab-mag, and all the leading officers of the king of Babylon;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>they even sent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19938Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19938Z\"></sup>took Jeremiah out of the court of the guardhouse and entrusted him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19938AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19938AA\"></sup>Gedaliah, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19938AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19938AB\"></sup>Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, to take him home. So he stayed among the people.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had come to Jeremiah while he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19939AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19939AC\"></sup>confined in the court of the guardhouse, saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Go and speak to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19940AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19940AD\"></sup>Ebed-melech the Ethiopian, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Behold, I am about to bring My words on this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19940AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19940AE\"></sup>for disaster and not for prosperity; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19940AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19940AF\"></sup>take place before you on that day.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19941AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19941AG\"></sup>deliver you on that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and you will not be given into the hand of the men whom you dread.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For I will certainly rescue you, and you will not fall by the sword; but you will have your <i>own</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19942AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19942AH\"></sup>life as booty, because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19942AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19942AI\"></sup>trusted in Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>The word which came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19943A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19943A\"></sup>Nebuzaradan captain of the bodyguard had released him from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19943B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19943B\"></sup>Ramah, when he had taken him bound in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19943C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19943C\"></sup>chains among all the exiles of Jerusalem and Judah who were being exiled to Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now the captain of the bodyguard had taken Jeremiah and said to him, “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19944D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19944D\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God promised this calamity against this place;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought <i>it</i> on and done just as He promised. Because you <i>people</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19945E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19945E\"></sup>sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and did not listen to His voice, therefore this thing has happened to you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But now, behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19946F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19946F\"></sup>freeing you today from the chains which are on your hands. If you would prefer to come with me to Babylon, come <i>along</i>, and I will look after you; but if you would prefer not to come with me to Babylon, never mind. Look, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19946G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19946G\"></sup>whole land is before you; go wherever it seems good and right for you to go.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As Jeremiah was still not going back, <i>he said</i>, “Go on back then to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19947H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19947H\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, whom the king of Babylon has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19947I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19947I\"></sup>appointed over the cities of Judah, and stay with him among the people; or else go anywhere it seems right for you to go.” So the captain of the bodyguard gave him a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19947J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19947J\"></sup>ration and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19947K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19947K\"></sup>gift and let him go.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Jeremiah went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19948L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19948L\"></sup>Mizpah to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19948M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19948M\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam and stayed with him among the people who were left in the land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19949N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19949N\"></sup>Now all the commanders of the forces that were in the field, they and their men, heard that the king of Babylon had appointed Gedaliah the son of Ahikam over the land and that he had put him in charge of the men, women and children, those of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19949O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19949O\"></sup>poorest of the land who had not been exiled to Babylon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So they came to Gedaliah at Mizpah, along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19950P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19950P\"></sup>Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19950Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19950Q\"></sup>Johanan and Jonathan the sons of Kareah, and Seraiah the son of Tanhumeth, and the sons of Ephai the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19950R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19950R\"></sup>Netophathite, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19950S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19950S\"></sup>Jezaniah the son of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19950T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19950T\"></sup>Maacathite, <i>both</i> they and their men.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19951U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19951U\"></sup>swore to them and to their men, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19951V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19951V\"></sup>Do not be afraid of serving the Chaldeans; stay in the land and serve the king of Babylon, that it may go well with you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now as for me, behold, I am going to stay at Mizpah to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19952W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19952W\"></sup>stand <i>for you</i> before the Chaldeans who come to us; but as for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19952X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19952X\"></sup>gather in wine and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19952Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19952Y\"></sup>summer fruit and oil and put <i>them</i> in your <i>storage</i> vessels, and live in your cities that you have taken over.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Likewise, also all the Jews who were in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19953Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19953Z\"></sup>Moab and among the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19953AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19953AA\"></sup>Ammon and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19953AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19953AB\"></sup>Edom and who were in all the <i>other</i> countries, heard that the king of Babylon had left a remnant for Judah, and that he had appointed over them Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then all the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19954AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19954AC\"></sup>returned from all the places to which they had been driven away and came to the land of Judah, to Gedaliah at Mizpah, and gathered in wine and summer fruit in great abundance.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now Johanan the son of Kareah and all the commanders of the forces that were in the field came to Gedaliah at Mizpah",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and said to him, “Are you well aware that Baalis the king of the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19956AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19956AD\"></sup>Ammon has sent Ishmael the son of Nethaniah to take your life?” But Gedaliah the son of Ahikam did not believe them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then Johanan the son of Kareah spoke secretly to Gedaliah in Mizpah, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19957AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19957AE\"></sup>Let me go and kill Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, and not a man will know! Why should he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19957AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19957AF\"></sup>take your life, so that all the Jews who are gathered to you would be scattered and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19957AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19957AG\"></sup>remnant of Judah would perish?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Gedaliah the son of Ahikam said to Johanan the son of Kareah, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19958AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19958AH\"></sup>Do not do this thing, for you are telling a lie about Ishmael.”"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19959A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19959A\"></sup>In the seventh month <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19959B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19959B\"></sup>Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, the son of Elishama, of the royal family and <i>one</i> of the chief officers of the king, along with ten men, came to Mizpah to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19959C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19959C\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam. While they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19959D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19959D\"></sup>were eating bread together there in Mizpah,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Ishmael the son of Nethaniah and the ten men who were with him arose and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19960E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19960E\"></sup>struck down Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, with the sword and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19960F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19960F\"></sup>put to death the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19960G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19960G\"></sup>whom the king of Babylon had appointed over the land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Ishmael also struck down all the Jews who were with him, <i>that is</i> with Gedaliah at Mizpah, and the Chaldeans who were found there, the men of war.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now it happened on the next day after the killing of Gedaliah, when no one knew about <i>it</i>,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>that eighty men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963H\"></sup>came from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963I\"></sup>Shechem, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963J\"></sup>Shiloh, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963K\"></sup>Samaria with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963L\"></sup>their beards shaved off and their clothes torn and their bodies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963M\"></sup>gashed, having grain offerings and incense in their hands to bring to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19963N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19963N\"></sup>house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Ishmael the son of Nethaniah went out from Mizpah to meet them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19964O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19964O\"></sup>weeping as he went; and as he met them, he said to them, “Come to Gedaliah the son of Ahikam!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet it turned out that as soon as they came inside the city, Ishmael the son of Nethaniah and the men that were with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19965P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19965P\"></sup>slaughtered them <i>and cast them</i> into the cistern.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But ten men who were found among them said to Ishmael, “Do not put us to death; for we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19966Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19966Q\"></sup>stores of wheat, barley, oil and honey hidden in the field.” So he refrained and did not put them to death along with their companions.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now as for the cistern where Ishmael had cast all the corpses of the men whom he had struck down because of Gedaliah, it was the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19967R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19967R\"></sup>one that King Asa had made on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19967S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19967S\"></sup>account of Baasha, king of Israel; Ishmael the son of Nethaniah filled it with the slain.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Ishmael took captive all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19968T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19968T\"></sup>remnant of the people who were in Mizpah, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19968U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19968U\"></sup>king’s daughters and all the people who were left in Mizpah, whom Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard had put under the charge of Gedaliah the son of Ahikam; thus Ishmael the son of Nethaniah took them captive and proceeded to cross over to the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19968V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19968V\"></sup>Ammon.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But Johanan the son of Kareah and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19969W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19969W\"></sup>commanders of the forces that were with him heard of all the evil that Ishmael the son of Nethaniah had done.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So they took all the men and went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19970X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19970X\"></sup>fight with Ishmael the son of Nethaniah and they found him by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19970Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19970Y\"></sup>great pool that is in Gibeon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now as soon as all the people who were with Ishmael saw Johanan the son of Kareah and the commanders of the forces that were with him, they were glad.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So all the people whom Ishmael had taken captive from Mizpah turned around and came back, and went to Johanan the son of Kareah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Ishmael the son of Nethaniah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19973Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19973Z\"></sup>escaped from Johanan with eight men and went to the sons of Ammon.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then Johanan the son of Kareah and all the commanders of the forces that were with him took from Mizpah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19974AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19974AA\"></sup>all the remnant of the people whom he had recovered from Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, after he had struck down Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, <i>that is</i>, the men who were soldiers, <i>the</i> women, <i>the</i> children, and <i>the</i> eunuchs, whom he had brought back from Gibeon.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they went and stayed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19975AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19975AB\"></sup>Geruth Chimham, which is beside Bethlehem, in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19975AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19975AC\"></sup>proceed into Egypt",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>because of the Chaldeans; for they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19976AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19976AD\"></sup>afraid of them, since Ishmael the son of Nethaniah had struck down Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19976AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19976AE\"></sup>the king of Babylon had appointed over the land."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then all the commanders of the forces, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19977A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19977A\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah, Jezaniah the son of Hoshaiah, and all the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19977B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19977B\"></sup>both small and great approached",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and said to Jeremiah the prophet, “Please let our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19978C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19978C\"></sup>petition come before you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19978D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19978D\"></sup>pray for us to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, <i>that is</i> for all this remnant; because we are left <i>but</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19978E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19978E\"></sup>few out of many, as your own eyes <i>now</i> see us,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God may tell us the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19979F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19979F\"></sup>way in which we should walk and the thing that we should do.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then Jeremiah the prophet said to them, “I have heard <i>you</i>. Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19980G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19980G\"></sup>pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in accordance with your words; and I will tell you the whole message which the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19980H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19980H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer you. I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19980I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19980I\"></sup>not keep back a word from you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then they said to Jeremiah, “May the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19981J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19981J\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be a true and faithful witness against us if we do not act in accordance with the whole message with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will send you to us.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whether <i>it</i> is pleasant or unpleasant, we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19982K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19982K\"></sup>listen to the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God to whom we are sending you, so that it may go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19982L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19982L\"></sup>well with us when we listen to the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19983M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19983M\"></sup>end of ten days the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he called for Johanan the son of Kareah and all the commanders of the forces that were with him, and for all the people both small and great,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and said to them, “Thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19985N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19985N\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> the God of Israel, to whom you sent me to present your petition before Him:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘If you will indeed stay in this land, then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19986O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19986O\"></sup>build you up and not tear you down, and I will plant you and not uproot you; for I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19986P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19986P\"></sup>relent concerning the calamity that I have inflicted on you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19987Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19987Q\"></sup>Do not be afraid of the king of Babylon, whom you are <i>now</i> fearing; do not be afraid of him,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19987R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19987R\"></sup>I am with you to save you and deliver you from his hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will also show you compassion, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19988S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19988S\"></sup>he will have compassion on you and restore you to your own soil.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But if you are going to say, “We will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19989T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19989T\"></sup>not stay in this land,” so as not to listen to the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>saying, “No, but we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19990U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19990U\"></sup>go to the land of Egypt, where we will not see war or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19990V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19990V\"></sup>hear the sound of a trumpet or hunger for bread, and we will stay there”;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>then in that case listen to the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O remnant of Judah. Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “If you really set your mind to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19991W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19991W\"></sup>Egypt and go in to reside there,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19992X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19992X\"></sup>sword, which you are afraid of, will overtake you there in the land of Egypt; and the famine, about which you are anxious, will follow closely after you there <i>in</i> Egypt, and you will die there.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So all the men who set their mind to go to Egypt to reside there will die by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19993Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19993Y\"></sup>sword, by famine and by pestilence; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19993Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19993Z\"></sup>have no survivors or refugees from the calamity that I am going to bring on them.”’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “As My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19994AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19994AA\"></sup>anger and wrath have been poured out on the inhabitants of Jerusalem, so My wrath will be poured out on you when you enter Egypt. And you will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19994AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19994AB\"></sup>curse, an object of horror, an imprecation and a reproach; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19994AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19994AC\"></sup>you will see this place no more.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken to you, O remnant of Judah, “Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19995AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19995AD\"></sup>go into Egypt!” You should clearly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19995AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19995AE\"></sup>understand that today I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19995AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19995AF\"></sup>testified against you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For you have <i>only</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19996AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19996AG\"></sup>deceived yourselves; for it is you who sent me to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, saying, “Pray for us to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God; and whatever the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God says, tell us so, and we will do it.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19997AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19997AH\"></sup>told you today, but you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19997AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19997AI\"></sup>not obeyed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, even in whatever He has sent me to <i>tell</i> you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore you should now clearly understand that you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19998AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19998AJ\"></sup>die by the sword, by famine and by pestilence, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19998AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19998AK\"></sup>place where you wish to go to reside."
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>But as soon as Jeremiah, whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God had sent, had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-19999A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-19999A\"></sup>finished telling all the people all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God—that is, all these words—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Azariah the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20000B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20000B\"></sup>son of Hoshaiah, and Johanan the son of Kareah, and all the arrogant men said to Jeremiah, “You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20000C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20000C\"></sup>telling a lie! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has not sent you to say, ‘You are not to enter Egypt to reside there’;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20001D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20001D\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah is inciting you against us to give us over into the hand of the Chaldeans, so they will put us to death or exile us to Babylon.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20002E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20002E\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and all the commanders of the forces, and all the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20002F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20002F\"></sup>did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20002G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20002G\"></sup>stay in the land of Judah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But Johanan the son of Kareah and all the commanders of the forces took the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20003H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20003H\"></sup>entire remnant of Judah who had returned from all the nations to which they had been driven away, in order to reside in the land of Judah—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>the men, the women, the children, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20004I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20004I\"></sup>king’s daughters and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20004J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20004J\"></sup>every person that Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard had left with Gedaliah the son of Ahikam and grandson of Shaphan, together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20004K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20004K\"></sup>Jeremiah the prophet and Baruch the son of Neriah—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and they entered the land of Egypt (for they did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>) and went in as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20005L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20005L\"></sup>Tahpanhes.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20006M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20006M\"></sup>Tahpanhes, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Take <i>some</i> large stones in your hands and hide them in the mortar in the brick <i>terrace</i> which is at the entrance of Pharaoh’s palace in Tahpanhes, in the sight of some <i>of the</i> Jews;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, “Behold, I am going to send and get <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20008N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20008N\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20008O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20008O\"></sup>My servant, and I am going to set his throne <i>right</i> over these stones that I have hidden; and he will spread his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20008P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20008P\"></sup>canopy over them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He will also come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20009Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20009Q\"></sup>strike the land of Egypt; those who are <i>meant</i> for death <i>will be given over</i> to death, and those for captivity to captivity, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20009R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20009R\"></sup>those for the sword to the sword.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I shall set fire to the temples of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20010S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20010S\"></sup>gods of Egypt, and he will burn them and take them captive. So he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20010T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20010T\"></sup>wrap himself with the land of Egypt as a shepherd wraps himself with his garment, and he will depart from there safely.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He will also shatter the obelisks of Heliopolis, which is in the land of Egypt; and the temples of the gods of Egypt he will burn with fire.”’”"
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah for all the Jews living in the land of Egypt, those who were living in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20012A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20012A\"></sup>Migdol, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20012B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20012B\"></sup>Tahpanhes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20012C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20012C\"></sup>Memphis, and the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20012D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20012D\"></sup>Pathros, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘You yourselves have seen all the calamity that I have brought on Jerusalem and all the cities of Judah; and behold, this day they are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20013E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20013E\"></sup>ruins and no one lives in them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20014F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20014F\"></sup>because of their wickedness which they committed so as to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20014G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20014G\"></sup>provoke Me to anger by continuing to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20014H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20014H\"></sup>burn sacrifices <i>and</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20014I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20014I\"></sup>serve other gods whom they had not known, <i>neither</i> they, you, nor your fathers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20015J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20015J\"></sup>sent you all My servants the prophets, again and again, saying, “Oh, do not do this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20015K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20015K\"></sup>abominable thing which I hate.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20016L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20016L\"></sup>they did not listen or incline their ears to turn from their wickedness, so as not to burn sacrifices to other gods.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20017M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20017M\"></sup>wrath and My anger were poured out and burned in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20017N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20017N\"></sup>cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem, so they have become a ruin and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20017O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20017O\"></sup>desolation as it is this day.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now then thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of hosts, the God of Israel, “Why are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20018P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20018P\"></sup>doing great harm to yourselves, so as to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20018Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20018Q\"></sup>cut off from you man and woman, child and infant, from among Judah, leaving yourselves without remnant,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20019R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20019R\"></sup>provoking Me to anger with the works of your hands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20019S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20019S\"></sup>burning sacrifices to other gods in the land of Egypt, where you are entering to reside, so that you might be cut off and become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20019T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20019T\"></sup>curse and a reproach among all the nations of the earth?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Have you forgotten the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20020U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20020U\"></sup>wickedness of your fathers, the wickedness of the kings of Judah, and the wickedness of their wives, your own wickedness, and the wickedness of your wives, which they committed in the land of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20021V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20021V\"></sup>have not become contrite even to this day, nor have they feared nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20021W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20021W\"></sup>walked in My law or My statutes, which I have set before you and before your fathers.”’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, ‘Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20022X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20022X\"></sup>set My face against you for woe, even to cut off all Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20023Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20023Y\"></sup>take away the remnant of Judah who have set their mind on entering the land of Egypt to reside there, and they will all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20023Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20023Z\"></sup>meet their end in the land of Egypt; they will fall by the sword <i>and</i> meet their end by famine. Both small and great will die by the sword and famine; and they will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20023AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20023AA\"></sup>curse, an object of horror, an imprecation and a reproach.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20024AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20024AB\"></sup>punish those who live in the land of Egypt, as I have punished Jerusalem, with the sword, with famine and with pestilence.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20025AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20025AC\"></sup>no refugees or survivors for the remnant of Judah who have entered the land of Egypt to reside there and then to return to the land of Judah, to which they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20025AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20025AD\"></sup>longing to return and live; for none will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20025AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20025AE\"></sup>return except <i>a few</i> refugees.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20026AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20026AF\"></sup>all the men who were aware that their wives were burning sacrifices to other gods, along with all the women who were standing by, <i>as</i> a large assembly, including all the people who were living in Pathros in the land of Egypt, responded to Jeremiah, saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20027AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20027AG\"></sup>message that you have spoken to us in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20027AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20027AH\"></sup>we are not going to listen to you!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But rather we will certainly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20028AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20028AI\"></sup>carry out every word that has proceeded from our mouths, by burning sacrifices to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20028AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20028AJ\"></sup>queen of heaven and pouring out drink offerings to her, just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20028AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20028AK\"></sup>we ourselves, our forefathers, our kings and our princes did in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem; for <i>then</i> we had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20028AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20028AL\"></sup>plenty of food and were well off and saw no misfortune.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But since we stopped burning sacrifices to the queen of heaven and pouring out drink offerings to her, we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20029AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20029AM\"></sup>lacked everything and have met our end by the sword and by famine.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“And,” <i>said the women</i>, “when we were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20030AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20030AN\"></sup>burning sacrifices to the queen of heaven and were pouring out drink offerings to her, was it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20030AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20030AO\"></sup>without our husbands that we made for her <i>sacrificial</i> cakes in her image and poured out drink offerings to her?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to all the people, to the men and women—even to all the people who were giving him <i>such</i> an answer—saying,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20032AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20032AP\"></sup>smoking sacrifices that you burned in the cities of Judah and in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20032AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20032AQ\"></sup>streets of Jerusalem, you and your forefathers, your kings and your princes, and the people of the land, did not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20032AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20032AR\"></sup>remember them and did not <i>all this</i> come into His mind?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20033AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20033AS\"></sup>no longer able to endure <i>it</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20033AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20033AT\"></sup>because of the evil of your deeds, because of the abominations which you have committed; thus your land has become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20033AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20033AU\"></sup>ruin, an object of horror and a curse, without an inhabitant, as <i>it is</i> this day.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Because you have burned sacrifices and have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20034AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20034AV\"></sup>not obeyed the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20034AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20034AW\"></sup>walked in His law, His statutes or His testimonies, therefore this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20034AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20034AX\"></sup>calamity has befallen you, as <i>it has</i> this day.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to all the people, including all the women, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20035AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20035AY\"></sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all Judah who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20035AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20035AZ\"></sup>in the land of Egypt,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, as follows: ‘As for you and your wives, you have spoken with your mouths and fulfilled <i>it</i> with your hands, saying, “We will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20036BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20036BA\"></sup>certainly perform our vows that we have vowed, to burn sacrifices to the queen of heaven and pour out drink offerings to her.” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20036BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20036BB\"></sup>Go ahead and confirm your vows, and certainly perform your vows!’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Nevertheless hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all Judah who are living in the land of Egypt, ‘Behold, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20037BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20037BC\"></sup>sworn by My great name,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20037BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20037BD\"></sup>never shall My name be invoked again by the mouth of any man of Judah in all the land of Egypt, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20037BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20037BE\"></sup>As the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> lives.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Behold, I am watching over them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20038BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20038BF\"></sup>for harm and not for good, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20038BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20038BG\"></sup>all the men of Judah who are in the land of Egypt will meet their end by the sword and by famine until they are completely gone.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20039BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20039BH\"></sup>Those who escape the sword will return out of the land of Egypt to the land of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20039BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20039BI\"></sup>few in number. Then all the remnant of Judah who have gone to the land of Egypt to reside there will know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20039BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20039BJ\"></sup>whose word will stand, Mine or theirs.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>This will be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20040BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20040BK\"></sup>sign to you,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘that I am going to punish you in this place, so that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20040BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20040BL\"></sup>My words will surely stand against you for harm.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Behold, I am going to give over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20041BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20041BM\"></sup>Pharaoh Hophra king of Egypt to the hand of his enemies, to the hand of those who seek his life, just as I gave over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20041BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20041BN\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah to the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, <i>who was</i> his enemy and was seeking his life.’”"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span><i>This is</i> the message which Jeremiah the prophet spoke to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20042A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20042A\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah, when he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20042B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20042B\"></sup>written down these words in a book at Jeremiah’s dictation, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20042C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20042C\"></sup>fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, saying:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> the God of Israel to you, O Baruch:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘You said, “Ah, woe is me! For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has added sorrow to my pain; I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20044D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20044D\"></sup>weary with my groaning and have found no rest.”’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus you are to say to him, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20045E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20045E\"></sup>what I have built I am about to tear down, and what I have planted I am about to uproot, that is, the whole land.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But you, are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20046F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20046F\"></sup>seeking great things for yourself? Do not seek <i>them</i>; for behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20046G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20046G\"></sup>bring disaster on all flesh,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘but I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20046H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20046H\"></sup>give your life to you as booty in all the places where you may go.’”"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span>That which came as the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Jeremiah the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20047A\"></sup>concerning the nations.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20048B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20048B\"></sup>Egypt, concerning the army of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20048C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20048C\"></sup>Pharaoh Neco king of Egypt, which was by the Euphrates River at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20048D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20048D\"></sup>Carchemish, which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon defeated in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20048E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20048E\"></sup>fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20049F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20049F\"></sup>Line up the shield and buckler,And draw near for the battle!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Harness the horses,And mount the steeds,And take your stand with helmets <i>on</i>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20050G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20050G\"></sup>Polish the spears,Put on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20050H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20050H\"></sup>scale-armor!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Why have I seen <i>it</i>?They are terrified,They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20051I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20051I\"></sup>drawing back,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20051J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20051J\"></sup>mighty men are defeatedAnd have taken refuge in flight,Without facing back;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20051K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20051K\"></sup>Terror is on every side!”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Let not the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20052L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20052L\"></sup>swift man flee,Nor the mighty man escape;In the north beside the river EuphratesThey have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20052M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20052M\"></sup>stumbled and fallen.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Who is this that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20053N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20053N\"></sup>rises like the Nile,Like the rivers whose waters surge about?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Egypt rises like the Nile,Even like the rivers whose waters surge about;And He has said, “I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20054O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20054O\"></sup>rise and cover <i>that</i> land;I will surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20054P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20054P\"></sup>destroy the city and its inhabitants.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Go up, you horses, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20055Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20055Q\"></sup>drive madly, you chariots,That the mighty men may march forward:Ethiopia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20055R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20055R\"></sup>Put, that handle the shield,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20055S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20055S\"></sup>Lydians, that handle <i>and</i> bend the bow.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20056T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20056T\"></sup>that day belongs to the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,A day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20056U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20056U\"></sup>vengeance, so as to avenge Himself on His foes;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20056V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20056V\"></sup>sword will devour and be satiatedAnd drink its fill of their blood;For there will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20056W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20056W\"></sup>slaughter for the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,In the land of the north by the river Euphrates.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20057X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20057X\"></sup>up to Gilead and obtain balm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20057Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20057Y\"></sup>O virgin daughter of Egypt!In vain have you multiplied remedies;There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20057Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20057Z\"></sup>no healing for you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The nations have heard of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20058AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20058AA\"></sup>shame,And the earth is full of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20058AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20058AB\"></sup>cry <i>of distress</i>;For one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20058AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20058AC\"></sup>warrior has stumbled over another,And both of them have fallen down together.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><i>This is</i> the message which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Jeremiah the prophet about the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20059AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20059AD\"></sup>coming of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20059AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20059AE\"></sup>smite the land of Egypt:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Declare in Egypt and proclaim in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20060AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20060AF\"></sup>Migdol,Proclaim also in Memphis and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20060AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20060AG\"></sup>Tahpanhes;Say, ‘Take your stand and get yourself ready,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20060AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20060AH\"></sup>sword has devoured those around you.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Why have your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20061AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20061AI\"></sup>mighty ones become prostrate?They do not stand because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20061AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20061AJ\"></sup>thrust them down.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“They have repeatedly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20062AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20062AK\"></sup>stumbled;Indeed, they have fallen one against another.Then they said, ‘Get up! And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20062AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20062AL\"></sup>let us go backTo our own people and our native landAway from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20062AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20062AM\"></sup>sword of the oppressor.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“They cried there, ‘Pharaoh king of Egypt <i>is but</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20063AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20063AN\"></sup>a big noise;He has let the appointed time pass by!’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“As I live,” declares the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20064AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20064AO\"></sup>KingWhose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“Surely one shall come <i>who looms up</i> like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20064AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20064AP\"></sup>Tabor among the mountains,Or like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20064AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20064AQ\"></sup>Carmel by the sea.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Make your baggage ready for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20065AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20065AR\"></sup>exile,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20065AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20065AS\"></sup>daughter dwelling in Egypt,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20065AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20065AT\"></sup>Memphis will become a desolation;It will even be burned down <i>and</i> bereft of inhabitants.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Egypt is a pretty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20066AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20066AU\"></sup>heifer,<i>But</i> a horsefly is coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20066AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20066AV\"></sup>from the north—it is coming!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Also her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20067AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20067AW\"></sup>mercenaries in her midstAre like fattened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20067AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20067AX\"></sup>calves,For even they too have turned back <i>and</i> have fled away together;They did not stand <i>their ground</i>.For the day of their calamity has come upon them,The time of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20067AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20067AY\"></sup>punishment.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Its sound moves along like a serpent;For they move on like an armyAnd come to her as woodcutters with axes.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“They have cut down her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20069AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20069AZ\"></sup>forest,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;“Surely it will no <i>more</i> be found,Even though they are <i>now</i> more numerous than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20069BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20069BA\"></sup>locustsAnd are without number.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“The daughter of Egypt has been put to shame,Given over to the power of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20070BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20070BB\"></sup>people of the north.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, says, “Behold, I am going to punish Amon of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20071BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20071BC\"></sup>Thebes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20071BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20071BD\"></sup>Pharaoh, and Egypt along with her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20071BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20071BE\"></sup>gods and her kings, even Pharaoh and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20071BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20071BF\"></sup>trust in him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I shall give them over to the power of those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20072BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20072BG\"></sup>seeking their lives, even into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and into the hand of his officers. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20072BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20072BH\"></sup>Afterwards, however, it will be inhabited as in the days of old,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“But as for you, O Jacob My servant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20073BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20073BI\"></sup>do not fear,Nor be dismayed, O Israel!For, see, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20073BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20073BJ\"></sup>save you from afar,And your descendants from the land of their captivity;And Jacob will return and be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20073BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20073BK\"></sup>undisturbedAnd secure, with no one making <i>him</i> tremble.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“O Jacob My servant, do not fear,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20074BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20074BL\"></sup>I am with you.For I will make a full end of all the nationsWhere I have driven you,Yet I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20074BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20074BM\"></sup>not make a full end of you;But I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20074BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20074BN\"></sup>correct you properlyAnd by no means leave you unpunished.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>That which came as the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Jeremiah the prophet concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20075A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20075A\"></sup>Philistines, before Pharaoh conquered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20075B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20075B\"></sup>Gaza.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Behold, waters are going to rise from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20076C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20076C\"></sup>the northAnd become an overflowing torrent,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20076D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20076D\"></sup>overflow the land and all its fullness,The city and those who live in it;And the men will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20076E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20076E\"></sup>cry out,And every inhabitant of the land will wail.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Because of the noise of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20077F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20077F\"></sup>galloping hoofs of his stallions,The tumult of his chariots, <i>and</i> the rumbling of his wheels,The fathers have not turned back for <i>their</i> children,Because of the limpness of <i>their</i> hands,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On account of the day that is comingTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20078G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20078G\"></sup>destroy all the Philistines,To cut off from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20078H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20078H\"></sup>Tyre and SidonEvery ally that is left;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is going to destroy the Philistines,The remnant of the coastland of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20078I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20078I\"></sup>Caphtor.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20079J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20079J\"></sup>Baldness has come upon Gaza;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20079K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20079K\"></sup>Ashkelon has been ruined.O remnant of their valley,How long will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20079L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20079L\"></sup>gash yourself?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Ah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20080M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20080M\"></sup>sword of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,How long will you not be quiet?Withdraw into your sheath;Be at rest and stay still.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“How can it be quiet,When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20081N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20081N\"></sup>given it an order?Against Ashkelon and against the seacoast—There He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20081O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20081O\"></sup>assigned it.”"
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20082A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20082A\"></sup>Moab. Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel,“Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20082B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20082B\"></sup>Nebo, for it has been destroyed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20082C\"></sup>Kiriathaim has been put to shame, it has been captured;The lofty stronghold has been put to shame and shattered.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“There is praise for Moab no longer;In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20083D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20083D\"></sup>Heshbon they have devised calamity against her:‘Come and let us cut her off from <i>being</i> a nation!’You too, Madmen, will be silenced;The sword will follow after you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“The sound of an outcry from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20084E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20084E\"></sup>Horonaim,‘Devastation and great destruction!’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Moab is broken,Her little ones have sounded out a cry <i>of distress</i>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For by the ascent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20086F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20086F\"></sup>LuhithThey will ascend with continual weeping;For at the descent of HoronaimThey have heard the anguished cry of destruction.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20087G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20087G\"></sup>Flee, save your lives,That you may be like a juniper in the wilderness.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For because of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20088H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20088H\"></sup>trust in your own achievements and treasures,Even you yourself will be captured;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20088I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20088I\"></sup>Chemosh will go off into exileTogether with his priests and his princes.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“A destroyer will come to every city,So that no city will escape;The valley also will be ruinedAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20089J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20089J\"></sup>plateau will be destroyed,As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has said.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20090K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20090K\"></sup>wings to Moab,For she will flee away;And her cities will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20090L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20090L\"></sup>desolation,Without inhabitants in them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20091M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20091M\"></sup>Cursed be the one who does the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> work <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20091N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20091N\"></sup>negligently,And cursed be the one who restrains his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20091O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20091O\"></sup>sword from blood.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Moab has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20092P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20092P\"></sup>at ease since his youth;He has also been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20092Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20092Q\"></sup>undisturbed, <i>like wine</i> on its dregs,And he has not been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20092R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20092R\"></sup>emptied from vessel to vessel,Nor has he gone into exile.Therefore he retains his flavor,And his aroma has not changed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore behold, the days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when I will send to him those who tip <i>vessels</i>, and they will tip him over, and they will empty his vessels and shatter his jars.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And Moab will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20094S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20094S\"></sup>ashamed of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20094T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20094T\"></sup>Chemosh, as the house of Israel was ashamed of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20094U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20094U\"></sup>Bethel, their confidence.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“How can you say, ‘We are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20095V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20095V\"></sup>mighty warriors,And men valiant for battle’?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Moab has been destroyed and men have gone up to his cities;His choicest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20096W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20096W\"></sup>young men have also gone down to the slaughter,”Declares the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20096X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20096X\"></sup>King, whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“The disaster of Moab will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20097Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20097Y\"></sup>soon come,And his calamity has swiftly hastened.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Mourn for him, all you who <i>live</i> around him,Even all of you who know his name;Say, ‘How has the mighty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20098Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20098Z\"></sup>scepter been broken,A staff of splendor!’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20099AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20099AA\"></sup>Come down from your gloryAnd sit on the parched ground,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20099AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20099AB\"></sup>daughter dwelling in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20099AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20099AC\"></sup>Dibon,For the destroyer of Moab has come up against you,He has ruined your strongholds.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Stand by the road and keep watch,O inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20100AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20100AD\"></sup>Aroer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20100AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20100AE\"></sup>Ask him who flees and her who escapes<i>And</i> say, ‘What has happened?’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Moab has been put to shame, for it has been shattered.Wail and cry out;Declare by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20101AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20101AF\"></sup>ArnonThat Moab has been destroyed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Judgment has also come upon the plain, upon Holon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20102AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20102AG\"></sup>Jahzah and against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20102AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20102AH\"></sup>Mephaath,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>against Dibon, Nebo and Beth-diblathaim,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>against Kiriathaim, Beth-gamul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20104AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20104AI\"></sup>Beth-meon,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20105AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20105AJ\"></sup>Kerioth, Bozrah and all the cities of the land of Moab, far and near.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20106AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20106AK\"></sup>horn of Moab has been cut off and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20106AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20106AL\"></sup>arm broken,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20107AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20107AM\"></sup>Make him drunk, for he has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20107AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20107AN\"></sup>arrogant toward the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; so Moab will wallow in his vomit, and he also will become a laughingstock.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now was not Israel a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20108AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20108AO\"></sup>laughingstock to you? Or was he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20108AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20108AP\"></sup>caught among thieves? For each time you speak about him you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20108AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20108AQ\"></sup>shake <i>your head in scorn</i>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Leave the cities and dwell among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20109AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20109AR\"></sup>crags,O inhabitants of Moab,And be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20109AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20109AS\"></sup>dove that nestsBeyond the mouth of the chasm.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20110AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20110AT\"></sup>We have heard of the pride of Moab—he <i>is</i> very proud—Of his haughtiness, his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20110AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20110AU\"></sup>pride, his arrogance and his self-exaltation.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“I know his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20111AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20111AV\"></sup>fury,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“But it is futile;His idle boasts have accomplished nothing.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Therefore I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20112AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20112AW\"></sup>wail for Moab,Even for all Moab will I cry out;I will moan for the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20112AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20112AX\"></sup>Kir-heres.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“More than the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20113AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20113AY\"></sup>weeping for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20113AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20113AZ\"></sup>JazerI will weep for you, O vine of Sibmah!Your tendrils stretched across the sea,They reached to the sea of Jazer;Upon your summer fruits and your grape harvestThe destroyer has fallen.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20114BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20114BA\"></sup>gladness and joy are taken awayFrom the fruitful field, even from the land of Moab.And I have made the wine to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20114BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20114BB\"></sup>cease from the wine presses;No one will tread <i>them</i> with shouting,The shouting will not be shouts <i>of joy</i>.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20115BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20115BC\"></sup>From the outcry at Heshbon even to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20115BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20115BD\"></sup>Elealeh, even to Jahaz they have raised their voice, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20115BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20115BE\"></sup>Zoar even to Horonaim <i>and to</i> Eglath-shelishiyah; for even the waters of Nimrim will become desolate.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>I will make an end of Moab,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “the one who offers <i>sacrifice</i> on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20116BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20116BF\"></sup>high place and the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20116BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20116BG\"></sup>burns incense to his gods.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Therefore My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20117BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20117BH\"></sup>heart wails for Moab like flutes; My heart also wails like flutes for the men of Kir-heres. Therefore they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20117BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20117BI\"></sup>lost the abundance it produced.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20118BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20118BJ\"></sup>every head is bald and every beard cut short; there are gashes on all the hands and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20118BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20118BK\"></sup>sackcloth on the loins.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>On all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20119BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20119BL\"></sup>housetops of Moab and in its streets there is lamentation everywhere; for I have broken Moab like an undesirable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20119BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20119BM\"></sup>vessel,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“How shattered it is! <i>How</i> they have wailed! How Moab has turned his back—he is ashamed! So Moab will become a laughingstock and an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20120BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20120BN\"></sup>object of terror to all around him.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Behold, one will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20121BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20121BO\"></sup>fly swiftly like an eagleAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20121BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20121BP\"></sup>spread out his wings against Moab.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“Kerioth has been capturedAnd the strongholds have been seized,So the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20122BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20122BQ\"></sup>hearts of the mighty men of Moab in that dayWill be like the heart of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20122BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20122BR\"></sup>woman in labor.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“Moab will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20123BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20123BS\"></sup>destroyed from <i>being</i> a peopleBecause he has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20123BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20123BT\"></sup>arrogant toward the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20124BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20124BU\"></sup>Terror, pit and snare are <i>coming</i> upon you,O inhabitant of Moab,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“The one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20125BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20125BV\"></sup>flees from the terrorWill fall into the pit,And the one who climbs up out of the pitWill be caught in the snare;For I shall bring upon her, <i>even</i> upon Moab,The year of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20125BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20125BW\"></sup>punishment,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“In the shadow of HeshbonThe fugitives stand without strength;For a fire has gone forth from HeshbonAnd a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20126BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20126BX\"></sup>flame from the midst of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20126BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20126BY\"></sup>Sihon,And it has devoured the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20126BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20126BZ\"></sup>forehead of MoabAnd the scalps of the riotous revelers.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20127CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20127CA\"></sup>Woe to you, Moab!The people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20127CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20127CB\"></sup>Chemosh have perished;For your sons have been taken away captiveAnd your daughters into captivity.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>“Yet I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20128CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20128CC\"></sup>restore the fortunes of MoabIn the latter days,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Thus far the judgment on Moab."
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">49 </span>Concerning the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20129A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20129A\"></sup>Ammon. Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Does Israel have no sons?Or has he no heirs?Why then has Malcam taken possession of GadAnd his people settled in its cities?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Therefore behold, the days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“That I will cause a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20130B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20130B\"></sup>trumpet blast of war to be heardAgainst <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20130C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20130C\"></sup>Rabbah of the sons of Ammon;And it will become a desolate heap,And her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20130D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20130D\"></sup>towns will be set on fire.Then Israel will take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20130E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20130E\"></sup>possession of his possessors,”Says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20131F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20131F\"></sup>Heshbon, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20131G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20131G\"></sup>Ai has been destroyed!Cry out, O daughters of Rabbah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20131H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20131H\"></sup>Gird yourselves with sackcloth and lament,And rush back and forth inside the walls;For Malcam will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20131I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20131I\"></sup>go into exileTogether with his priests and his princes.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20132J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20132J\"></sup>boastful you are about the valleys!Your valley is flowing <i>away</i>,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20132K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20132K\"></sup>backsliding daughterWho trusts in her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20132L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20132L\"></sup>treasures, <i>saying</i>,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20132M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20132M\"></sup>Who will come against me?’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Behold, I am going to bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20133N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20133N\"></sup>terror upon you,”Declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,“From all <i>directions</i> around you;And each of you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20133O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20133O\"></sup>driven out headlong,With no one to gather the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20133P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20133P\"></sup>fugitives together.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“But afterward I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20134Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20134Q\"></sup>restoreThe fortunes of the sons of Ammon,”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20135R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20135R\"></sup>Edom.Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“Is there no longer any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20135S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20135S\"></sup>wisdom in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20135T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20135T\"></sup>Teman?Has good counsel been lost to the prudent?Has their wisdom decayed?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Flee away, turn back, dwell in the depths,O inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20136U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20136U\"></sup>Dedan,For I will bring the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20136V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20136V\"></sup>disaster of Esau upon himAt the time I punish him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20137W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20137W\"></sup>If grape gatherers came to you,Would they not leave gleanings?If thieves <i>came</i> by night,They would destroy <i>only</i> until they had enough.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20138X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20138X\"></sup>stripped Esau bare,I have uncovered his hiding placesSo that he will not be able to conceal himself;His offspring has been destroyed along with his relativesAnd his neighbors, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20138Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20138Y\"></sup>he is no more.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Leave your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20139Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20139Z\"></sup>orphans behind, I will keep <i>them</i> alive;And let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20139AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20139AA\"></sup>widows trust in Me.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, those who were not sentenced to drink the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20140AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20140AB\"></sup>cup will certainly drink <i>it</i>, and are you the one who will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20140AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20140AC\"></sup>completely acquitted? You will not be acquitted, but you will certainly drink <i>it</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20141AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20141AD\"></sup>sworn by Myself,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20141AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20141AE\"></sup>Bozrah will become an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20141AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20141AF\"></sup>object of horror, a reproach, a ruin and a curse; and all its cities will become perpetual ruins.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20142AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20142AG\"></sup>heard a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20142AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20142AH\"></sup>envoy is sent among the nations, <i>saying</i>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20142AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20142AI\"></sup>Gather yourselves together and come against her,And rise up for battle!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“For behold, I have made you small among the nations,Despised among men.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“As for the terror of you,The arrogance of your heart has deceived you,O you who live in the clefts of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20144AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20144AJ\"></sup>rock,Who occupy the height of the hill.Though you make your nest as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20144AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20144AK\"></sup>high as an eagle’s,I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20144AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20144AL\"></sup>bring you down from there,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Edom will become an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20145AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20145AM\"></sup>object of horror; everyone who passes by it will be horrified and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20145AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20145AN\"></sup>hiss at all its wounds.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20146AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20146AO\"></sup>overthrow of Sodom and Gomorrah with its neighbors,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20146AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20146AP\"></sup>no one will live there, nor will a son of man reside in it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20147AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20147AQ\"></sup>Behold, one will come up like a lion from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20147AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20147AR\"></sup>thickets of the Jordan against a perennially watered pasture; for in an instant I will make him run away from it, and whoever is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20147AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20147AS\"></sup>chosen I shall appoint over it. For who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20147AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20147AT\"></sup>like Me, and who will summon Me <i>into court</i>? And who then is the shepherd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20147AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20147AU\"></sup>who can stand against Me?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore hear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20148AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20148AV\"></sup>plan of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which He has planned against Edom, and His purposes which He has purposed against the inhabitants of Teman: surely they will drag them off, <i>even</i> the little ones of the flock; surely He will make their pasture <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20148AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20148AW\"></sup>desolate because of them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20149AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20149AX\"></sup>earth has quaked at the noise of their downfall. There is an outcry! The noise of it has been heard at the Red Sea.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, He will mount up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20150AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20150AY\"></sup>swoop like an eagle and spread out His wings against Bozrah; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20150AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20150AZ\"></sup>hearts of the mighty men of Edom in that day will be like the heart of a woman in labor.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20151BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20151BA\"></sup>Damascus.“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20151BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20151BB\"></sup>Hamath and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20151BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20151BC\"></sup>Arpad are put to shame,For they have heard bad news;They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20151BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20151BD\"></sup>disheartened.There is anxiety by the sea,It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20151BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20151BE\"></sup>cannot be calmed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Damascus has become helpless;She has turned away to flee,And panic has gripped her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20152BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20152BF\"></sup>Distress and pangs have taken hold of herLike a woman in childbirth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“How the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20153BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20153BG\"></sup>city of praise has not been deserted,The town of My joy!",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Therefore, her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20154BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20154BH\"></sup>young men will fall in her streets,And all the men of war will be silenced in that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20155BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20155BI\"></sup>set fire to the wall of Damascus,And it will devour the fortified towers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20155BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20155BJ\"></sup>Ben-hadad.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20156BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20156BK\"></sup>Kedar and the kingdoms of Hazor, which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon defeated. Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Arise, go up to KedarAnd devastate the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20156BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20156BL\"></sup>men of the east.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“They will take away their tents and their flocks;They will carry off for themselvesTheir tent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20157BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20157BM\"></sup>curtains, all their goods and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20157BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20157BN\"></sup>camels,And they will call out to one another, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20157BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20157BO\"></sup>Terror on every side!’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Run away, flee! Dwell in the depths,O inhabitants of Hazor,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20158BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20158BP\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon has formed a plan against youAnd devised a scheme against you.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Arise, go up against a nation which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20159BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20159BQ\"></sup>at ease,Which lives securely,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“It has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20159BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20159BR\"></sup>no gates or bars;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20159BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20159BS\"></sup>dwell alone.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Their camels will become plunder,And their many cattle for booty,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20160BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20160BT\"></sup>scatter to all the winds those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20160BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20160BU\"></sup>cut the corners <i>of their hair</i>;And I will bring their disaster from every side,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Hazor will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20161BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20161BV\"></sup>haunt of jackals,A desolation forever;No one will live there,Nor will a son of man reside in it.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>That which came as the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Jeremiah the prophet concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20162BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20162BW\"></sup>Elam, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20162BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20162BX\"></sup>at the beginning of the reign of Zedekiah king of Judah, saying:",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,‘Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20163BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20163BY\"></sup>break the bow of Elam,The finest of their might.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>‘I will bring upon Elam the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20164BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20164BZ\"></sup>four windsFrom the four ends of heaven,And will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20164CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20164CA\"></sup>scatter them to all these winds;And there will be no nationTo which the outcasts of Elam will not go.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>‘So I will shatter Elam before their enemiesAnd before those who seek their lives;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20165CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20165CB\"></sup>bring calamity upon them,Even My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20165CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20165CC\"></sup>fierce anger,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20165CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20165CD\"></sup>send out the sword after themUntil I have consumed them.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>‘Then I will set My throne in ElamAnd destroy out of it king and princes,’Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>‘But it will come about in the last daysThat I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20167CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20167CE\"></sup>restore the fortunes of Elam,’”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">50 </span>The word which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20168A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20168A\"></sup>Babylon, the land of the Chaldeans, through Jeremiah the prophet:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20169B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20169B\"></sup>Declare and proclaim among the nations.Proclaim it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20169C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20169C\"></sup>lift up a standard.Do not conceal <i>it but</i> say,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20169D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20169D\"></sup>Babylon has been captured,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20169E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20169E\"></sup>Bel has been put to shame, Marduk has been shattered;Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20169F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20169F\"></sup>images have been put to shame, her idols have been shattered.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For a nation has come up against her out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20170G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20170G\"></sup>north; it will make her land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20170H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20170H\"></sup>an object of horror, and there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20170I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20170I\"></sup>no inhabitant in it. Both man and beast have wandered off, they have gone away!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“In those days and at that time,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “the sons of Israel will come, <i>both</i> they and the sons of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20171J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20171J\"></sup>as well; they will go along <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20171K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20171K\"></sup>weeping as they go, and it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20171L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20171L\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God they will seek.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20172M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20172M\"></sup>ask for the way to Zion, <i>turning</i> their faces in its direction; they will come that they may join themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <i>in</i> an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20172N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20172N\"></sup>everlasting covenant that will not be forgotten.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“My people have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20173O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20173O\"></sup>lost sheep;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20173P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20173P\"></sup>Their shepherds have led them astray.They have made them turn aside <i>on</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20173Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20173Q\"></sup>mountains;They have gone along from mountain to hillAnd have forgotten their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20173R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20173R\"></sup>resting place.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“All who came upon them have devoured them;And their adversaries have said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20174S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20174S\"></sup>We are not guilty,Inasmuch as they have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <i>who is</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20174T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20174T\"></sup>habitation of righteousness,Even the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20174U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20174U\"></sup>hope of their fathers.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Wander away from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20175V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20175V\"></sup>midst of BabylonAnd go forth from the land of the Chaldeans;Be also like male goats at the head of the flock.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20176W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20176W\"></sup>arouse and bring up against BabylonA horde of great nations from the land of the north,And they will draw up <i>their</i> battle lines against her;From there she will be taken captive.Their arrows will be like an expert warriorWho does not return empty-handed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20177X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20177X\"></sup>Chaldea will become plunder;All who plunder her will have enough,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Because you are glad, because you are jubilant,O you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20178Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20178Y\"></sup>pillage My heritage,Because you skip about like a threshing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20178Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20178Z\"></sup>heiferAnd neigh like stallions,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20179AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20179AA\"></sup>mother will be greatly ashamed,She who gave you birth will be humiliated.Behold, <i>she will be</i> the least of the nations,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20179AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20179AB\"></sup>wilderness, a parched land and a desert.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Because of the indignation of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> she will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20180AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20180AC\"></sup>not be inhabited,But she will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20180AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20180AD\"></sup>completely desolate;Everyone who passes by Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20180AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20180AE\"></sup>will be horrifiedAnd will hiss because of all her wounds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Draw up your battle lines against Babylon on every side,All you who bend the bow;Shoot at her, do not be sparing with <i>your</i> arrows,For she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20181AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20181AF\"></sup>sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Raise your battle cry against her on every side!She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20182AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20182AG\"></sup>given herself up, her pillars have fallen,Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20182AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20182AH\"></sup>walls have been torn down.For this is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20182AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20182AI\"></sup>vengeance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:Take vengeance on her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20182AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20182AJ\"></sup>As she has done <i>to others, so</i> do to her.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Cut off the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20183AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20183AK\"></sup>sower from BabylonAnd the one who wields the sickle at the time of harvest;From before the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20183AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20183AL\"></sup>sword of the oppressor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20183AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20183AM\"></sup>They will each turn back to his own peopleAnd they will each flee to his own land.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Israel is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20184AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20184AN\"></sup>scattered flock, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20184AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20184AO\"></sup>lions have driven <i>them</i> away. The first one <i>who</i> devoured him was the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20184AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20184AP\"></sup>king of Assyria, and this last one <i>who</i> has broken his bones is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20184AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20184AQ\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: ‘Behold, I am going to punish the king of Babylon and his land, just as I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20185AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20185AR\"></sup>punished the king of Assyria.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20186AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20186AS\"></sup>bring Israel back to his pasture and he will graze on Carmel and Bashan, and his desire will be satisfied in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20186AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20186AT\"></sup>hill country of Ephraim and Gilead.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In those days and at that time,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘search will be made for the iniquity of Israel, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20187AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20187AU\"></sup>there will be none; and for the sins of Judah, but they will not be found; for I will pardon those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20187AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20187AV\"></sup>whom I leave as a remnant.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Against the land of Merathaim, go up against it,And against the inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20188AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20188AW\"></sup>Pekod.Slay and utterly destroy them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And do according to all that I have commanded you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20189AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20189AX\"></sup>noise of battle is in the land,And great destruction.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“How the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20190AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20190AY\"></sup>hammer of the whole earthHas been cut off and broken!How Babylon has becomeAn object of horror among the nations!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20191AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20191AZ\"></sup>set a snare for you and you were also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20191BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20191BA\"></sup>caught, O Babylon,While you yourself were not aware;You have been found and also seizedBecause you have engaged in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20191BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20191BB\"></sup>conflict with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has opened His armoryAnd has brought forth the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20192BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20192BC\"></sup>weapons of His indignation,For it is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20192BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20192BD\"></sup>work of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hostsIn the land of the Chaldeans.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Come to her from the farthest border;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20193BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20193BE\"></sup>Open up her barns,Pile her up like heapsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20193BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20193BF\"></sup>utterly destroy her,Let nothing be left to her.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20194BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20194BG\"></sup>Put all her young bulls to the sword;Let them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20194BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20194BH\"></sup>go down to the slaughter!Woe be upon them, for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20194BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20194BI\"></sup>day has come,The time of their punishment.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>There is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20195BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20195BJ\"></sup>sound of fugitives and refugees from the land of Babylon,To declare in Zion the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20195BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20195BK\"></sup>vengeance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,Vengeance for His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20195BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20195BL\"></sup>temple.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Summon many against Babylon,All those who bend the bow:Encamp against her on every side,Let there be no escape.Repay her according to her work;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20196BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20196BM\"></sup>According to all that she has done, <i>so</i> do to her;For she has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20196BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20196BN\"></sup>arrogant against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Against the Holy One of Israel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Therefore her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20197BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20197BO\"></sup>young men will fall in her streets,And all her men of war will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20197BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20197BP\"></sup>silenced in that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20198BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20198BQ\"></sup>I am against you, O arrogant one,”Declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,“For your day has come,The time when I will punish you.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20199BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20199BR\"></sup>arrogant one will stumble and fallWith no one to raise him up;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20199BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20199BS\"></sup>set fire to his citiesAnd it will devour all his environs.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“The sons of Israel are oppressed,And the sons of Judah as well;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20200BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20200BT\"></sup>all who took them captive have held them fast,They have refused to let them go.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20201BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20201BU\"></sup>Redeemer is strong, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20201BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20201BV\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name;He will vigorously <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20201BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20201BW\"></sup>plead their caseSo that He may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20201BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20201BX\"></sup>bring rest to the earth,But turmoil to the inhabitants of Babylon.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20202BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20202BY\"></sup>sword against the Chaldeans,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And against the inhabitants of BabylonAnd against her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20202BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20202BZ\"></sup>officials and her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20202CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20202CA\"></sup>wise men!",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“A sword against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20203CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20203CB\"></sup>oracle priests, and they will become fools!A sword against her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20203CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20203CC\"></sup>mighty men, and they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20203CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20203CD\"></sup>shattered!",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“A sword against their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20204CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20204CE\"></sup>horses and against their chariotsAnd against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20204CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20204CF\"></sup>foreigners who are in the midst of her,And they will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20204CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20204CG\"></sup>women!A sword against her treasures, and they will be plundered!",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20205CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20205CH\"></sup>drought on her waters, and they will be dried up!For it is a land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20205CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20205CI\"></sup>idols,And they are mad over fearsome idols.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20206CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20206CJ\"></sup>desert creatures will live <i>there</i> along with the jackals;The ostriches also will live in it,And it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20206CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20206CK\"></sup>never again be inhabitedOr dwelt in from generation to generation.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“As when God overthrew <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20207CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20207CL\"></sup>SodomAnd Gomorrah with its neighbors,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“No man will live there,Nor will <i>any</i> son of man reside in it.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“Behold, a people is coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20208CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20208CM\"></sup>from the north,And a great nation and many kingsWill be aroused from the remote parts of the earth.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20209CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20209CN\"></sup>seize <i>their</i> bow and javelin;They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20209CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20209CO\"></sup>cruel and have no mercy.Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20209CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20209CP\"></sup>voice roars like the sea;And they ride on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20209CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20209CQ\"></sup>horses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20209CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20209CR\"></sup>Marshalled like a man for the battleAgainst you, O daughter of Babylon.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20210CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20210CS\"></sup>king of Babylon has heard the report about them,And his hands hang limp;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20210CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20210CT\"></sup>Distress has gripped him,Agony like a woman in childbirth.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20211CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20211CU\"></sup>Behold, one will come up like a lion from the thicket of the Jordan to a perennially watered pasture; for in an instant I will make them run away from it, and whoever is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20211CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20211CV\"></sup>chosen I will appoint over it. For who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20211CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20211CW\"></sup>like Me, and who will summon Me <i>into court</i>? And who then is the shepherd who can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20211CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20211CX\"></sup>stand before Me?”",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Therefore hear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20212CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20212CY\"></sup>plan of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which He has planned against Babylon, and His purposes which He has purposed against the land of the Chaldeans: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20212CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20212CZ\"></sup>surely they will drag them off, <i>even</i> the little ones of the flock; surely He will make their pasture desolate because of them.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>At the shout, “Babylon has been seized!” the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20213DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20213DA\"></sup>earth is shaken, and an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20213DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20213DB\"></sup>outcry is heard among the nations."
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">51 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Behold, I am going to arouse against BabylonAnd against the inhabitants of Leb-kamaiThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20214A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20214A\"></sup>spirit of a destroyer.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I will dispatch foreigners to Babylon that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20215B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20215B\"></sup>winnow herAnd may devastate her land;For on every side they will be opposed to herIn the day of <i>her</i> calamity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Let not him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20216C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20216C\"></sup>bends his bow bend <i>it</i>,Nor let him rise up in his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20216D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20216D\"></sup>scale-armor;So do not spare her young men;Devote all her army to destruction.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“They will fall down slain in the land of the Chaldeans,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20217E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20217E\"></sup>pierced through in their streets.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20218F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20218F\"></sup>neither Israel nor Judah has been forsakenBy his God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,Although their land is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20218G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20218G\"></sup>full of guiltBefore the Holy One of Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20219H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20219H\"></sup>Flee from the midst of Babylon,And each of you save his life!Do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20219I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20219I\"></sup>destroyed in her punishment,For this is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20219J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20219J\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> time of vengeance;He is going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20219K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20219K\"></sup>render recompense to her.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Babylon has been a golden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20220L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20220L\"></sup>cup in the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Intoxicating all the earth.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20220M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20220M\"></sup>nations have drunk of her wine;Therefore the nations are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20220N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20220N\"></sup>going mad.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Suddenly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20221O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20221O\"></sup>Babylon has fallen and been broken;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20221P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20221P\"></sup>Wail over her!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20221Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20221Q\"></sup>Bring balm for her pain;Perhaps she may be healed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We applied healing to Babylon, but she was not healed;Forsake her and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20222R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20222R\"></sup>let us each go to his own country,For her judgment has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20222S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20222S\"></sup>reached to heavenAnd towers up to the very skies.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20223T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20223T\"></sup>brought about our vindication;Come and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20223U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20223U\"></sup>recount in ZionThe work of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20224V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20224V\"></sup>Sharpen the arrows, fill the quivers!The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has aroused the spirit of the kings of the Medes,Because His purpose is against Babylon to destroy it;For it is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20224W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20224W\"></sup>vengeance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, vengeance for His temple.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20225X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20225X\"></sup>Lift up a signal against the walls of Babylon;Post a strong guard,Station sentries,Place men in ambush!For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20225Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20225Y\"></sup>purposed and performedWhat He spoke concerning the inhabitants of Babylon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>O you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20226Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20226Z\"></sup>dwell by many waters,Abundant in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20226AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20226AA\"></sup>treasures,Your end has come,The measure of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20226AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20226AB\"></sup>end.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20227AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20227AC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sworn by Himself:“Surely I will fill you with a population like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20227AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20227AD\"></sup>locusts,And they will cry out with shouts of victory over you.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><i>It is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20228AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20228AE\"></sup>He who made the earth by His power,Who established the world by His wisdom,And by His understanding He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20228AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20228AF\"></sup>stretched out the heavens.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When He utters His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20229AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20229AG\"></sup>voice, <i>there is</i> a tumult of waters in the heavens,And He causes the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20229AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20229AH\"></sup>clouds to ascend from the end of the earth;He makes lightning for the rainAnd brings forth the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20229AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20229AI\"></sup>wind from His storehouses.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20230AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20230AJ\"></sup>All mankind is stupid, devoid of knowledge;Every goldsmith is put to shame by his idols,For his molten images are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20230AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20230AK\"></sup>deceitful,And there is no breath in them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20231AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20231AL\"></sup>worthless, a work of mockery;In the time of their punishment they will perish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20232AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20232AM\"></sup>portion of Jacob is not like these;For the Maker of all is He,And of the tribe of His inheritance;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20232AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20232AN\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><i>He says</i>, “You are My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20233AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20233AO\"></sup>war-club, <i>My</i> weapon of war;And with you I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20233AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20233AP\"></sup>shatter nations,And with you I destroy kingdoms.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“With you I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20234AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20234AQ\"></sup>shatter the horse and his rider,And with you I shatter the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20234AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20234AR\"></sup>chariot and its rider,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And with you I shatter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20235AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20235AS\"></sup>man and woman,And with you I shatter old man and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20235AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20235AT\"></sup>youth,And with you I shatter young man and virgin,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And with you I shatter the shepherd and his flock,And with you I shatter the farmer and his team,And with you I shatter governors and prefects.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But I will repay Babylon and all the inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20237AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20237AU\"></sup>Chaldea for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20237AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20237AV\"></sup>all their evil that they have done in Zion before your eyes,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20238AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20238AW\"></sup>I am against you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20238AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20238AX\"></sup>O destroying mountain,Who destroys the whole earth,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And I will stretch out My hand against you,And roll you down from the crags,And I will make you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20238AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20238AY\"></sup>burnt out mountain.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“They will not take from you <i>even</i> a stone for a cornerNor a stone for foundations,But you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20239AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20239AZ\"></sup>desolate forever,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20240BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20240BA\"></sup>Lift up a signal in the land,Blow a trumpet among the nations!Consecrate the nations against her,Summon against her the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20240BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20240BB\"></sup>kingdoms of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20240BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20240BC\"></sup>Ararat, Minni and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20240BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20240BD\"></sup>Ashkenaz;Appoint a marshal against her,Bring up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20240BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20240BE\"></sup>horses like bristly locusts.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Consecrate the nations against her,The kings of the Medes,Their governors and all their prefects,And every land of their dominion.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20242BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20242BF\"></sup>land quakes and writhes,For the purposes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> against Babylon stand,To make the land of BabylonA <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20242BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20242BG\"></sup>desolation without inhabitants.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20243BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20243BH\"></sup>mighty men of Babylon have ceased fighting,They stay in the strongholds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20243BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20243BI\"></sup>Their strength is exhausted,They are becoming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20243BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20243BJ\"></sup><i>like</i> women;Their dwelling places are set on fire,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20243BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20243BK\"></sup>bars of her <i>gates</i> are broken.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20244BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20244BL\"></sup>courier runs to meet another,And one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20244BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20244BM\"></sup>messenger to meet another,To tell the king of BabylonThat his city has been captured from end <i>to end</i>;",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The fords also have been seized,And they have burned the marshes with fire,And the men of war are terrified.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel:“The daughter of Babylon is like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20246BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20246BN\"></sup>threshing floorAt the time it is stamped firm;Yet in a little while the time of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20246BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20246BO\"></sup>harvest will come for her.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20247BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20247BP\"></sup>devoured me <i>and</i> crushed me,He has set me down <i>like</i> an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20247BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20247BQ\"></sup>empty vessel;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20247BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20247BR\"></sup>swallowed me like a monster,He has filled his stomach with my delicacies;He has washed me away.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“May the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20248BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20248BS\"></sup>violence <i>done</i> to me and to my flesh be upon Babylon,”The inhabitant of Zion will say;And, “May my blood be upon the inhabitants of Chaldea,”Jerusalem will say.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20249BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20249BT\"></sup>plead your caseAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20249BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20249BU\"></sup>exact full vengeance for you;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20249BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20249BV\"></sup>I will dry up her seaAnd make her fountain dry.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20250BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20250BW\"></sup>Babylon will become a heap <i>of ruins</i>, a haunt of jackals,An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20250BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20250BX\"></sup>object of horror and hissing, without inhabitants.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“They will roar together like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20251BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20251BY\"></sup>young lions,They will growl like lions’ cubs.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“When they become heated up, I will serve <i>them</i> their banquetAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20252BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20252BZ\"></sup>make them drunk, that they may become jubilantAnd may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20252CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20252CA\"></sup>sleep a perpetual sleepAnd not wake up,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“I will bring them down like lambs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20253CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20253CB\"></sup>to the slaughter,Like rams together with male goats.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20254CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20254CC\"></sup>Sheshak has been captured,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20254CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20254CD\"></sup>the praise of the whole earth been seized!How Babylon has become an object of horror among the nations!",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20255CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20255CE\"></sup>sea has come up over Babylon;She has been engulfed with its tumultuous waves.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“Her cities have become an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20256CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20256CF\"></sup>object of horror,A parched land and a desert,A land in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20256CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20256CG\"></sup>no man livesAnd through which no son of man passes.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20257CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20257CH\"></sup>I will punish Bel in Babylon,And I will make what he has swallowed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20257CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20257CI\"></sup>come out of his mouth;And the nations will no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20257CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20257CJ\"></sup>stream to him.Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20257CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20257CK\"></sup>wall of Babylon has fallen down!",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20258CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20258CL\"></sup>Come forth from her midst, My people,And each of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20258CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20258CM\"></sup>save yourselvesFrom the fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20259CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20259CN\"></sup>so that your heart does not grow faint,And you are not afraid at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20259CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20259CO\"></sup>report that <i>will be</i> heard in the land—For the report will come one year,And after that another report in another year,And violence <i>will be</i> in the landWith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20259CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20259CP\"></sup>ruler against ruler—",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Therefore behold, days are comingWhen I will punish the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20260CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20260CQ\"></sup>idols of Babylon;And her whole land will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20260CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20260CR\"></sup>put to shameAnd all her slain will fall in her midst.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20261CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20261CS\"></sup>heaven and earth and all that is in themWill shout for joy over Babylon,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20261CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20261CT\"></sup>the destroyers will come to her from the north,”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20262CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20262CU\"></sup>Indeed Babylon is to fall <i>for</i> the slain of Israel,<i>As</i> also for Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20262CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20262CV\"></sup>the slain of all the earth have fallen.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20263CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20263CW\"></sup>who have escaped the sword,Depart! Do not stay!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20263CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20263CX\"></sup>Remember the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from afar,And let Jerusalem come to your mind.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20264CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20264CY\"></sup>We are ashamed because we have heard reproach;Disgrace has covered our faces,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20264CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20264CZ\"></sup>aliens have enteredThe holy places of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>“Therefore behold, the days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“When I will punish her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20265DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20265DA\"></sup>idols,And the mortally wounded will groan throughout her land.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>“Though Babylon should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20266DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20266DB\"></sup>ascend to the heavens,And though she should fortify her lofty stronghold,From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20266DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20266DC\"></sup>Me destroyers will come to her,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20267DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20267DD\"></sup>sound of an outcry from Babylon,And of great destruction from the land of the Chaldeans!",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is going to destroy Babylon,And He will make <i>her</i> loud noise vanish from her.And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20268DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20268DE\"></sup>waves will roar like many waters;The tumult of their voices sounds forth.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20269DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20269DF\"></sup>destroyer is coming against her, against Babylon,And her mighty men will be captured,Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20269DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20269DG\"></sup>bows are shattered;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a God of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20269DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20269DH\"></sup>recompense,He will fully repay.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20270DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20270DI\"></sup>make her princes and her wise men drunk,Her governors, her prefects and her mighty men,That they may sleep a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20270DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20270DJ\"></sup>perpetual sleep and not wake up,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20270DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20270DK\"></sup>Declares the King, whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,“The broad <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20271DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20271DL\"></sup>wall of Babylon will be completely razedAnd her high <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20271DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20271DM\"></sup>gates will be set on fire;So the peoples will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20271DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20271DN\"></sup>toil for nothing,And the nations become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20271DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20271DO\"></sup>exhausted <i>only</i> for fire.”",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>The message which Jeremiah the prophet commanded Seraiah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20272DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20272DP\"></sup>Neriah, the grandson of Mahseiah, when he went with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20272DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20272DQ\"></sup>Zedekiah the king of Judah to Babylon in the fourth year of his reign. (Now Seraiah was quartermaster.)",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>So Jeremiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20273DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20273DR\"></sup>wrote in a single scroll all the calamity which would come upon Babylon, <i>that is</i>, all these words which have been written concerning Babylon.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to Seraiah, “As soon as you come to Babylon, then see that you read all these words aloud,",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>and say, ‘You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have promised concerning this place to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20275DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20275DS\"></sup>cut it off, so that there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20275DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20275DT\"></sup>nothing dwelling in it, whether man or beast, but it will be a perpetual desolation.’",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>And as soon as you finish reading this scroll, you will tie a stone to it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20276DU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DU&quot;&gt;DU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20276DU\"></sup>throw it into the middle of the Euphrates,",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>and say, ‘Just so shall Babylon sink down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20277DV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DV&quot;&gt;DV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20277DV\"></sup>not rise again because of the calamity that I am going to bring upon her; and they will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20277DW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DW&quot;&gt;DW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20277DW\"></sup>exhausted.’” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20277DX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DX&quot;&gt;DX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20277DX\"></sup>Thus far are the words of Jeremiah."
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">52 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20278A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20278A\"></sup>Zedekiah was twenty-one years old when he became king, and he reigned eleven years in Jerusalem; and his mother’s name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20278B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20278B\"></sup>Hamutal the daughter of Jeremiah of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20278C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20278C\"></sup>Libnah.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20279D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20279D\"></sup>evil in the sight of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> like all that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20279E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20279E\"></sup>Jehoiakim had done.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20280F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20280F\"></sup>anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <i>this</i> came about in Jerusalem and Judah until He cast them out from His presence. And Zedekiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20280G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20280G\"></sup>rebelled against the king of Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20281H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20281H\"></sup>Now it came about in the ninth year of his reign, on the tenth <i>day</i> of the tenth month, that Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon came, he and all his army, against Jerusalem, camped against it and built a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20281I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20281I\"></sup>siege wall all around it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20282J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20282J\"></sup>So the city was under siege until the eleventh year of King Zedekiah.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On the ninth <i>day</i> of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20283K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20283K\"></sup>fourth month the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20283L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20283L\"></sup>famine was so severe in the city that there was no food for the people of the land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the city was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20284M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20284M\"></sup>broken into, and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20284N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20284N\"></sup>men of war fled and went forth from the city at night by way of the gate between the two walls which <i>was</i> by the king’s garden, though the Chaldeans were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20284O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20284O\"></sup>all around the city. And they went by way of the Arabah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the army of the Chaldeans pursued the king and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20285P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20285P\"></sup>overtook Zedekiah in the plains of Jericho, and all his army was scattered from him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then they captured the king and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20286Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20286Q\"></sup>brought him up to the king of Babylon at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20286R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20286R\"></sup>Riblah in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20286S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20286S\"></sup>Hamath, and he passed sentence on him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20287T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20287T\"></sup>slaughtered the sons of Zedekiah before his eyes, and he also slaughtered all the princes of Judah in Riblah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20288U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20288U\"></sup>blinded the eyes of Zedekiah; and the king of Babylon bound him with bronze fetters and brought him to Babylon and put him in prison until the day of his death.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20289V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20289V\"></sup>Now on the tenth <i>day</i> of the fifth month, which was the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20289W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20289W\"></sup>nineteenth year of King Nebuchadnezzar, king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20289X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20289X\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard, who was in the service of the king of Babylon, came to Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20290Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20290Y\"></sup>burned the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20290Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20290Z\"></sup>king’s house and all the houses of Jerusalem; even every large house he burned with fire.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So all the army of the Chaldeans who <i>were</i> with the captain of the guard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20291AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20291AA\"></sup>broke down all the walls around Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20292AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20292AB\"></sup>carried away into exile some of the poorest of the people, the rest of the people who were left in the city, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20292AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20292AC\"></sup>deserters who had deserted to the king of Babylon and the rest of the artisans.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20293AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20293AD\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard left some of the poorest of the land to be vinedressers and plowmen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now the bronze <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20294AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20294AE\"></sup>pillars which belonged to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20294AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20294AF\"></sup>stands and the bronze <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20294AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20294AG\"></sup>sea, which were in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Chaldeans broke in pieces and carried all their bronze to Babylon.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They also took away the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20295AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20295AH\"></sup>pots, the shovels, the snuffers, the basins, the pans and all the bronze vessels which were used in <i>temple</i> service.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The captain of the guard also took away the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20296AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20296AI\"></sup>bowls, the firepans, the basins, the pots, the lampstands, the pans and the drink offering bowls, what was fine gold and what was fine silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The two pillars, the one sea, and the twelve bronze bulls that were under the sea, <i>and</i> the stands, which King Solomon had made for the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—the bronze of all these vessels was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20297AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20297AJ\"></sup>beyond weight.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>As for the pillars, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20298AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20298AK\"></sup>height of each pillar <i>was</i> eighteen cubits, and it <i>was</i> twelve cubits in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20298AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20298AL\"></sup>circumference and four fingers in thickness, <i>and</i> hollow.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20299AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20299AM\"></sup>capital of bronze was on it; and the height of each capital was five cubits, with network and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20299AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20299AN\"></sup>pomegranates upon the capital all around, all of bronze. And the second pillar was like these, including pomegranates.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>There were ninety-six exposed pomegranates; all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20300AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20300AO\"></sup>the pomegranates <i>numbered</i> a hundred on the network all around.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then the captain of the guard took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20301AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20301AP\"></sup>Seraiah the chief priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20301AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20301AQ\"></sup>Zephaniah the second priest, with the three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20301AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20301AR\"></sup>officers of the temple.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He also took from the city one official who was overseer of the men of war, and seven of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20302AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20302AS\"></sup>king’s advisers who were found in the city, and the scribe of the commander of the army who mustered the people of the land, and sixty men of the people of the land who were found in the midst of the city.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard took them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20303AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20303AT\"></sup>brought them to the king of Babylon at Riblah.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20304AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20304AU\"></sup>struck them down and put them to death at Riblah in the land of Hamath. So Judah was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20304AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20304AV\"></sup>led away into exile from its land.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>These are the people whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20305AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20305AW\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar carried away into exile: in the seventh year 3,023 Jews;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>in the eighteenth year of Nebuchadnezzar 832 persons from Jerusalem;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>in the twenty-third year of Nebuchadnezzar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20307AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20307AX\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard carried into exile 745 Jewish people; there were 4,600 persons in all.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20308AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20308AY\"></sup>Now it came about in the thirty-seventh year of the exile of Jehoiachin king of Judah, in the twelfth month, on the twenty-fifth of the month, that Evil-merodach king of Babylon, in the <i>first</i> year of his reign, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20308AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20308AZ\"></sup>showed favor to Jehoiachin king of Judah and brought him out of prison.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20309BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20309BA\"></sup>Then he spoke kindly to him and set his throne above the thrones of the kings who <i>were</i> with him in Babylon.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So Jehoiachin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20310BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20310BB\"></sup>changed his prison clothes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20310BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20310BC\"></sup>had his meals in the king’s presence regularly all the days of his life.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For his allowance, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20311BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20311BD\"></sup>regular allowance was given him by the king of Babylon, a daily portion all the days of his life until the day of his death."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;